user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Chloe Rachel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgExGuK1W-XgQc1tPnrQlqQkWxCTaNhdz977uVTTY3zjpsAzs-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favourite eatery! I used to visit their Vancouver location all the time, before it unfortunately closed. Kind staff, and was nice to see a familiar face! My go-to is their be the creator bowl. Their charred chicken tikka, roasted cauliflower, and mint mayo sauce are not to be missed. I also ordered a Liquid Gold smoothie with a base of oat milk. The drink was delicious and so creamy! Minimal ginger taste, which was fine for me!

This location sells pizza as well (under the brand Pizza Dough Therapy and Oja's Blend), and the staff were kind enough to let us try a piece (pepperoni and vegetable). Can attest that it was a good slice of pizza! I don't know if I'll be able to part with my favourite bowl, but the pizza sure is tempting! They have a deal on pizza on Tuesdays where their medium pizzas are $10.99 - half off the regular price of $20.77. The White Rock location is quite far for me, but I was happy to return and look forward to my next visit. Hoping they open more locations in the future!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMd5Pxvz1O4HsCNwyOOD5_p4IR1FW-9QWvNoAu4&fid=0x0:0x6163c9d0eaa8d8d7"],"When":"2024-11-13"},{"Name":"Mer_bestybay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-YRI28t2Ru_2IKmV1DodXyZ-Qg6RUTjLngyQR9W1eMj5KQndl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got the Funky Chicken and Cauli-Sautra bowl and they were both AMAZING. My mom and I agreed that the produce was so fresh. The sauce was so flavourful, ingredients were cut into bite sized pieces and the quality was just impeccable. This is the second time I have gone back and I’ll def go many times again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8xfZp5uZszJTphThHbEiS0jQnCkV6NG0LGIBx&fid=0x0:0x6163c9d0eaa8d8d7"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Shanti Jamilah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5MjQNZty7iy-5mfQsq9txTh4xqLqQJg41EeO1Evjh6KZhpeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Most wonderful Oja’s blend has the best salad bowls, pizza, wraps, smoothies and more! My go to favourite is the funky chicken bowl. Everyone always tastes so fresh, service is always lovely, and my belly is always happy after I eat here :) come support your small business White Rock residents! Shout out to Mahek for the great service today!
Ps they have their own parking lot too so very convenient to step in on the go and pick up food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAT14ZEfN7c7XIShq6KDPIraJQs7Rfea4iYmcU&fid=0x0:0x6163c9d0eaa8d8d7"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"Stephanie Chua","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxi5fhi7MPPGJB9Cugn3OxtPslAwDfdiaP0TYZEHUq31GDzn5I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved the “be the creator” salad & the butter chicken wrap - the whole ingredients were organic & really fresh, both items tasted delicious!! Service was excellent, definitely returning for more! Vegan friendly too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYKX2vqp-fpVJlG_TZT5cB-M4ei_YIJy1wPYlm&fid=0x0:0x6163c9d0eaa8d8d7"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"noopur trivedi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7s2zsAIHG-LokBqYJJ3f0H2uL_aYf8eUdFf8o8qGpPyBIskPrFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Ojas and tried their pizza, tofu wrap, and paneer wrap, and I absolutely loved everything! The pizza had the perfect crispy crust, and both wraps were fresh, flavorful, and satisfying. What I really appreciated was that their recipes seem to be crafted with health-conscious people in mind. The meals are not only full of flavor but also well-balanced, with a great mix of protein, fiber, and carbs, so you can enjoy the taste without feeling guilty.  Overall the food is really delicious no matter what you try. Every bite felt thoughtfully made.

On top of the delicious food their customer service was exceptional. The staff were welcoming and attentive, the restaurant ambience was very chill and relaxed, and there’s plenty of seating, plus a huge parking area making the whole experience very comfortable.

If you're looking for a place that combines healthy eating with great taste and friendly service, I highly recommend Ojas. This will be my go to place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHoJbtw3T3YlCEi7MzB8nBf-vRzF-XX8ecbsem&fid=0x0:0x6163c9d0eaa8d8d7"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Stephane Nicaise","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpjd9fbIfWTb-Krfg_3Ti9SCy2OjgDnwaQ5DWuJFO5irnJG-7rLA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely amazing! Super fresh produce, healthy and delicious tasting food. I had the funky chicken bowl and I will be back to try the rest of the menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIERn-mBUYqKRYYnzAfl4EbfSsrrO5KZL7n7Kp&fid=0x0:0x6163c9d0eaa8d8d7"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Juan Porragas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLeW6RZdmyJgwXp1wvKsYDFg9x6R2XFvJ-8-LFxnldQowiWZr7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their specialty are bowls, wraps and smoothie but they also have a great tasting pizza. With a special twist the pepperoni pizza turns into a party of flavors in the mouth. Oh! And they are also very nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOY4-juHGcMFa5l54qTfzfJggPVrIoiQGyUXoET&fid=0x0:0x6163c9d0eaa8d8d7"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Patti O","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWePJiTBjjdIxnSFHvXAuhSxG_sKf8GW4hgfJcoZXFh9orPRNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food and service is outstanding. Atmosphere is average, very small area to dine-in but great to people watch. The owner and employees are so accommodating and friendly.
The best authentic pizza I’ve had in 25 yrs, homemade on the spot and ready in 12 minutes.
Definitely a must try 👍","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Joaquin Tamesis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWG7NY6NFFto1U0OMGi2HMLhV4PeOJJAGyzrQ8zPk_v4DLlqhT_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Spent my 32 birthday here for brunch with my very big family. Not the first time around we've spent birthday brunches at the Wooden Spoon. And definitely will not be the last. As crazy as my family are .. and how many people we have immediately. The Wooden Spoon never fails to provide us with an experience that will last a life time.

Thank you for always being so welcoming to us @TheWoodenSpoon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrhe6gwo4q-LcE7Q84LsP4XruHTofZYnKgnjqX&fid=0x0:0x4bf8347495ab85d9"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Davy Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgCAO9FlA0EqUedpS0FJ6mMhFo-aO0PkgQk6i9OQ6eUwYN7G2C=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience at Wooden Spoon. The staff were very welcoming and friendly and the service was fantastic as well. The vegetarian hash was absolutely delicious, and the freshly squeezed orange juice was definitely worth it. Will come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJlQQaY-mqfwERelCI_EDYFpRPf8CpsVT-Mee8&fid=0x0:0x4bf8347495ab85d9"],"When":"2024-11-20"},{"Name":"James Sloan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVA-agu3VJJ1b4cH3FSrybrAm4sxkh85afsrr_K0JW7gzoYvVjz1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Do it! Eat at this place. Our first time today and certainly not our last. The food was great. I was very hungover so I stuck with the classic breakfast, their “Farmhouse”. It did not disappoint. My husband had the steak sandwich and was very pleased. The staff was friendly and the little bear with the beard that works front of house was very engaging and attentive. Eat here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxDEMLCFrJneYr7Oq9LESVIVCaMo0IA9atVR6f&fid=0x0:0x4bf8347495ab85d9"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Sara Carlyle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUfagfxPSsqRzysTwGF0HJYhcU468FFL0xhcJkSC6KqdQt-JTe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very unique spot. It’s a small comfortable atmosphere with a nice patio. Our server Eric was very personable and kind. I had the mushroom egg benny my husband had a burger, wow 10/10! The drinks are also top tier. Ethical sustainable ingredients is also nice. Not like other greasy breakfast spots. Parking was easy to get and I’ll definitely be back. Thanks for the great service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjp7dlaSysT8KAEIydzgE287uFBnz3sP-Xnsbe&fid=0x0:0x4bf8347495ab85d9"],"When":"2024-8-20"},{"Name":"Kim Brooks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQ6tjiVVur3Zx2mh_ZpqgeQ3XGWzX1NGG9QWnGyV_1FV_wzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food and drinks were amazing! Good portion sizes and incredibly tasty. Based on food alone it would be 5 stars. My issue was with the service. It wasn’t terrible, our server got our order and brought our food but it certainly seemed like she wanted to be anywhere else but serving food. No conversation, no recommendations basically no personality. That would be fine if there wasn’t the expectation of a tip. I work in the industry and I have no problem tipping. But when I get the bare minimum of service it makes it really difficult to justify. She made a small attempt at conversation when the bill came, presumably to secure a good tip. I’ll be coming back, but probably just for take out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8Qq6Q-o7NJ0bWv2Pc8WLY57OrnkhQzYet8gr1&fid=0x0:0x4bf8347495ab85d9"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"James Mendonca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDOYVs1G-8iT9QF6Fj3_nUauDo1DS6zISrEp3lZ9wij4inDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted to eat at the Wooden Spoon Bistro when I decided to go to White Rock to look at the sites. When I got there, it was very busy because of the long weekend and that they had a street market where the restaurant was. Naturally, the place was busy. The establishment had a hipster aesthetic look, despite being a brunch restaurant. I ordered the Tiramisu French Toast with Coffee. The coffee was decent, and they serve it with cream in a steel bell pourer and raw brown sugar packets. The french toast practically tastes like a cake, in a great way. The vanilla espresso mascarpone was potent in palate, and it was covered in cocoa powder and cookie crumble. They also serve it with maple syrup in a steel bell as well. The waiters are admirable about their work and never neglect their customers. Overall, this is a fantastic restaurant for breakfast and lunch. However, I do suggest calling for reservations in advance to avoid any long waits.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuVJy_Lt0bdgie6BBTBhwyNE3c-Wd4y6SvU4YI&fid=0x0:0x4bf8347495ab85d9"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Astara Astara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfcpTVZZi1UCJCkSHf3RSKmSt-kLjSDFa7hxD1qQV-49_Z6EhP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another White Rock gem that took me way too long to try!

Really nice staff and vibe here. It’s so hard to find spots that compare to service and standards of Vancouver and Wooden Spoon does not disappoint!

We came for a birthday lunch/brunch and it was pretty busy for a weekday.

The service was great. The food was delicious and the drinks were great.

We are vegan + gluten free and dairy free + gluten free so there isn’t too much for us on the menu, but that’s ok. Unfortunately in 2024 it’s still a struggle to find restaurants that cater to non soy + gluten eating vegans + dairy free peeps.

I would definitely come here again. It’s seems like a really awesome local spot to have some awesome food and drinks!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_PwvcUUYSz213-AuxeZuwKYNkou6IZXhfT1N1&fid=0x0:0x4bf8347495ab85d9"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"F. D. Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIKoboKBCCoVNFoBeRYNjWH_q7v3Y0TEFC_2o5biRC5M-XjcK-QA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food 4.5/5 Fresh and tasty
Service 4/5 Staff are kind and attentive. They nicely asked us to leave after about two hours of dining time saying people were waiting. We understood and settled the bill. But there were empty tables so not really sure why they rushed us.
Ambience 5/5 Very cute

Return likelihood: yes if I am in the area again as it’s quite far away from my neighborhood","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVu2ghDwORYVqY1uw6EmCw1p74EgMs2AdZSue3&fid=0x0:0x4bf8347495ab85d9"],"When":"2024-2-27"}]

[{"Name":"Lanie Zulueta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIjacOZZNFIlv1T1yr25Te9nNNi1G78MhV6gOT7cCRO1Lr8sw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything was perfect! The food was flavourful, the service was amazing, and the patio dining was cozy and warm with an awesome view. They were very accommodating and even gave our puppy a drink. Food servings are generous and the cheesecake is a must-try! Special thanks to our incredible server Emma!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTDhenxs6D_lsg2rNJFsTwXGRhm4cvnz0W2uad&fid=0x0:0x3e5b2d2998e89619"],"When":"2024-11-4"},{"Name":"Jorge Enrique Marciales Acosta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs9G5ZpQ_qTBOsbd8J0VpmKWERzXHqzAq0CocOXlhPv9vZOWo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely the best hamburgers in BC! It’s been almost two years since my last visit, and I wish I’d come back sooner. The customer service is fantastic. I just want to say, thanks for existing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPWmBkThtYETLTHs3yBwa-3QunnN2Zc-UKuL71&fid=0x0:0x3e5b2d2998e89619"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Marnie Eudela-Umlas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXg_gVRD_Hd9V3XIUh6_P71KHCryea9xsHYGqrZHTuXW_jdxEU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Spent my birthday here with the hubby and we loved their food. Their location is awesome as it’s by the pier. Food, drinks and dessert were all good. Service was fast. Our desserts were on the house coz they had to move a bit to make room. Would have done it for free anyways as we understood the crowd getting bigger. Another great choice in White Rock and we will be back :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkjMopHuQ2oHdYhbLde7D4Mx3WMrltRdP8d2hD&fid=0x0:0x3e5b2d2998e89619"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Stacey Lynne Simonson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyKS51fEefwIy5YcywkkUqLaDpWTrPcgMBYo43CUdOCl26MZxX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a delightful lunch, the crab cake was amazing! Shared a salad with added duck leg, and it was perfect. Our server, Adrienne (sp?), was attentive and charming. I would definitely return. So many lovely gluten free options. I was so excited I didn't get a picture of the crab cake, but it was so good I almost ordered another, but I was too full.  The view was beautiful from the patio.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOkxxOVaZzweVymqx1yfifPR-6qWjzdSsqoZ9P&fid=0x0:0x3e5b2d2998e89619"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Starry Kitten","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYY50MptQOO49temYVIECZVVr4N9-usBp2e7mhqV9OIOvBzrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came to visit Uli’s based on the great reviews and because I am Celiac and they sounded like they were very accommodating. We were not disappointed. While the menu and everything is a bit expensive, I believe the majority, if not the whole menu is locally sourced. The food was great and I loved the Fire in the Sky and Holy Smokes drinks (I’m an old man drink person who loves old fashioneds).

They were so knowledgeable about Celiac & the food was so yummy! My partner loved the salmon and I really enjoyed the oysters there 😋

They were also so sweet to my partner’s kiddo and were so kind when he spilled Pepsi all over himself 😅 which reminds me that my partner also specifically said he really loved the napkin quality there?? Haha.

That being said, the best part was the customer service. The staff there are fantastic. They’re super personable and sweet and I was so happy they all remembered us on our second visit. Absolutely 100000/10 service, thank you Dean, Mateo, and of course our first night’s server. She was the sweetest woman ever and I’m so sorry I don’t know her name. But we loved her. I’m so happy we came to Uli’s for our couple dinners 🥰 We will come back next summer when we visit White Rock! Thanks Uli’s staff!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPf299Sym8OEya7adQ8hVB7oDqcaHoIBE9XkjKi&fid=0x0:0x3e5b2d2998e89619"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Darlene Kemp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgwwGuFoHvNYs2Uy7o6DnrTQFssfKNuG22yRrnqcR8DXBJmDcMGg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Uli's is located right on the White Rock beach strip and has beautiful ocean views. The atmosphere, service, food and drinks are great. Our server was very attentive, polite and knowledgeable with the menu and drink options. The menu has a great selection so bring your appetite. We ended up ordering many starters ( so we could try as much as possible 😉) and shared the paella as a main. The mussels were delicious, in a fantastic spicy sauce with bread for dipping. The calamari and Burrata were also good, however the paella was the highlight of the night. The flavors were amazing and if you love spicy, you'll love it! Uli's is very popular in White Rock, so definitely make a reservation and enjoy the experience. See you soon","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPn5grlaSHGu9obKSuCTfrtQh20NQlTYvxYV76&fid=0x0:0x3e5b2d2998e89619"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"Sally","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYjadMy5T259gkmUlT3p9sRdMDrhLZLohAcAX0TlTZ6TSMTtRT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's no wonder this restaurant has received so many positive reviews. Not only is the food incredibly delicious, but the view from the patio seating is also beautiful. The crab cakes are my favorite. Despite being busy, the staff remains very friendly and attentive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXLbIWNJUod9JMhzh_CS2A9Gi0Qt-w0sYfLx3l&fid=0x0:0x3e5b2d2998e89619"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Sepideh S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXePHoGqfjXTu88_zA93ZofNB6PX0pX6RXgoHKgIAA5gbfR0KrP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We visited this restaurant for lunch and ordered Ulie’s burger and a chowder soup. The soup was good however the burger was really disappointing. Considering $30 for a burger! it was really basic. The patty didn’t have any taste, the fries seemed like McDonald fries or at least not in house made. The servers were attentive and helpful though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_UXR7D1Eneb256CMAf6c8Lg8hp8vN0HT8OPmr&fid=0x0:0x3e5b2d2998e89619"],"When":"2024-9-30"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As soon as we stepped foot, we were greeted by a warm, cozy atmosphere perfect for seeking shelter from the cruel weather. The waitress was very friendly and offered us a window seat and hot tea. There was light serene music playing.

The food was nothing short of exceptional. Fresh sushi, perfectly satisfying crisp tempura and the katsu don was piping hot. The pork in the katsu don was succulent and tender, and the sauteed vegetables (onion in particular) were exceptionally flavorful.  Presentation was immaculate too.

Praise be the generous portions meant to satisfy us completely! Even the sushi was much bigger than we expected, to our delight. For the rice bowl sushi and tempura, we had to ask for takeout containers.

I should also emphasize how friendly the service was. There were two servers who were very attentive, they checked up on us frequently and refilled our glasses and cleared our dishes as needed. Their energy set a really positive note for us, we had a good impression of the place because of them!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNhVEanbY9yKQY2xGekCgpzCOSV5v-5FcsAl8p&fid=0x0:0x8d111c26371b8644"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Royal Tigris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9dT9OI5ZBWeJucVykH2fBSMtJafmmvJ3YXKozUmOb-YdJ1U28hw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recommended by friends who frequent this restaurant when in town. Decided to try it out for our anniversary.  Fresh tasting, good quality, and delicious!!!  Ordered the garlic butter edamame - yum!  Also ordered yam tempura, assorted tempura, chicken teri dinner box (good size!), party tray A (also good size), sashimi, and a salmon don. Nothing was left. Kids and in-laws enjoyed every bite. Service was good! We will come again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4cCKKKI5VJ2M5VYf_rSU5J3dpEN0sWnhXt8RE&fid=0x0:0x8d111c26371b8644"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Margaux","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXa0G08qyAdoulkXBjoyRZRQORqJw_tFapZTpYt3D1p3KaOL2eN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had lunch at Nami yesterday and it was really good! [{"Name":"angel lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1IzL3-IELA7R7E3oFObEFF5jKqUJ8mIkFOIr338r21pBTPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a great experience for Indian dinner!
Lots of parking outside the restaurant!

Lots of choices in the menu to choose from

The mango drink was very delicious and the apple cider is yummy as well

The seafood platter with the halibut and the prawns are pretty nice, but they out of the oyster and another kind of seafood

But overall, it is a very good experience in this restaurant with good customer services as well","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_2CYf6x4VAV6d12ZoLLgn-MYP9ScmT3k7dFaX&fid=0x0:0x9871be95d5524496"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"HCS Hui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUsZNlh-z_hRWGZ5_xGZ7jum6_uUQVIV-m5M0kD-rovShQYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a combo platter for $20.99 and a glass of Shiraz, both very good. I had 4 pawns, excellent! My very friendly server told me she’s newly from Nepal and found Halloween and Diwali very interesting. Will be back to try their Biryani.👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHl3I-ys4DpRKyBQ931eptHqpKJIuqijPKl6h7&fid=0x0:0x9871be95d5524496"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Isabella J Rivero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLo4dbx_Xoy4GP6c5W7Y-s2yGL6Hmais3CWAErR_XP8CuHcSjA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So delicious! It was my first time here and I can’t wait to return. I ordered the mini goat combo and everything was spiced perfectly. Some of the best curry I’ve had. Everything was super flavourful. I also had amazing service from Tripti! She was so nice and attentive. I enjoyed chatting with her and she always made sure everything was okay. Thank you so much 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOm_XjsIHQfjV8N-JFh_oN6uDhJzH-K8jkeDiIt&fid=0x0:0x9871be95d5524496"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Jeremiah Aquitania","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlcgxnH1Q3Td2PGfTe3LL27NRMaa_ePQYw_yyw4q8hPVOed0-Eiw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Man their butter chicken is a must! Good portion of chicken cuts inside, and the gravy is so good. The staff is very friendly, and there are affordable options in the menu. I spent 15 dollars total on this. That’s including tip. 😉 Worth every single penny.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMe-SAjQZtPZe18QInDTZFsks-1TaBNt2zigC7D&fid=0x0:0x9871be95d5524496"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Jack Daswani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrk1YrkVQNHfBs6Rf4Sm7Bhk4rWULTfCBi9Ng3-mKeVewTnJo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here many, many times. Have always had Indian food as opposed to the fish and chips which I've heard are also delicious. The Indian food is absolutely delicious and very reasonably priced. It's our go to place when we're too busy or lazy to cook. Service is fabulous. I'm surprised the place isn't busier. Highly recommend it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nikita Kuckian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUenktKqsk6kyHyXReajlMH7lYDK7SyMslvAV5jK0QE6ouiOUUA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Everything we ordered was good except Tandoori chicken. It was tasteless and got no flavour . Service was slow so if you are in hurry then this place is not for you. Our server tried her best as she was only one on the floor.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDv4ysMOk3UnPOGlWz3VtWaHyleaX8TXgFR9ti&fid=0x0:0x9871be95d5524496"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"Vineet Nirmal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocINqe2dpuuXqMxzs7X1lUuzygF65mwQkY40_lDKN-r9WJ-p6RHk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had lunch... Veg Thali... food is very tasty, and the staff is very friendly and communicative and such a fantastic Chef... She is awesome 👌 👍🙏💐
Please do visit... 🙏","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqd8SRLH3i1D5NIQu26EugcJX5EGHJ8PZDkTyR&fid=0x0:0x9871be95d5524496"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Foodieatlarge Ou812!","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUV5WjUsogcvFcdpk650G44_1nDSsUxfDfJjUXorbWVcHcaIaXI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Much improved over previous owners. Fish is now fresh,  crispy and not at all greasy.
Interior has vastly improved.
Free street parking. Decent venue with views but needs brightening up.
Service could be more attentive.
Signage is confusing and nearly absent.
Decent $10.99  Fish & Chips special. Gr8 tartar sauce too.

When in the Rock, stop in.
We will be back.

Appy Trails kids
Brianm

[{"Name":"Wendy Pham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4j2bfPvHmCKcsy9P575jiUCx0xb9EqDRmc2C7wiV1c_3OvLU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Asian style food which a bit different than chinese’s, Vietnamese or japanese. Their dumpling, stir fried noodles, fried rice are tasty. No MSG tastes at all. I love the home style kind of food here. Price is right as well.  Non Alcohol drinks are fabulous. Good Prices for white rock.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMalV7ehrABhxJmv8po88Qkps7-iWUDoxXbLSg1&fid=0x0:0x8ef251cb4464ba6e"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"Britni Pinette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4E1gODd03xvjUy7DJcOO2EHiVqSJS2GAsrRBrHi6SYXM4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came for brunch on a Monday morning. Was nice and quiet and food was delicious! Staff very friendly and beautiful view! We will be back next visit to the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCdjvl92npqkv48N9v5xy5z-ipIVCn--Py1XM&fid=0x0:0x8ef251cb4464ba6e"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"万竹","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnsirj2w9NgKxB4GQZVGrpbGaK60xEpSi0cVmeVC0yEcSSkqbG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here a few times and the nepalese flavors are unique.  Fish and chips are as good as it gets!  Must try momos (nepalese dumplings ).  Also wonderful breakfast here.  Also amazing ocean views!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9DXmL0mYzwy8IflcfDIRI4k01aJKKoYNUGBH1&fid=0x0:0x8ef251cb4464ba6e"],"When":"2024-6-14"},{"Name":"Sankriti KC","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnaoWJjttSoHETnelOLNKZBXLWaZqTA-Kvgmn_BivFUsEOGZLD9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious Nepali mo:mo,chatamari and milk tea. Also loved the biryani with it's own special touch. And great service with sweet views. Second time coming from the States (:
(Just so people know, chatamari is more of a rice flour crepe nicknamed as pizza, not actual pizza)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVm21rPcOmT6CvQb7y1HdT7wDxdYtssbkErT-L&fid=0x0:0x8ef251cb4464ba6e"],"When":"2023-12-25"},{"Name":"Mason Alikhani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoYSc5AKrYCPiMGPOXSUaGALdPIDFeQ80sTBffcQ3TU8d33m90_A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This restaurant was a HUGE DISAPPOINTMENT! We went here for a family dinner and ordered Momo, chicken curry, and spaghetti (for kids). The only edible food was momo. The curry was too salty and came with two small pieces of naan. ($21) kids Spaghetti was unusually sweet and kids only had the toasts that came with it! ($14 each) When I asked the waitress if this dish is expected to be so sweet, she said yes, alfredo sauce is sweet! The service staff, in general, lacked training and didn't know much about the menu.
I went to this place excited as I love momo and Nepalese food but ended up leaving disappointed and hungry! I am honestly not sure how this place has high rating. I doubt their authenticity after going there. Even at time we were there we saw other unhappy customers. Our next table ordered briyani and sent it back after trying one spoon!
I have to WARN everyone: save your money and try something else.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1DjF7qzISDeQEqWC5tUTyg1OFUPiLmAzdBeP9&fid=0x0:0x8ef251cb4464ba6e"],"When":"2024-3-30"},{"Name":"Ramesh K Yadav","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUr5RlL_ZR_RqxN0l0ojgwIoTu9EaQy22NGhHVIFnlBZ47GCMd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I found Warm welcome , MOMO is the most Delicious food here but there are lots of Nepali dishes options available. Very good
Atmosphere and very friendly staff. All the food I tried here was very delicious. I recommend this restaurant. It is a must try place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjoCTw_iLdQvsGw-BnogEoHP4Gjr8lRwznURBO&fid=0x0:0x8ef251cb4464ba6e"],"When":"2023-2-8"},{"Name":"Syd D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxjzsvhO1Bnv6-Vy77MSzLYkzGVsV3CBjXnDfbypIlvvQXbw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The food was so gross we all could not finish our food . Waiting almost an hour for dinner and was not edible , thankful they took the food off , also paid $14 for a mojito and was not good at all also","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXlPZACwjEq-ni_vClA_crHwhUuHpl7qiQkcKn&fid=0x0:0x8ef251cb4464ba6e"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"Aviva Schecterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWp6fbUzx1nn-ecDRbiILcIZG4flp2Q00w_NRktaH99oyOk7oc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I'm actually pretty disappointed in the food for the cost here. We ordered the 5-piece chicken momo for $11 and the chatamari "pizza" for $20. Looking at the cost before coming in, I felt the prices were reasonable for the location and food advertised. The pizza was a thin flimsy flatbread with a few super tiny pieces of chicken on it and spices so we left feeling super ripped off. It tasted good, but definitely not a $20 pizza. If not for this pizza, I would have rated this place a 4 for overall quality and flavor.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN24kGi-F5jKQNEwmCJCc4KfTiGQkd2bmHA86cY&fid=0x0:0x8ef251cb4464ba6e"],"When":"2023-9-17"}]

[{"Name":"Richard the Lyon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKWmV4vMp_e8xsCZSZL3urTGoOZk4NpMl5CyietjN8uuUqTNkREQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My life partner and I visited the Morrison Cafe at the corner of Johnson Road and Pacific Avenue on a Friday night a couple of weeks ago just before Halloween. Boy are we glad we did, Jasmine our waitress to start with was amazing, super friendly and so accommodating for everything and it wasn't too busy so we got some exceptional service not to say that it wouldn't have been that way if the place was full.
We started off with the seafood salmon dinner and a good bottle of wine. The wine was excellent and so was the seafood salmon along with a great solid potato wedges and superbly flavored vegetables, everything was exceptional except for the salmon with the shrimp and scallops was not as flavorful as we would have liked with the dill sauce however it was still very acceptable.
Then we decided to try the two-piece fish and chip dinner and they gave us half of the regular fries and half of the Masala fries and that was outstanding and the tartar sauce was amazing as well. We were full and by then we had been there over an hour and a half and then Abby the owner showed up and asked if we'd ever tried his carrot cake and we are not super big on desserts however Abby was gracious enough the owner to give us a complimentary piece of carrot cake to try and it was truly the best carrot cake I've ever had both of us actually.
It was so good I asked what would you charge for a whole tray as I we were going to a Halloween party the next day.
So we negotiated a great price and I showed up the next day to pick it up and it was actually two full trays we froze one and took the other to the Halloween party and it was a huge hit. Abby even gave me a cake serving knife which I will be returning in the next few days.
This was a truly amazing experience and if you haven't tried out the Morrison Cafe at either of their two locations you're in for a great treat it is not just for breakfast or brunch or lunch please try out their dinner and please see the  photos below.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4V26PqCCYuSqxCfO6saBhsl6zEeOKGN-EoGER&fid=0x0:0xa12c46e871453fb9"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Lelaina Lindsay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6lhE5QzkR1uqsg6IgP5pav-urj0DJqD937D0GKPMoQS-NYgbo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is fantastic, my husband said the best wings he's ever had. My veggie bowl is so yummy and colorful. The price is also so reasonable. The customer service is actually the best part. We had our daughter's birthday dinner with her friends there, and they made all the little girls felt so grown up and cared for. Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMf5zAN5EiNEZYoMfWZz2T7Shs_OiRsP2B0ka1E&fid=0x0:0xa12c46e871453fb9"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Miss Mayette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhoepfdi2GA4VyP2mG3ugg6DC6lF52RgOcoZVf3bT2nvzCZNqx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Have been to the other location in Ocea  Park and loved it. This location is larger and in a much nicer location. I think the menu is slightly different and maybe I just wasn't in the mood but I felt the menu offerings weren't as good as the other location. Food took awhile to get to us (there were three at our table) but the servers themselves were good (we seemed to have at least two or three people so I wasn't really sure which one was actually ours). Overall, it was a nice brunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNybO8sbRiEoAktlJhBdNcxpM7gJYKHlUhoEVAo&fid=0x0:0xa12c46e871453fb9"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Gabriel Radford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRSYSvwmCABbDWhQfEZkLvDWmCXk-0RmDphOBRYYJrA5iwSsm2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Such clearly kind and nice people. Wonderful service. It’s just that it’s expensive and the salad bowl I had was skimpy. The special tacos were much less than 1/2 the price and more than 2x the food. I don’t love healthy penalties and that’s how it felt. I’ll go back for sure and get the tacos.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwLUr9OoeYEnJ-LEhHrF_LJBkRdZOXVrnUSugo&fid=0x0:0xa12c46e871453fb9"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"BG NM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLIgxf3VWTXRdNaR42_xh1VaJ7ACVaPao73t4k_e3RRZMhrg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am all for supporting local and paying for good food, so we were excited to try this new place advertised as high quality brunch eatery. What a disappointing experience. The service was decent. Not her fault but the food was just simply not good. From presentation to execution to the quality of ingridients. Even the garnish was bad quality.  There was stuff on our plate I wouldn't dare serve at home let alone a customer paying top dollar for their meal. Really tough fried hashbrowns with lots of burnt pieces, old rotten oranges for garnish, this slices of deli pressed deli ham, bland hollandaise, bacon was deep fried and so on. A simple place like IHOP blows this place out of the water and that's just a regular IHOP for almost half the price and double the quality. 2 adults, 1 teen and we spent almost $90. Just no where near what they advertised this place to be as a fresh high quality ingridients. We had high hopes but very disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIX7vWKsDVwDmsFBcRiEYPuG9iBrtqR6Mk5qqR&fid=0x0:0xa12c46e871453fb9"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"matt evans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZFke1_kQU1RLy4hb8hBtMhAwtgw4vWjMf-JoDLqOHtuPeGw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I visited on Sunday afternoon and, while the food was excellent and the location is fantastic, I was quite let down by the service. Our server, Archie, seemed inattentive—it took over 20 minutes to get a water refill, which added to my frustration since I had specifically asked Archie to make the food not too spicy, yet my dish turned out much spicier than expected. Great food and atmosphere can only go so far when the service falls short.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"KK G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDkywEHWvk3mlH4bYmyAPGT5kGsdTEiXAEVfULeb5FntaoxJhAXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Morrison Cafe is an absolute gem with a cozy, inviting atmosphere and exceptional service. The menu is diverse and delicious, especially the signature Morrison Breakfast and rich, aromatic coffee. Highly recommend for a memorable dining experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUP9wCf7R97YM2XTY1rLGqYmqle_IceY2sNYa0&fid=0x0:0xa12c46e871453fb9"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"BK12","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1iGczOM8Bx9YxvUjeEQmluiqW0K_6gyY71ziKGv9PWFmsVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We came here prior to ownership change I believe. The food has gone down to crap. The kids menu was so well prior the French toast was on a thick piece of bread now it’s on a thin slice of bread over done. We’ve recently gone to both locations. Same menu, services and prices at both. The hipster avocado was HUGE prior now it’s a thin piece of bread with way too much balsamic & half avocado. For 2 adults and 1 toddler we spent $70+ and it was not worth $10. Never going back to either location. Makes sense the line ups are gone.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Sofia Kingsley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVscMfV773tiAinmQb8EmCQe8fupb_zckAC6DxPMjzxzAvwQEER=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"was very excited to try montgomerys fish and chips after hearing all about it! price is decent, 1$ cheaper than its neighbouring restaurants. size was alright, but they only gave us 1 medium sized piece unlike other restaurants that offer 2/ a giant piece. when we started eating the fish, it was a bit too soft for our liking and the crust and the fish crumpled pretty quickly. the aftertaste of the fish and chips wasn’t the best either, as it left a bitter/metallic like taste. Service was great however, but other restaurants nearby have better fish and chips in my opinion :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKTRU7OOYNKHjl-RsqvwDO-gSsBkGHcPeRDSC0&fid=0x0:0x7454c866ca60bed1"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"Malyss Unomi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFcHkOObfNH-3EATlg4qpCD977HrikpWMqPVtURMfzz0vkSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing food. Frosted glasses. On the beach. Historical mom n pop. Whats not to love. Seriously up your F&C game! No other place in this vicinity even comes close in comparison. Nice light super crispy coating on high quality slabs of white fish. Served on a mountain of home made chips. Zero grease! Not kidding. Not one drop of grease on the plate. Seriously bring your appetite and the whole family. I just cant rave enough! 8m a person who usually might do f&c once a year. At MCL I could eat every week! Oh the cravings....","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZdNj9b_MUEWHvimG7yj85dLU82TAFlx5i9373&fid=0x0:0x7454c866ca60bed1"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"Terry Braumberger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuziWkPSmtFLsonsQrA8jaubopZEPk5Tb0MsabTSm9wiC9b_4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had a great dinner of cod and French fries 🍟, tartar sauce included! Everything was delicious and Cooked perfectly the staff were very friendly and polite. Our meal for three with drinks was $52 well worth the price! I will make it again soon 🔜 on my places to eat in white rock 🪨","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmQ5rt49VJM2O3n4gjo2RyQE1blkYTw8sNtPFt&fid=0x0:0x7454c866ca60bed1"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Jai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjvdj-EkU9IiiNJyRDXvhS8otpXbjfsmZNq51YNNHdoDj3luI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family’s go here very time we’re in white rock. The fish and chips is amazing, and cooked perfectly. The owner and staff is also very accommodating and offered to just fry my gmas fish since deep fried hurts her stomach. There are tables inside and outside to eat, the food is delicious not greasy and cooked quickly! Everyone who has served us has been amazingly nice and welcoming. 10/10.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNisit_awRKUREhyu80g5ilnR5bpRQvYCCBZhvb&fid=0x0:0x7454c866ca60bed1"],"When":"2023-9-15"},{"Name":"Eva Jahnsen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQ-VPnZANRbfE_PVCy_psuHGxXpe1dZA-gRwb0VTXxlwp8Zg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best fish and chips on white rock beach! An awesome atmosphere, and delightful history. The service was great, a group of extremely pleasant teenagers! I quite admired the nice light batter, as I didn’t feel heavy after, which allowed me to have a delicious milkshake with my meal.

I also was pleased with the option to salt my fries to my own personal liking!

Overall a 10/10 experience! Would recommend to anyone looking for fish and chips in the area!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Britany L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2I8TzkDvGJWOyaU7oegyvNeQ0T0PWPZ_qljJoK3TsY6rMuA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best fish in chips in white rock. We have tried them all, the others the batter is thick and greasy but Montgomerys is perfect, light and crispy. They offer salmon and chips which we look forward to every year when we come vacation. Food tasted fresh and delicious.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"TaBo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRKUbkmZ_rq-mSlQpsUZQfDz6N08jBOcGspos2TBoIaPqAYtpk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My fiance and I were vacationing in White Rock visiting my mother and growing up there, I've always loved Marine Dr. so I wanted to give my fiance the ultimate White Rock experience. I took him for lunch at Surfside Grill. Upon entering, your hostess was gossiping with a server and barely acknowledged our existence. The rest of the servers were hanging out at the bar with the bar tenders chatting. My Fiance has managed night clubs, restaurants and bars his entire adult life and this was a huge turn off for him and for me as I am a marketing manager and presentation of a restaurant is everything in running one.Staff should always be aware of this. We were seated at a dirty table when there were at least five clean ones to sit us at. The Hostess didn't even acknowledge it was dirty and left us there. The server came and I had to ask for the table to be cleaned as she just threw down two menus. She then only wiped up the space in front of me and my fiance, not the entire table. A dirty knife was left on the ground and stepped over and walked around by multiple staff at least 7 times until they noticed I took a picture of it, which I attached to this review. The food came out fast, that was the only good thing to say so we could eat and get out of there. The cooks must be fairly decent. The food was good. I had the coconut shrimp and my fiance had the spicy chicken sandwich. Props to the cooks. However, we will NEVER return. The cleanliness was lacking, the staff presentation of the restaurant was disgraceful. Where did work ethic go? If I owned that place, everyone but the cooks would be FIRED. Disgusted with the service. Sad because for the prices we pay, you would think your expectation of staff would be higher. My advice to owners, fire everyone and hire people that value customer service, and treat people the way they want to be treated. PS - I purposely left a piece of coleslaw on the side of the table, when we walked by after we left, the table had been cleaned but the coleslaw was still there. Man, that''s embarrassing for the owners. Management obviously needs to change.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angela Q","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWb_531iDFVKCasGm6UvuKw9uZaENkT6KFE4j7gJIfH4GYfpwM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Not too bad if you always love into Greek meal","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOp6tEXnlKZgi49gyzG0VyWv3HrZN_57nY3bsTI\u0026fid=0x0:0x226105dd2c2286cc"],"When":"2020-7-16"}]

[{"Name":"Aom Hildebrand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqzk0-t2eCJ3dWbzxrmO1EFkEGk94crNKQpEhBC-DrbexpqzAYfw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were beyond satisfied with the service "Neil" Thank you very much for making our first visit very happy. We dropped by after watching the lights so most people were leaving while we walked in. Love the place, love the food and the service. Nice patio even this season. So definitely see you again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNztzETf73hou6q2rABzdFLR4RkPirYCz5HDFYf&fid=0x0:0xa3f248c11c642f72"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Jay A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0RELLdGDmU4mUU2O4splg5RoL3yTJnShh825sqC7IizJnW3IrnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice! Love the place, love the service! This was our first time eating here and we were beyond satisfied with the service as well as the food!

Outside waiting area - Although, I get it, we didn't book for reservation but due to the already tight sidewalk and people are lining up outside either under the sun, rain or snow, really kills the mood. I really hoped the sidewalk area for the push back to the restaurant would be bigger.

Food and service- Try all of them! I am excited to say my family really loved their cooking and the flavours were just tight. Service was a little slow due to resto being full but I really appreciate everyone for trying. Good job on the servers on keeping it cool! :)

Washroom - nope! Not for me. too small and only one person at a time. I understand the place isn't big but, that was not a good experience. Washroom floor was wet. it was a bit dirty altogether.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAZPho9d_SbG-9xRZeEYB4T5vPpRkgkAPUUc_t&fid=0x0:0xa3f248c11c642f72"],"When":"2024-8-16"},{"Name":"Shery On The Move","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmAA3VItm5d-LzZjMzSS_FZs12aHSse1X5w-nXQqVmdbUvhBBJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Date of visit : 28 June 2024 / 8:00pm

I came on a very busy weekend, too crowded and the waiter also didn't do a good service.

Nothing exceptional with the foods that i ordered. I dont mine paying more if the portion of the food is worth the price.  Unfortunately i'm very disappointed with the grilled salmon. For the price ($30), i feel like this a 'scam meal'.  The salmon and other sides were so small. This portion is like a lunch box for our kids to bring to school! *Please refer to the photo i attached.

Personally, summer is not a good idea to come here. In fact this is the first and last for me.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHez7dnHO_LiYpKXm7rYO7ijiDPxFYAVqBon5S&fid=0x0:0xa3f248c11c642f72"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"Troy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIhZurtpkj0z1bBZM75XFlAoZd7Dg4GKtfahXL8UtBigvqrqzc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Mom, partner & I wanted some fish & chips in white rock before we went back home to Ontario. My cousin who lives in BC suggested Charlie Don't Surf because it's right on the water and they had excellent calamari (that we forgot to order). Reviews also looked decent so away we went.

Food: All of us ordered fish & chips with extra tartar. Overall the food was pretty good. I wouldn't say it was my favourite fish & chips, but would definitely recommend it if you are looking for a decent meal.

Service: I found the service a bit subpar on a Sunday afternoon for a popular restaurant. It wasn't overly busy, the outside patio was full but they had plenty of room inside. There appeared to be plenty of employees, but everything from seating, getting drinks & food ordered, to actually receiving the check was slow. Had to request the check after about 10 minutes of having our food taken away. But I may just be an opinionated tourist.

Atmosphere: I loved the view of the water while eating. Even tho we were inside we still had a lovely view with the lovely breeze. Would be a wonderful spot to eat, have a drink and enjoy the sunset 🌇

Overall: I really enjoyed Charlie Don't Surf. Would definitely love to return and watch a sunset or the tide come in and out while enjoying some delicious food. Hopefully I just had a bad service day for the waitress we had.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWb4troud2z39Ak74hKrtupUg2cGEyyqB0O1dC&fid=0x0:0xa3f248c11c642f72"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"ThanhHa H.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9SgyjQ-eUBy_7O_CgcBP4KAU3tbGL9QOkb0R_Pzk8Zsc9Yc-E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great view of the pier!   Foods were decent as we ordered standard items: Blue shrimp pizza, fish & chips & fried calamari.   Fried calamari was served with diced tomatoes and green chive combined together created a very fresh tasty dish.  Blue shrimp pizza was tasty served on a thin crust.   Service was a bit slow at checkout… our server seemed to forget to bring us the bill and to go boxes as requested.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPg_YwhcrEBGBTK7RlGyjVK5Vgym_cGELDdmBZ_&fid=0x0:0xa3f248c11c642f72"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"Charles Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5lZN5knB2qSkj_yit5R1DmMmO9ctZ4Kan_8Aydp5VNcqpbH-R=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"the pizza was a huge letdown. Tasted and looked like pre packaged frozen pizza from a store. Dough was bland, dry, and crunchy. Cheese didn’t taste real. rest of the toppings were also unappetizing. Felt like a serious crime to pay 21$ for it. Rest of the food was alright. don't get the pizza.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyMhd3R_2lD_1oRCfAaGQaobHwu7p_s4anwj-w&fid=0x0:0xa3f248c11c642f72"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Kiera Latajka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZoMZxlaTgoTiuTuemP65yst3xrZiqNAz7ZUP5kGdq69bgb1zu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Coming from Alberta, we had a great time on this beach side restaurant and the staff was super kind and accommodating (literally everyone we talked to, I would add names but all the staff from the evening of July 24th were great and we didn't catch all the names!)

Seriously, the staff was so great and really made our experience!

The food was great and worth the price for sure considering location as well as quality.

We brought our two dogs and the patio was pretty narrow but the staff was awesome and found us a spot we could sit at with the dogs still in arms reach. They also brought us out some water for them which we appreciated so much!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrFA1pdtRxM1xxRU267FxaSzGak_TQAxVG_6U&fid=0x0:0xa3f248c11c642f72"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Look Look","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFnkEC0Vtlns3Rc_vpXyJoBK911s7R33e1juwoNfOw_Qrl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food and service are good!

I sit outside to enjoy the scenery of white rock pier!
Heat is supply and won’t feel cold!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYhcpdQf77msAMy7tZpobAOYrRlur5KORGrn0&fid=0x0:0xa3f248c11c642f72"],"When":"2024-10-23"}]

The service is excellent.   All-day breakfast.   The food is good and reasonably priced for the area.   I will come back here again!   5/5","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuREoMVBPGjZxQj5Y7HG_o_iH6js4x5HdRbBsj&fid=0x0:0x4ec0e5cbf9c5571e"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Leon L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIPVqeMS68EPWMybA4BFjpYJ_UCsZUvdmrDnjNCgOiXZCu4MMU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely homey restaurant. Hash browns are the best here. We don’t feel heavy/sick or lethargic after eating here unlike other restaurants. Nice people as well!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKRT0LUL9Jcn3zqizKVlsgI6O1ln_OVH5ArSW8&fid=0x0:0x4ec0e5cbf9c5571e"],"When":"2024-6-29"},{"Name":"t willis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlefb_jtHTqXks194bsBTasnkX7bwhXMGaXmWdFB6eEODX-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Wonderful spot, very warm and friendly food fresh and arrives at table in a timely fashion. Only one thing is pricey for portion size.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEPJIMrNN2gBNRJekO_t0SWacdsu3gFsqW8ocU&fid=0x0:0x4ec0e5cbf9c5571e"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"Susan H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzyhWUuvO0u5SHQXJCItJV9VkX0Jmt-Ui6-FYM3gaPiKpO1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My place for brunch. Great coffee and best egg benedicts & crisp fried hashbrown, in town!
Dishes are served prompt. There's plenty of parking spaces in the back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaXLdZlzmaAvch2ykwrzb7ybcUDZf4YxLOZXvs&fid=0x0:0x4ec0e5cbf9c5571e"],"When":"2021-12-4"},{"Name":"Sylvia Oppitz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfXwH6yQsaoANozsAxcY4eS-oemDOWR7Ga7ZYxUCtjL7AiXrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been going to Cafe 8 for several years and have found everything to be so good here.  Tracy and Vincent her husband, in the kitchen, do an excellent job in every meal.  It is tasty, home cooked food.  We love their shredded hash browns, delicious eggs and bacon.  My husband always has their Salmon Eggs Benny and says they make just the very best hollandaise sauce around.
Please come out and help support Cafe 8 during this difficult period.  Johnston Road is closed to traffic currently, let's help them   Thank you","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vancitygreen 1","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3jbkrSJncRFiQf2y5C7xDuUa8kr0sgaPANZ6v9uZXBxgMGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in for breakfast had hash Browns were homemade and delicious bacon was Crispy eggs were cooked, perfect. Pancakes were nice and fluffy, my wife also had the BLT, and I tried, it was very good.
Definitely want to come back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexandra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWod6EbW5D4lQiIr-KZpM7_XafS1GjbPyWk8hXBh63OaLnzfHCWEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super cute and cozy cafe for brunch! Actually my #1 favourite spot to go for brunch in white rock. Love the atmosphere and the staff are super nice and always check in on how our meal is going. The owner Tracy, is super sweet, they recognize us whenever we go and always check in!

As for food, their hashbrowns are THE BEST 🤤 they're perfectly crispy especially when you dine in. My favourite to order is the vegetarian house omelette - absolutely PACKED with veggies. You don't have to be vegetarian to love it (though I am). They have great hot or cold drinks too, my favourites being their vanilla iced coffee (in the summer) or hot chocolate (in the chillier days) 😍 brunch dates and family breakfasts here are a must!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQG_Ij8PtsTwgH-rT2JscF5xgD7w1Oo3UCDc1g&fid=0x0:0x4ec0e5cbf9c5571e"],"When":"2022-8-27"},{"Name":"Louise Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_z6sMqang1CZDbe0S_xMm-gRiq53X0Hx33KpfmtkHfVw2nw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just wanted to give a shout out to Vincent & Tracy, owners of Cafe 8 all day breakfast.  I always order the Eggs Benny all day Breakfast with perfectly grilled Bacon and shredded Hash Browns.  Yummy!
I recommend this restaurant and would like to let others know that they are suffering at the moment due to ongoing road work on Johnston Road.  The Road is completely closed to traffic, no parking in the immediate area and access is difficult if you have mobility issues.
This has caused great losses for the businesses affected in the area and Cafe 8 has seen their flow of business decimated in the last few months.
Please make an effort to help this business and the many others affected during this difficult time.  You will certainly enjoy your all day breakfast.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Ess November","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuPJ8X9jOZ2CtOO2jCad-r9UmiPcylLXs6WZsf1PzrAZBsBSHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place deserves zero stars. First off, the waitress was visibly annoyed that we ordered only one dish and drinks. Flavourless and barely mediocre fish and chips in White Rock? Is that a trend? Skip this place and head to Scott’s Landing instead or Cockney Kings. Mediocre food along with the service. Should have walked out after the attitude from the waitress. All in all, stay clear of this establishment. Very strange it actually has a 4 star total review - absolutely misleading!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJN5Jd6lzWlJvIAzU0ZygLZUFzC3iiUrHStFzX&fid=0x0:0xc3d7007cbdf7b37f"],"When":"2024-9-11"},{"Name":"SHERRY WOOLLEY","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLB8AqbYqBRiSEPA5A_PqLi3lEtbgh-MxVobVWIOunijDoyEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Popped in after an event at the walkway. I really enjoyed this pub. The staff was engaging and fun to talk with. The food was excellent. I had the chowder and my wife had the perogies.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVfzfTrq-l_-tuPPzgIRSByvqDskNAiLOtxtLV&fid=0x0:0xc3d7007cbdf7b37f"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Mucahit Mert Alagoz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlZFzlr8OmJ6ReNSeqILjiXkPYOR-Wi6HlJhjaTTE_xGsRl7kohA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm really happy that I discovered this restaurant! From the moment I stepped in, I was greeted with a warm and inviting atmosphere. The exterior decor of the restaurant is charming and welcoming, while the interior decoration is simple yet elegant.

The food is truly amazing! The menu offers delicious and diverse options. I especially recommend the seafood platter. It's filled with fresh and tasty seafood, truly a feast for the senses. Additionally, the meat dishes are excellent; especially the grilled steak, perfectly cooked and full of flavor.

Moreover, the service at the restaurant is great. The waitstaff are extremely polite and helpful, taking your orders promptly and serving the meals in a timely manner.

Furthermore, having a paid car parking space in front of the restaurant is a big advantage. Having such a facility in the city center is really convenient. You can enjoy your meal without worrying about parking your vehicle.

In conclusion, Garden of Flavors has become one of my favorite restaurants due to its delicious food and excellent service. I definitely plan on visiting again and would recommend it to everyone!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3xV91hd8TX0piBdzSU1dtts33NQQWdnOjCd69&fid=0x0:0xc3d7007cbdf7b37f"],"When":"2024-5-4"},{"Name":"Florence","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnC23bKNzD4-mdIoNPkAaCQIQwjnS-wlBLbvPCG_t2uysMrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Arrived at ~1pm; not busy. Server was lovely. Partner ordered omelette & hash browns. It was very tasty. Unfortunately, I ordered the burger & salad. The party was a grocery store, frozen patty….not good. The salad was lack luster at best (I found the butt of the romaine lettuce bunch amongst the leaves) with store bought dressing; very disappointing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Geordie Parker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWerFaB16iY_D7tHGEa6UJLqDQ4NbFV3poN1AAn6ELdRLGqoyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I recently visited West Beach Bar and Grill in White Rock, BC, with my son and a few others. The service was decent, and the overall atmosphere was pleasant. Most of our experience was good; however, unfortunately, my son and I both got minor food poisoning from the 2-piece cod and chips that we shared. This has left me out of commission for the past two days, and I feel especially bad for my son, who had to travel abroad the next day with a very sick stomach.

While this may not be the fault of the server, the kitchen should really inspect the fish carefully before serving it to customers. The other people in our party had the chicken club and chicken strips, and they seemed fine, so it appears to have just been the fish.

I don't want to say I won’t return, but after this experience, I’ll be steering clear of the fish and chips for a while. Aside from that, everything else seemed fine.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lost In A Bookstore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUep-lNAehn1EOil8HFw63ABg9mhtb-nFLLZUFmSP6cakRPKKc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Slower than average service. Seemed only one waitress was working so I can’t be too harsh as she was balancing 5 other tables alongside us.

Drinks were okay, selection is good.

Location is pretty good, but lack of shade for tables outside.

Food was meh, but all we had to eat were fries.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sherrey Alindogan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWp7pl-DCu3BblLZAXhTwV3y_p_n2kCWqibkOcJdmfgtoUKhXG0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My partner and I went for dinner and I really enjoyed the atmosphere and ambience of the restaurant. There also a nice view of the water and you can see Blaine on the far side of the water. Service was okay. The crab bisque soup was amazing and probably the highlight of my dining experience. It was creamy and full of flavour. Lamb shank was soft and delicious, lobster ravioli was very creamy but the asparagus were over cooked (?).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRDQHb2-51uAUN0GsOb9f3dXu-UCU2oe5yptX_&fid=0x0:0xc3d7007cbdf7b37f"],"When":"2022-9-18"},{"Name":"Jeff P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8ANn8aBkavAPNUSgGW1aejBQhwkVOQznVHcMhvjI34G4-HQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Special thanks to Lina for the awesome service, she was so attentive and accommodating. Much better prices compared to others by the water. Great patio and water view!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIzZ7IxZzCPnKIKgtmWOkVvcPkK8YFpnQAuTfB&fid=0x0:0xc3d7007cbdf7b37f"],"When":"2021-9-3"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kwangshin Oh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmURrBfjvjbZeNZTSmNIKU-nwFBIWBf2lmnVvv2AIbeff8kDp9xg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moby Dick is the place to be if you’re a fan of classic fish and chips. Their “Fish & Chips” dish is absolutely spot-on, featuring perfectly fried, golden-brown fish that’s crispy on the outside and tender and flaky on the inside. The fries are just as satisfying—crispy yet fluffy—and the portion size is generous, leaving you fully satisfied.

The casual, nautical-themed atmosphere adds to the charm, making it a great spot to relax and enjoy a hearty meal. The staff are welcoming, and service is quick, so you’ll be digging into your meal in no time. If you’re craving authentic fish and chips, Moby Dick is a must-visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEOn4XxG4nwq_-ISJ9pZo72PzEMuMlxnFEAHQT&fid=0x0:0xb4853871e924d3b3"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"Mori","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzjNclSLYHoLurDMy1z6lBJJfgC1i3gQXUk28JpQQw8EIfuYkF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time coming here, came on a Monday afternoon and we didn't have to wait to get seated, about 30 minutes in, the place started to get pretty busy just before 1pm.  The place is small, about 4 tables of 4 and 2 tables for 6 and is located along the main strip along the water.
Ordered a 3 piece fish & chips, and each order includes an extra piece, so 4 pieces in total for $31.95. We also ordered calamari for $15.95 with 2 steam works brew pints for $7.50 each ($15 total).
The price for the fish and chips was fair and the ratio from batter to fish was on point. Tartar sauce doesn't come with the fish, so a medium size is $1.25 - the tartar sauce wasn't all that great, so lemon and vinegar would do the trick unless it's a must for the tartar. The fries were nice and crispy and didn't come saturated in salt. The calamari was a little over fried, but it wasn't too bad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPl74z9Gtui0mFjN9d3l9JgcDgfSRPtQAFSRFnY&fid=0x0:0xb4853871e924d3b3"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxP-ADvohB6hXpEbci04qD4fdlJ8qjEvYJvIIZqjiOIuWU9BVM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved the cozy marine decor of this place. I’ve walked past this place so many times when I was younger and finally gave it a go.

First off, don’t listen to the people complaining about the batter or the fish to batter ratio. You can see in my photo that the ratio is on point.

Service was friendly and insanely fast. It literally took 3-4 minutes for both our orders to arrive piping hot and fresh. The fries were hot, crispy fresh cut fries and were amazing. Tartar sauce is delicious and they give large portions.

The coleslaw is also quite good and i would recommend ordering that as well to help cut through the grease and balance things out a bit.

Can’t wait to come back! Oh and the portions are generous for the price. Nice to see that in today’s market.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM39yRELY_MQCVDGcvDLAO-8fHRkhbgYqtS3V1c&fid=0x0:0xb4853871e924d3b3"],"When":"2024-8-14"},{"Name":"Somewhere Out There","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxyC1orGEQvfd-l7Mx11h63qB1QAGjP_8-pjtC_UJ7TA0EluWn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"this is our go to place whenever we are in white rock promenade. value for your money highly recommended. staffs are friendly and service is fast. only down side is the limited tables available if you get there on a busy day or you can just do take out and eat by the beach.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPmVsxt4SttmxlZxhujcwQ3tcG8CpyHkomtFQh&fid=0x0:0xb4853871e924d3b3"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Tony","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRg-EL4i5nR0Qm5mWTrzEPyMDUpLpr58BcJtSzzyZvCP7e5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here a couple days ago with a friend and it was awesome. Great portions and you have to buy tartar sauce separately but they are so generous. The waitress was nice enough to let us know the amount of tartar sauce would be a lot and we couldn’t believe the amount they brought to us. Fantastic place for fish and chips.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyPagayiuisVsLo86tAnJZmQjqgIIcCsbG7Z4j&fid=0x0:0xb4853871e924d3b3"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Kab Kbaas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5U0xr3upvQTURbvXCvcu5mgHu9kAs3kt9vv_C4iuqaE8mdtRkEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The total experience was completely enjoyable. This included of course the food, we enjoyed our dinner there at this seaside restaurant.
Both fish and chips were quite enjoyable.
You have a choice of of dining in, or order fr on their take out window.
Cod fish is the only choice for the fish and chip meal.
Thoroughly enjoyed, and will definitely return.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCfsbxSESfA1IRfVBBoZTbT8_WIrtaewhjxSdo&fid=0x0:0xb4853871e924d3b3"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"Devineah Prasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX1DFa9bRk6bvv1_M-orvwe0-273w8OFGry_kkVxXgLnOAtjdI1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I tried this place before, and today was my first time inside the restaurant. The food was really good. I had the fish and chips, calamari, and crab jalapeño poppers. The service was good for how busy the place was. I really loved the atmosphere. I enjoyed decoration around the restaurant. I would definitely recommend this place forfish and chips. Five out of five.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPun76gd20-81dTqVyQ-Nuc86-vLzebw5T_-hvu&fid=0x0:0xb4853871e924d3b3"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Candy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrUMyyWw6hSjujjN69_yuaxt2bZvmrf9-_HvHRZnlaHoFjOHma=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love this space. We always go with Grandma and Grandpa. This year was an extra special visit as you see from the fish in the picture. How perfect haha. Kids love it. Great service this night as well, as always","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6ZBbnvA0SlxcCVEs8tzXL0243ETMQDmdv7DII&fid=0x0:0xb4853871e924d3b3"],"When":"2024-11-18"}]

Ordered mediums and they were super thin crust and the size of a usual small. Got the game day package and they forgot the dips. Ordered for delivery and got a call 25 minutes later saying the delivery driver was busy so could we come pick it up which was not great. Waiting for the to refund the delivery fee as they said they would. Overall not a great first time experience and was super excited to try it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMmuAtB1n83FuBVND9IIqyRsBgsc2-_yoKWcet&fid=0x0:0x206073f21a2e10d1"],"When":"2023-11-13"},{"Name":"Travel Guide","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrp_dLwcToyc2q9H-VMVTm9FHJWqo9MGdEwRe375YZcO0_YjGY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great pizza, and made fast.
