user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ane Strathdee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOlZ1L6DU41aUczU482PdKoXEm0OeL0U4SjOs7WWki0ZC9Hkuu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is our second time dining in here, and we got so lucky to have Helen as our server again! She is amazing, very friendly, professional and offered excellent service. The food always tastes amazing and delicious. The cocktails are amazing and the atmosphere is ok on the floor that we were at. We’d like to try the patio upstairs next, maybe we’ll get an amazing view. Overall it’s a fabulous place to dine in and we absolutely look forward to our next visit. Hopefully Helen will be our server again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_IFU3zWHz1f6nEtWkZrEUrW_JZTKvABmpYQAB&fid=0x0:0x1604547be26888c6"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"christin sebastian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0mvV7FGvaVxE8njIc8STUgT3TU6MKVTNTaYNTtCNK2l4tHIM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I recently dined at the Boathouse in White Rock, and my experience was mixed. The starters were enjoyable, and the drinks were spot on – exactly what you'd hope for at a nice seaside restaurant. However, the mains fell short. While the dish itself was okay, the fried rice was a disappointment; it was underwhelming, though still somewhat passable. The biggest issue was the service time – our food took far too long, especially considering the restaurant was nearly empty. This really impacted the overall experience. On a positive note, the server was fantastic, attentive, and friendly, even though I can’t recall her name. Overall, the visit had its highlights but could use improvements in both food quality and kitchen timing","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQR_nXc5F7YfKkXDmTdtkx0YUL9TVGTKAoNUE&fid=0x0:0x1604547be26888c6"],"When":"2024-10-29"},{"Name":"Geraldine Sangalang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcAsqfNVs6uRfmsJ5FtsU66GdsPGBE4zo_tn8DnG79e7VADqel9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Fantastic seaside restaurant. Comfortable indoor and outdoor seating, great menu, and friendly service.

We tried the mussels, oysters, and ahi tuna tacos. The tacos were my favourite: crisp and light, savory and satisfying. Fantastic on their own.

The mussels and oysters were exactly as we hoped they would be. I'd definitely order them again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRWFXRUG8z7OCg6jIOjq5vjpS9Tef7YDDQorXj&fid=0x0:0x1604547be26888c6"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Lora Janzen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSjM49qR2KGrSRMrTVhWb-mAF1Ln6lYWVpRPHLo9F6dEqoxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely romantic dinner to celebrate our 49th wedding anniversary. Delicious seafood, ordered the calamari with tempura veggies as appetizer, my favourite ahi  tuna tacos with mango salsa and the halibut special for main course. Food was amazing and our server, Helen, was wonderful. Helen, made our evening special with complimentary dessert to share ❤️ Thanks Helen for your joyful service in our special evening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNotb8txSfgvZ41k_gc49MQKsYt1D1zuEKqwwoL&fid=0x0:0x1604547be26888c6"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Kam A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIaThVRJZZnnIukpyacUqIkPMdE_IBDDbi6NLBCpZMHf_Mmvg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Haven't been here in years. Always a great view. Our waitress wasn't super friendly. Also they asked when we made the reservation if we were celebrating anything, and we said a birthday, but there was nothing special done for us. Not sure why they ask? We also told the waitress it was a birthday celebration and she didn't seem to care.
The brunch food was well made and big portion sizes. There wasn't as much seafood selection for lunch and brunch, instead more meat. I just wish they would ask how we wanted our eggs cooked when taking the orders.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nazira Chatur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWR2Ai_tu8Xys-yfjDA3wFYMwRjHmuVeKKzWwh-aq2MAZamw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went for a family dinner and had an absolutely awesome time. I MUST give a shout out to our server Keith!!! He was soooo amazing and made me laugh till I cried!!!

View was amazing and food was great as well. The salads were very fresh, the bread to die for and fish was good!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWIRSfjTjlmbKVFOe9f1GT6xSkeWEJsq1l4Vaj&fid=0x0:0x1604547be26888c6"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Gerardo Arguello","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_gEqSYpuyw_593mBPluD9AYdfZoi5RriJwzpHKFFKeZiFQy8H=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Some of the Food portions too small 🦐 and too expensive and the Drinks feels like water down alcohol.  Food was okay but pricey for what was served.

We had all of the Warm Bites menu and one from the Chilled Bites.

We also order 4 additional Main Menu items, over $300.00 later left with not a good feeling.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNj9stPMQm-7PHsf3l3zULOZGBOYB-8Imv0jWU&fid=0x0:0x1604547be26888c6"],"When":"2024-6-27"},{"Name":"Betsy CT","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQGGIyc_AHsnDVRkUQkbSnV2yECP14J_GFVoTan8z9D8GO3iLAQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We booked New Year's Eve dinners here a few times before Covid because of the nice view and atmosphere, less about the food. For food, we've been going to Sandbar. My friend who lives in White Rock was celebrating this week and she picked this place. I was pleasantly surprised to find food quality has improved since the last time I was here, good flavours and fresh. Our waitress Helen was excellent and all her recommendations were bang on. I had the seafood salad and my friend ordered the Fully Rigged (prix fixe). Both were very good and good value, good portions for the price. Overall, an excellent place to go for a nice meal. I want to return with my husband for Valenitnes, to use my VIP credits and try their key lime pie mmmm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOD28JS8F-UuMk4hG65kyHB_4Oeg66MHZP7M75H&fid=0x0:0x1604547be26888c6"],"When":"2024-11-8"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Yasmine Esmail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEZXBMNTPF4jvg42VCs7awd7M64MsfZxN-AdLy-sBCNVAIaJYSAg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had the most amazing time last night. We went to celebrate our friend's birthday.  The ambience was beautiful.  The customer service was absolutely amazing. If I could give more than 5 stars, I would. The food was delicious.  They played birthday  songs for my friend. The music was foot tapping. I will highly recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoG8ZeiKLGeZFNUEKLmoxDTB_Y4uF66kYt1HbE&fid=0x0:0xcaf510e0d4d1af9e"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Indu Sarpal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4_acp5Qqc-ILbnY4RzcRcTKTYv1QBDhYOsgzc5pBje06tSZA4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Dastaan Modren indian cafe and was absolutely blown away by the experience. From the moment we walked in, the warm and inviting atmosphere set the tone for what would be an exceptional dining experience. The decor was a perfect, seating was  comfortable , creating a cozy yet vibrant ambiance.

The food was the star of the show—authentic,, and absolutely delicious.

The hospitality was just as impressive. The staff were attentive, friendly, and eager to ensure that we had a wonderful experience.
I would highly recommend this place to my family and friends","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRF6FSTCMlHnfchJoIyH1HGuZgE2ZO_UGgneVg&fid=0x0:0xcaf510e0d4d1af9e"],"When":"2024-9-25"},{"Name":"To Michael","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZSnl2VtIk2iqSXyK3X8RiT6ZVa0H1PNK6k19WCAZGzBN4fwcx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I had the pleasure of dining at your restaurant today.
The food was an absolute delight - a harmonious fusion of familiar spices and unexpected flavor combinations. The curry dishes, in particular, the Samosa struck the perfect balance between the authentic boldness of Indian spices and infusing it with a modern, contemporary flair.
But it wasn't just the food that made our visit so memorable. The attentive and knowledgeable service provided by the Chef Mr. Harmeet truly elevated the experience. He was patient in explaining the menu items as well as the cooking style, and ensured that our meal was a seamless and enjoyable experience from start to finish.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMOUplTRw4z-Z04yX8zRSmRDd0Y_n3uNZPXAYVv&fid=0x0:0xcaf510e0d4d1af9e"],"When":"2024-5-30"},{"Name":"Manjot K Dhaliwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVltJ0CHX9LgefyEBj5RAuRhrkCEb6LTN0h0A6parHSDOOeMWGE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Comparing it to the price point and other local Indian restaurants.

Menu: 1/10, nope!!! Just print outs off regular printer, that’s the first impression and I was very disappointed.

I’ve had 3 food items:

1. Vada pao sliders: I would rate 7/10 for this one. It was good, but not excellent. I feel a little bit some flavour would make it better

2. Manchurian and rice combo: 6/10 all because the spice level was way too high on this one. Manchurian is one of my favourite, it wasn’t really great.

3. Tandoori chicken: It was good! 8/10.

The drink I had was Dastaan’s special: 9.5/10 loved it!!!

I might come back but not sure. Great service though, servers were very polite. Food presentation was good as well.

Vibes are good though!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzFwgtN436uiC2cRjZ6fps4wy7VfT3j2LZCr1I&fid=0x0:0xcaf510e0d4d1af9e"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Mannu Batra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKPYroeqtNXQW6pg4A85sKF5LhYmPlzQ5AVRWLKGEWSjjWDw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything is delicious, awesome presentation, great service, beautiful location and inside ambiance. Such a welcoming, friendly and humble owners.. must visit place. One of our favourite places for dine in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNm07vz93Fg-ekQeM19_RpuEiP-g6Poy7qy_Nxf&fid=0x0:0xcaf510e0d4d1af9e"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Isha Bagaria","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpoXBrXfdfF0Wz3jm4-JbGgV9WTX7imS4CoRjuUNwemqNHMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited this restaurant and the girl greated us very well and her service was also awesome! Fish fritters were cold at first but they replaced it. French fries was too good. Overall the experience was good😃","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBWNnyu1rnVz-jEgqlKR610EgCRTwh9Vmu2fdS&fid=0x0:0xcaf510e0d4d1af9e"],"When":"2024-6-30"},{"Name":"Emmanuel Meza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITPvdIXzy_IJ1cLM0ecWmxpqSRSiWDcYUzUQevMtGuGRd3Uw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Went inside very excited but left sadly. Their food was gross subpar. Server was rude at first , they sat us in outside patio . Their patio furniture is old and broken . Our table fireplace was not working, but server turned it on and off even though she knew it was broken before she sat us . Wasted our time , felt bad while my partner was asked to get up twice to fix the fireplace. Their dirty paper menus were disgusting, food and dirt marks all over the menus. One of the menus were about to catch fire while server was playing with broken fireplace on table . I ordered 2 items as course 1 and 2 . While course 2 mains showed up first and appies were still not ready.
Samosa Chana chat was 2 star lacked flavour.
Saag and maki roti was not appetizing at all  , it was salty while the maki ki roti was actually not maki but a mix of besan and other flour . It was served in old English skillet probably from old business. Server ignored us for a long time after we were done with appetizers as we send our mains back at first . Probably she was pissed off .
Owner was nice , as he understood the concern, but their staff need more service training in order to survive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwW-PbGwv3hv-NYzx2W53y1RJIvQ9VhS9T-yPi&fid=0x0:0xcaf510e0d4d1af9e"],"When":"2024-10-2"},{"Name":"Jyotsana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhM9MGRK0Ro0cqK-HkNY2GsfiHBnkrDRqV7VffENp2guUmwUcTLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at Dastaan with my family. Their patio setup is beautiful and faces the water. The owner, Vishal, ensured that we received a top notch service. The quality of the food is unbeatable. Everything was fresh & perfectly flavored. We were recommended to try the Dastaan special drink ( Mojito) , Fish tikka and the chicken tikka, Vada pav slider & pani puri. All the dishes were well prepared. We definitely coming back. White rock area in general is lively. I find the location & food make it worth a visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBBqcfmKsuqUpvaYT57YQQSWyq-6G4SWG9f64T&fid=0x0:0xcaf510e0d4d1af9e"],"When":"2024-6-29"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Tannis Zboroluk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9FnlGDpKGSy_fc09OaANTBleqoD1NZSVbHGCdZN42Oaf5NA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely delicious! I’ve always loved pizza and after turning vegan 13 years ago, I have missed eating really great pizza. This is my first time trying Damianos but unless I drop dead within a month, it won’t be the last.  I ordered the veggie (minus pineapple) and subbed vegan cheese and, really, it’s been 13 years since I’ve had a pizza as good as this one, and I’ve tried vegan restaurant pizza many times before. I make a vegan pizza that I thought couldn’t be beat, but this one beats it. Pizza may not be the healthiest choice, but if you’re going to indulge, try Damianos. We did a pick up order. My mother and brother shared a regular special pizza (this is my brother and his wife’s fave place for pizza) and they both thoroughly enjoyed theirs as well. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vancityzee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNIEIOxwS1qZ-60KEcYgzZC0RO_ryd-f22jddJDy8o5SEJFmdp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at Damianos Pizza \u0026 Pasta! The pizza was absolutely delicious, perfectly crispy crust, fresh ingredients, and flavorful toppings that made every bite a treat. The staff were incredibly friendly and attentive, making the expierence even more better. Highly recommend this spot for anyone craving great pizza and amazing customer service in white rock.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"py0413","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhqvwQrQBP1Ho2kEoDqZgSrifkk5JwGR5lNkcGFu5IU-p8UTjq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thumbs up for these guys! 👍👍👍\n\nIt’s our first time having their pizza. Absolutely delicious. We ordered 2 medium size House Pizza. Not only they offer some of the best priced menu, their pizza are full of good quality toppings. Very flavorful, very tasty, and very satisfying. We can’t wait to return and try other flavors.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeZmitYZ3nB7dDUdNL1NVMupSlp-8w618K0iKl\u0026fid=0x0:0x3c9e8a70d9fc7543"],"When":"2023-3-10"},{"Name":"Byron O'Neill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXuTZWN9SfLcq8rbH3ka6iia8Us8645B7OUTGPYfhUaFd2aA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"So I ordered for the first time about a week ago. It wasn’t cooked right. Doughy. I was quite impressed that the owner reached out to me. He wanted to make things right. Which tbh is quite impressive. And the second time was very good. Lots of quality toppings. Not greasy. Just a good flavourful pizza! Definitely a place to check out if you are looking for good pizza. Thanks a bunch! Will be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rick Grant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJOmVIpO90wl-bxaW0v4Cz_ANzXaOZaFMI6DLTbYpyVDcJknw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This was the worst meal I’ve ever had. Chicken souvlaki was extremely dry, only had 3 small pieces, no skewer- I think it was just boiled. Very bland and had an off smell. The rice was mushy and has little to no flavour. Even the tzatziki was watery.  The only thing I ate was the pita bread and everything went straight into the trash bin. I would NOT recommend this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2sZmbY2f1h-6FvfKW7KU_KzsRB1TwxW4gHJch\u0026fid=0x0:0x3c9e8a70d9fc7543"],"When":"2024-3-7"},{"Name":"Jeff Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXe5nXixN6LLMXauv4eW2sb8SyPzqYhkDWNGQ7d1dOWCQtqdpH6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious, hand-made pizzas with perfect crust and fresh ingredients. Has a nice view of the waters from the street side tables. Food was between average-good. Ingredients are fresh, but lacks uniqueness when compared to other seafood restaurants in the strip. We had the Captain's Platter and Fish Tacos which had generous portions. Unfortunately, they ran out of mangoes for the fish tacos which they told us about soon after ordering. We'll try this place again given their reasonable prices and quality food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKphTAEPwWSpW7Gg5Mgh9JSd4NjSkULrRp1mb2\u0026fid=0x0:0x36c99e12f0a40d02"],"When":"2017-10-16"},{"Name":"daveyb98126","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWKb9pyDzbo_yXTTCzLhDTAXkXAVT1nZ6moYVMdoT_IYD73ws6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An owner who genuinely cares about customers and the food. At first, we had to wait so the deep fry oil could be changed out. How many places even do this? Thank you Fishboat! The taste of your fish (we picked cod; they also have halibut) was exceptional and the fries portion was generous for the 5 piece family menu item. Seating away from the sun was much appreciated and yes, we rewarded ourselves with their organic ice cream. Highly recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhGHpsaonDwsKBmsuKIG2zzZdX6uHI0swnI584\u0026fid=0x0:0x36c99e12f0a40d02"],"When":"2023-8-9"}]

The vibe here is so laid-back and welcoming, making it the perfect spot to relax. The couches are super comfy, ideal for lounging with a coffee or enjoying a meal. The staff are incredibly friendly and attentive, really making you feel at home. And the food? Absolutely delicious – everything is fresh, flavorful. Definitely a five-star experience all around! I can't wait to come back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Denver Eddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0z5fqO3QmTRVVYQXXArJwmy2ttspO-kQwTiVAzYhXiOhvTw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Aside from lovely coffees and treats and snacks, my experiences here are always uplifting. I'm a little scatterbrained so when I forget to ask for oatmilk, at least one of the baristas will come up and ask if I want it. It's little things like this that make a cafe feel like a community space. Thank you to all the kind and helpful staff here 🤙 also the chocolate macadamia nut latte is delicious I definitely recommend it","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMS7l7VvSsnjS3NsAYvcoW-xZJA2EIKUMNFHM1X&fid=0x0:0xccaf50df2411c221"],"When":"2024-10-29"},{"Name":"Cynthia Jia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-m436tQWdJnnH0jkC_WxxnkredmQg4cwhEVOq0qzHQqwCGhZGHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really cute cafe with yummy bagel sandwiches and smoothies! The big kahuna sandwich was 👌👌👌 and everyone was so nice :) Definitely recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPW4gM-_LegcdWOp0qbQXdWOeBEJtSkUMl2AK6u&fid=0x0:0xccaf50df2411c221"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"Gabriel Radford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRSYSvwmCABbDWhQfEZkLvDWmCXk-0RmDphOBRYYJrA5iwSsm2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The perfect neighbourhood spot. Great people. Good prices. Tasty food and coffee. Had a smoothie one day and a breakfast bagel the next. 10/10.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWnYgORIRJkqns1hD0JzNV1bS3KJeacqknwu8w&fid=0x0:0xccaf50df2411c221"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Mckenna Christine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoQHUOXUDaEhthxRrciZoqCJQg-H_1WzTnV2J0BLK1f8cbMS1y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I keep trying Islands and their different locations because I really WANT to like it, but I always find I’m disappointed. Especially with the drinks.

I actually really like their food here, of what I’ve tried. I’ve gotten the Mana bagel before and it was actually REALLY good. I was surprised how good it was given how simple it’s ingredients are. I also really like their poke. I’ve heard a lot of complaints about it as it’s not like “sushi poke” you see at a lot of other restaurants, but it’s supposed to be like traditional Hawaiian poke which I personally like a lot more.

Back to drinks… I tried a smoothie one time, I forget which, but it was just okay. Nothing better than I could’ve made at home for half the price. $10 for a smoothie is pretty steep, although I do understand they use fresh fruit.

Their matcha tastes… really bad. It tastes fake. Like very low quality. It tastes like it has a lot of fillers rather than just being a pure ceremonial matcha. And the fact that they advertise it as “organic matcha tea” makes you think it’s going to be really good and authentic but it’s just not. The colour is also a lot paler and yellow-green rather than the bright vibrant green you see in high quality matcha.

I’ve also tried their iced chai recently and it tastes good but not great. It’s super heavy on the cinnamon flavour. Chai is supposed to be a mixture of many different spices but it literally tastes like straight cinnamon.

Btw I find $1 extra for non-dairy milk super steep. Even a giant like Starbucks who gouges every cent doesn’t charge quite that much. I could understand $0.50 or $0.75 but a whole dollar is a lot for the tiny bit of milk you end up pouring in most drinks.

Staff are not friendly at all… no hello when you enter, no goodbye when you leave, even when they’re not busy. They don’t smile or tell you to have a good day when you grab your order, they’re not personable or chatty at all. And this isn’t just on one occasion, this is every time I’ve been in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuLdeeWLmyyn2-ZpjB-u96n1MvuwrMiST27Rf9&fid=0x0:0xccaf50df2411c221"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Dianna Filippelli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXz9XTsXE656tR16KgQZkN5rtINQZWCn27_tgMcMaIxSERt0meg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Surprisingly, I have never been to this location despite vacationing and living down the street. They don't overtly advertise, with extensive signage. Perhaps, this is unnecessary because the cafe has a unique theme and ambiance.

My order is always the same, so I've been able to compare the quality, presentation and taste in different locations. The White Rock site, definitely met my expectations for the aforementioned. The acai bowl both looked and tasted appealing. Moreover, the machiatos are made the European-way, simply with a dash of milk and shots of espresso . This enables you to actually distinguish the flavor of the coffee
rather than the milk. Some Western cafes struggle with this concept.

Hence, I was delighted that I didn't have to educate or train the staff on the creation of these items. I will certainly return here more as a local. Thank-you for this excellent experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQeFTTiCIrZEgAgiVzJu5ezi8vDhRcLK34jkhg&fid=0x0:0xccaf50df2411c221"],"When":"2024-7-31"},{"Name":"Kitty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhMuwg_tl1TRTc24JxH5iTo3OJVTHqCQijM2P6PldLkYJ1Idkn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great coffee shop. The palm tree latte was very yummy, I got it half sweet and it was perfect!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyTYWq221tWesJEkmKI7bZD6qsGJ8vuHIehxDu&fid=0x0:0xccaf50df2411c221"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Harmeet Bhatia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNnAl78AOIxyt7c4IFDfDZa6TPcOoOsagwed_PuJK-JO6EfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for a brunch with my son. Island cafe you are my new favorite place. Everything is just so right, the staff, the food and most
Importantly the store arrangement. We ordered the Big Kahnua Breakfast Sandwich which was just amazing. We also got Honalua breakfast sandwich which my son also really enjoyed.
Additional note for awesome staff, I ordered iced vanilla bean, but got the hot one instead. The staff didn’t blink and gave me a new one.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9kcgxs6Bu3mQANZl0Wob5hSXx0KLkFTNj2uu7&fid=0x0:0xccaf50df2411c221"],"When":"2023-1-16"}]

[{"Name":"Mehak Arora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0qgdzw12xvrqEXZSttuHOY2Q3LwS_fhvaqB0eIOFtEDvpmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"First time I have ordered the food and worst food I have ever eat. All the tandoori roti was topped up with vegetable oil and all black. I understand tandoori leave black rust but never turned out all black. My hands were black. Dal makhni was so bad that. Lol part When i opened it and said is it dal makhni or shahi dal makhni. My family laughed😂. We also ordered vinegar onions rubbish. Sirka onions are never like this. Restaurants dont serve like this and way too expensive. Certainly not coming back to waste my money.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwrUHgQd695IM5rNt-2PXTCRWHBjWSgBabOa1e&fid=0x0:0xac043873730d0e87"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Ani Sandhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUd72X5OfyskatngImckkRe6wxbEzaOGbYq9pnx02eSncTLA3naA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"really bad service we guys have been waited for our from 1 hour and they gave us half of our order we guys are waiting for bread.
really very bad service please do not visit this restaurant👎🏻.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRE6xIgqTG4t6zkMFldxBGgvtUYWHnkw_OM5al&fid=0x0:0xac043873730d0e87"],"When":"2024-12-25"},{"Name":"Sagar Aulakh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLg6mcVhQKfKobV554h56mIRmrM465wvK3JFR9QdL95CIWYugI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Could have given them a 5-star rating if I was reviewing them 5-6 months ago. But these days their service and quality of food are getting worse day by day.
Last month we ordered white sauce pasta and 2 kulad chai. Pasta was barely enough for one person (less than half a bowl). And chai was without sugar and only Splenda packets on the side. When I asked them for sugar for our chai, they said they were out of sugar. Also, the chai was ice cold. It looked like they made it in the freezer, not on the burner.
Today, we ordered just 2 kulad chai again for takeout, and she said it will take 10-15 minutes. But, she brought it in just 2-3 minutes, and no surprise, it was without sugar again (with Splenda on the side). When I asked for sugar again, she said they are out of sugar. Like seriously!!! You guys are running a restaurant, and you are out of sugar from the last couple of months. Also, chai was again ice cold.
Just a suggestion for you guys: please rename it from kulad chai to iced chai with Splenda for the sake of customers.

serve Large, extra sauce, light on the cheese, pepperoni, onions, pineapple, jalapenos... Well done and square cut.  Simply... delicious!!!
Always makes my order correct. Even when there was a glitch with the promo code, they were able to credit my account right away. This location is great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"tarun chaudhary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9GVirq62qmMi23hxKF3aGT1JM9Y_jqZGxRVNQty3XAlv59g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve thoroughly enjoyed Freshslice Pizza’s Veg Pizza every time I’ve visited. The crust is light and crispy, topped with fresh, flavorful veggies like bell peppers, onions, and olives, perfectly balanced with their tangy tomato sauce and just the right amount of cheese. The store’s welcoming ambience, with its clean and friendly atmosphere, makes the experience even better. It’s always a pleasure to stop by and savor their delicious pizza!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raymanjeet Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL7k6Yey1tO88QSlBuZRAQ1B-k4JUez9kvCudUu7Gl0ySksEf4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently ordered 5 pizza from Freshslice Pizza while visiting Peace Arch Park, and it was an amazing experience! The delivery service was smooth, bringing our order right to the park. The pizza arrived hot, fresh, and ready to enjoy outdoors. The crust was just right—crispy yet soft—and the toppings were generous and packed with flavor. It was the perfect addition to our day at the park.

We really appreciated the convenience and quality of the service. The delivery driver was friendly and punctual, making the whole process seamless. Enjoying that delicious pizza in such a beautiful setting made the experience even more memorable. Highly recommend Freshslice Pizza for both the food and the service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karim Haddad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUSwfr_7-xKEIBWH6WVrAtUnOZDhEHDPlJjWk4yDy6W1EJWcBB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly and happy staff!  It is so refreshing to walk into a business and to be greeted with such enthusiasm!  This is very rare today!  They made my day better just by coming to this great pizza place!  I hope you open more locations and start a movement of enthusiasm that is so needed especially in Vancouver where most places I go to treat me like a number.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kaurpreet Preet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUzOcg1yP-XDk49F5FYhV357rBwH743dgYm-KFZ2qw7nycZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience! What truly stood out was the personal touch whether it was the thoughtful small talk, the constant refilling of water glasses, or the genuine smiles from every team member. It’s rare to find a restaurant that makes you feel at home while delivering such a polished level of professionalism.

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"ella bak beauty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDdLruNlUssQ7xZo-1immi2cr3tCI-_0Id8k1HcAXfbAXSqoW8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently had a terrible experience at this restaurant. I ordered a Greek wrap, and the chicken had a foul odor. After eating just half of it, I felt nauseous and later experienced food poisoning. My family also ordered waffles, which were cold and turned out to be store-bought, even though the menu didn’t indicate this. It felt very deceptive to serve store-bought food as fresh.

Charging $15.79 for store-bought waffles is deceptive and misleading.
While we received a refund for the waffles, I was refused a refund for the Greek wrap, despite the obvious issues with its quality. I reached out to the restaurant to resolve the matter, but they have not responded.

The combination of serving smelly chicken and store-bought food while ignoring customer concerns is extremely disappointing. I do not recommend dining here, and I hope they take steps to improve both their food quality and customer service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuJ1KN94HEZU8kIDgX03VUdq9v_gfSnrVRE4Ia&fid=0x0:0xe180a1375fe7592"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"x80WildCat08x","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKb8Lw-7G_CRLEv8baur6SEG2bz5BMY_zAhSXcbvYswJmN_lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was disappointed with my visit. The $15.79 waffles were just store-bought, covered in excessive whipped cream, and didn’t match the “freshly baked” claim. The chicken wrap was inedible and made my sister sick. While they refunded the waffles, they refused to address the wrap issue. Overall, poor quality and overpriced. Wouldn’t recommend.

Also, the review rate is higher because it used to be Watts cafe, and owned by someone else who had integrity when it came to the quality, taste and the price of food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMilyWCfxtl-9fYo6nyLti1OMADEHvQouMI10k&fid=0x0:0xe180a1375fe7592"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Jack Peters","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6tuotdk1_dATGiaaY-PEJ7e94vRmmulQ4gtBej1xawfyQQRAu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I still like this local family business. Lately I had the fresh baked warm muffin & another time the banana bread. Leaving my previous kind words review... place for coffee and a cookie. Great sheltered seasonal patio. As I've said before "The new open/close patio is very impressive, fresh and clean." Finlay's Happy Hour w/large selection of beer or alcohol drinks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPioSj0XKZ8c56PIszwLUaqB1i7BF2T1kHnxHus&fid=0x0:0xe180a1375fe7592"],"When":"2024-10-31"},{"Name":"Christine Lewis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKfYBZs46slkf_04ulYGW9g34olC-cqprVHzp0zZHCXKzE121y9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"On December 7, I was here and had a delicious soy latté and a breakfast wrap, which I enjoyed outside on the heated patio right across the road from the beach. This was the only breakfast place with a view of the ocean. Although it was a cloudy day, it was heavenly being there breathing in the salt air with my daughter (she loved her smoked salmon on a bagel with cream cheese) and my granddaughter. The staff were very quiet but polite and professional. I hope their business keeps going strong. I look forward to returning and highly recommend it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIf8_ZRDsAFJABvAZNDThvatEdsE2Q0ubcY22D&fid=0x0:0xe180a1375fe7592"],"When":"2022-12-31"},{"Name":"Daniel Wilkinson (dwilks23)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmF_9Nv6fYw6dJAgceWdRVHn8731nPn03zPDyTI-g6P-CHrHlL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Walked in and were one of only 4 others in the whole restaurant. Waited abnormally long time for order to be taken as workers seemed to be puttering around like we were not even there. Ordered cafe con pana (espresso with whip cream). Used old ground  flavoured coffee, not espresso grounds, coffee tasked awful and cost more than Starbucks which is saying something. Lots of potential based on location but as is would not return.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kellan Ferencz-elder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIomh-rWaS_ouHYMTMAgihKnll3MvtCmjpUCHTpmC-4YY5Mbg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food is good, service was not great. Ordered 2 ice coffees and a sandwich. Tried to confirm two ice coffee a couple times and thought she understood but she left shortly after taking the order. Only received one ice coffee and was having a wrap made instead of sandwich, just an mis communication I think, was fine to have the wrap either way. I said there was supposed to be two iced coffee and she said no you didn’t order two look at the order. I said I did and you didn’t even take my order and I did order two. I said it’s fine I will get another iced coffee and she said I have another order you can wait. We left. Won’t be going back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katarina Konstantinovic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqvMqGNC44wVdGlIhtKTTxfCVm8U7SX-PltUMmWhLVuooGkf0Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Simple, little cafe with self service, and a good bite! You order at the counter and the food is brought to you. People staying at the hotel above it comes down for meals, which makes it somewhat international :) We had breakfast there, which was simple, but good and filling, and definitely enough to keep you going for the day! Would recommend it. Good spacing on patio with tables so it's comfortable and not cramped, and has outside heating. Also, scones are OK!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsasXKKL1PuqaNrKXJSXibokISgnapDQj3uAtq&fid=0x0:0xe180a1375fe7592"],"When":"2022-4-16"},{"Name":"Kevin Skewes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUI51Xj5hAveav-pmhM9Lb6nsvSWgMx8Fv_bwSorvXAk8tOwlB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great location and atmosphere, don't expect a server at the table though, this is order at counter only. They also have a full selection of alcohol on display, but when I asked for a mixed drink with Grey Goose, which I could clearly see they had, I was told they didn't have any. I pointed at it, and it was at the end of my fingertips, and the girl still didn't appear to understand 🙃","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Ali Naddaf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzP_43VhVJ37G6Qo5Vhw5j1kr89rDFzpw7Pp-6VP6xhoGuU8nI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was our second time here and we loved the food and service. I got the chicken schnitzel and my wife got the grilled chicken ciabatta and we were both satisfied with the quality and portions.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3LyuQ0IeX2shUmLns-6Qk5Twqn1cyZWx9qIUa&fid=0x0:0x87fbfcc3c4a774f1"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Malyss Unomi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFcHkOObfNH-3EATlg4qpCD977HrikpWMqPVtURMfzz0vkSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Its ok. Extremely overpriced for breakfast. Brekkie should NEVER cost $30. Especially if its mostly carbs. All of the brekkie meats are pork. Sad. Otherwise its nice... 50s/60s living room feel with chrome leg tables and a nice lounge. Always tables free. Outdoor seating available. Licensed. Happy hour  2 til 6 daily.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbwhewzj6hVA_LKt3RGd4hBmvExmH9J7UwpoEO&fid=0x0:0x87fbfcc3c4a774f1"],"When":"2024-9-4"},{"Name":"Tim The T00l Man Gardener","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBqSx9cr1tBlZT5Mp-2Z13nvebib1ALqcfn4j0iK2O_tGB9eE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It's not what  it used to be. Last time I came here was roughly 11 years ago, and it was excellent. One thing I notice in the reviews is the quality and high ratings for breakfast, which is what I remember being very good. Maybe I'll return and give the breakfast a shot, but dinner was honestly deserving of a refund. Gordon Ramsay would have had such a red face with steam coming out his ears.

One thing positive is our waitress was very good. Great service and energy. 👍 Probably a good place to go for breakfast with the family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"WILLIAM REN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKRmqUVmhhErGGqKi-Bzn0et1-EnBX9lgvZO2NQ0f1pzZpZEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Roadhouse Grille has been in Peninsula Community since 1997.
I have been here with my family or my friends here over 10 years. I enjoy the delicious home-made food and great service, especially the atmosphere with a variety of room and decor. I love all the foods, especially the award-winning King George Beef Burger. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYb5Vds22bOtaBLaxVHMmYwYlShyKkoI7yMZrQ&fid=0x0:0x87fbfcc3c4a774f1"],"When":"2024-4-18"},{"Name":"Daryl Snell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkLKaiQpognVlGgjL8SLgMW5-fyufaPXN_IojvO2zeUkO0PeIp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got there a bit late however we were welcomed with open arms. Ribs were a fraction overdone for me but still very good. A friend had the Lasagna which was great. On the table was a burger and Yorkshire pudding prime rib with mash and gravy which was excellent. Lots of meat..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOr6cYavZ6MEww3xrqXATjiVfkpDi5qsXLKZjMy&fid=0x0:0x87fbfcc3c4a774f1"],"When":"2024-1-4"},{"Name":"Miguel J.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvFKKyw6Zz6cZM3bYhyRix8dzFrproaGAy4C3ZnwOLkIFumger=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I went here for a brunch date and it did not disappoint. Look, the prices are on the higher side but they make up for it in portions. Very generous portions. I would consider this place a gem in South Surrey.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPh9sj4WzWMFeN6VqNAU1VGIfcZ4H7n5O17vwoN&fid=0x0:0x87fbfcc3c4a774f1"],"When":"2024-1-13"},{"Name":"Tamara","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYpIOv6JR4yTsTnowi0aUt_2H5BIvtXoxwU_IFXgckmNpTCPk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I love this place. It’s a bit pricey but worth it because we’ve never been disappointed the in food. It’s always fresh and loaded with flavour. The servers are always friendly and it has a nice atmosphere.
The breakfast and coffee is especially delicious 😋","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AW","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVHql0MQe2Rgqo2NRgodyekiurZCtKEBtFXXT2sANqxQPhOBgVSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the cozy environment and old school decor vibe. Breakfast is excellent and service is top notch. Treasure cave is awesome for kids - one free toy each! Well worth the 30 minute drive to get there. They were very busy this morning and it seems most if not all customers there are regulars!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWnBReGS5rGXrJ7gomxeYdqiA8TODQEpj4BVvu&fid=0x0:0x87fbfcc3c4a774f1"],"When":"2019-7-25"}]

[{"Name":"Gazal G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNfRt6AYTRne5R5YyIlS82FlCPvw6yjMF8Wl3AyoUgCtB2w_8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"In my opinion, this restaurant deserves a 4-star rating. The food tasted good, but the portions were small compared to the price. However, I would rate the decor and ambiance at 2 stars. It felt like I traveled back in time to restaurants from 30 years ago!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVWy3sfwoXm1utsQc_cnXQrDj0T6rYGotq-uVT&fid=0x0:0x79f84014a6cbb9f8"],"When":"2024-10-29"},{"Name":"Sid Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKI2bIXmjxisLX5k-tksyfAVrfiduLeS2Y0yeu3bZezto2_sQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried White Rock Indian Flavours in Surrey for the first time and wasn’t disappointed.

Ordered Dal Makhni & Paneer Bhurji along with some Tandoori Rotis, Butter Naans & Laccha Parantha from their menu for takeout.

Both the dishes were delicious and well made. They looked appetizing and the quantity was good as well. I felt that the Paneer Bhurj was missing a bit of salt but that was fine. It was also priced a bit higher and there was some hair in it.

The tandoori rotis were hard immediately after I returned and opened the packing foil but the butter naans and laccha parantha were okay.

I had asked for some onions and green chillies on the side but the green chillies were not fresh.

Overall, I liked the food and would definitely recommend trying this Indian restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOClSeJWAF5Wl9qRs0bA0ujgEMXjxCxpf_244Q&fid=0x0:0x79f84014a6cbb9f8"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"Zeeshan Sohail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQzSgXcEIo5d0fY039IL3LLi7k1i-9eyjB9u0xnur9BQekUdtD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little place for some of the best vegetable samosas and chaats.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8Ir_nuo2lPjS_N1ExqujvDUS_xpcPirKKf7nK&fid=0x0:0x79f84014a6cbb9f8"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Harish N V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWM2JgJ-Uqa_YnUvHB1Xf8jTDDcKLZrnGW-T4Z4M-rQ04WxUyDk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I visited here for lunch with family and friends during my long weekend trip. Ordered tandoori roti, chicken tikka, fish and chicken pakora, chilli chicken dry and veg noodles. Chilli chicken is the top hit with amazing taste. Both chicken and fish pakora tasted decent. Chicken curry flavoured awesome but not happy with the tandoori roti. Roti’s were not fresh and hard. Vegetable noodles is average as it tasted bit spicy and didn’t had any authenticity in it. The service is good and the waitress is accommodating. Ambience needs to be improved. I am overall satisfied and will visit again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqNx_VKT7Skr3MHuSkXSNKQWOveFan5DciQnL7&fid=0x0:0x79f84014a6cbb9f8"],"When":"2023-9-3"},{"Name":"Linda Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtIFngKmQt2Nbl9kPzBVTsvrnb2HJS3_cPEQL2WcV5IEApQE_J=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Our first visit to this restaurant. We ordered the fish pakora appetizer, lamb vindaloo, lamb korma, white rice, vegetable biryani rice, and garlic naan. Everything was really good. The lamb dishes were exceptional. We ended up with leftovers of course…and that was intentional.
A young woman waited on us and she was very sweet. We felt well taken care of.
We ordered a 1/2 carafe of wine too. Small wine list but good choices.
This a small place with booths. Casual and comfortable space.
It’s great to have this dinner or takeout option so close to the U.S./Canadian border.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwV62hFkDlou58Dr2MR2newHikEXSLz1Odqvqv&fid=0x0:0x79f84014a6cbb9f8"],"When":"2023-9-27"},{"Name":"Sunrose Heer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJFBfNTjugoIKm8c6Ys0-nqw6yBMTaOT-HKQhTConlr_gi5eDc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered honey chilly cauliflower and fish pakora as starters, and they were super amazing. Kadahi chicken was normal, not too bad, and not so good. The staff was good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeg_SUQLsmt-_0B_Wrqr3mm6ExASfzaLzS2Doz&fid=0x0:0x79f84014a6cbb9f8"],"When":"2023-5-7"},{"Name":"Anik Roy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5UPl4nGTRKC4BUqsGPxQyotz2dSHdhLtrTYELrYJ5nidJARyp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good food!
Went there after the kitchen closed, still they agreed to take the order.
Chicken Biriyani and Chicken Fried Rice.
Taste was amazing, just felt a bit oily - otherwise really good.
Would surely visit again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"PC Experts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMb8bSV9UMC1oG0k1qKZ_D1Qf15c14AG4IDwm0IqGuQtomutfH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered the non-veg Thali with lamb, it was excellent. I ordered it with mild spice, and maybe next time I'll ask for medium. Service was fast, and I got more than I could eat. The atmosphere is casual, but very clean and inviting. I liked this place on my first visit, and shall definitely be coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXPp6GJIyZHsnG8p49WTebxZ4SwslYvf-SIwTu&fid=0x0:0x79f84014a6cbb9f8"],"When":"2023-7-4"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Madison G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtZsEld-Yz5a2Swm5LesjF83lo03ZXPGgujeQvQiLn6WLaIuGx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I went to Laura’s Coffee Corner for brunch, and I was impressed by the huge variety of food options, both pastries and meals. I loved that they had seasonal drink options as well! I ordered the grilled cheese, but it was pretty plain; they used sliced cheese instead of grated, and the bread was very dry. I’d love to see some butter or extra cheese on the outside to enhance it. On the bright side, the drink was delicious, and I appreciated that they used people's names to avoid confusion with orders. One downside was finding the door to the place; it was a bit tricky, and if it wasn’t for a local, I don’t know if we would have figured out how to get in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBOYf48FdqFNbdQiJ3NdMdyA4KxGdMzgOptJ4f&fid=0x0:0xacbab57ad972554d"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Channi Mangat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrsgGQLKm8w8TdtaiM7vIS9IHZZpxCCxANG8pw_GWQef-3Bw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The aroma of freshly brewed coffee blends with the enticing scent of baked goods. A chalkboard menu highlights a variety of crafted coffee drinks, from rich espressos to creamy lattes.

The food menu features an array of delicious options, including sandwiches, salads, breakfast options, pastries and so much yummy goodness. On top of it all the staff is super friendly!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPvJi-CbZRE-8m1tScJuecxAeWcP3SJ2ob2JFpy&fid=0x0:0xacbab57ad972554d"],"When":"2024-8-14"},{"Name":"J P Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVv-TZdheQ2KRgbv66PStcV7Bg2Aya6_K0c9TCrcSOX10hChF3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the most amazing , cozy cafe in town , food was amazing we ordered chicken soup, salads and sandwiches , everything was amazing","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDqg-kqh8LoqFC9_vFmxEefPYKalsuxnQ_XZil&fid=0x0:0xacbab57ad972554d"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"jen m","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeQNO8NNd0t9FbBnznetBUT44TCQLsDB-hDGiBjQVIVhMKQXMDtA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was pleasantly surprised from the moment I stepped into the beautiful Laura's cafe...the atmosphere was socially bustling but fun! The display of food next to none with delicious home made muffins, cakes and savoury foods being made before your eyes by the exceptional and very busy owner chef.
Nothing but good things to say here with a welcoming environment and excellent food! Enjoy 😊 !!
Make sure you check out the clothing store next door afterwards if you want to have the icing on the cake 😉","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmdbUcoIA14eVmgHyeeIaCOtyqLDNJZk5zxt7n&fid=0x0:0xacbab57ad972554d"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Adrian MacNair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIviILMdblqon6QnkYL7-t7G53EY3ssnJ3YNZ2zAnNhDD6ehU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Laura's is a nice south facing diner so it gets great sun on some days making it a nice place for lunch.

It may just be inflation everywhere but I was a bit surprised that two sandwiches, two coffees and a slice of cake cost $50. Perhaps that's normal these days.

The food was good. As it's largely self service I don't think it's really worth tipping for, unless you want to express gratitude for when they bring the plates to your table.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fatih 'Fred' F Kaya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkzdVemcW3kQxI5Yuln0AfI1uMAuQjYu-cB9QStImZYm8LhXclBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"With a beautiful ocean view, it was very joyful and relaxing to sit and have chitchat with my wife. The food was perfect, I had a sandwich and a cheesecake, they were very delicious and fresh. I would definitely come again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP89RiQQwXd-gU6KAv3UKsl_W-mvwbV1pr4vXYe&fid=0x0:0xacbab57ad972554d"],"When":"2023-12-14"},{"Name":"Savanna Bobyk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvN9NsgKCf5YadPFuS44BB8Yqak50PQQYTf_Wkosr8gEiBGYZa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very cute cafe!! delicious coffee & food . Friendly staff as well 🤗","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOt6n_1p_iIarihKfaOcy2s5d2kv7RgJ3ys78JK&fid=0x0:0xacbab57ad972554d"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Elvira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzRK4_7yxEfrmCsOQcVlphSbzAAdhYPYhY8hDsv-E5jr2H0G3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The place is nice for white rock but coffee has no smell , I guess it’s not fresh roasted. The cake was nice and the salad bowl is sooo generous, it’s hard to finish if you don’t share with someone!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCciP8SDg3Xorad8SAfCe9Rh-dMBK5h_pGJcWj&fid=0x0:0xacbab57ad972554d"],"When":"2024-6-23"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"James Pflanz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS26ix_P4Nldv6brUMlqSUeZcP4HwdJt6NUfMZp__CAWdAxr68=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's a fabulous neighborhood bakery. Friendly and helpful staff but they can get overwhelmed when it gets busy.

I love their chocolate cake.  Very close to homemade. Some other sweets remind me of my German grandmother. Also love their bacon butter biscuits.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcO4F0zv_pOHr7IJrYIR3lyZcfY64r6fuPT5erJ2F6pMwsiDAD-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered a day prior: sticky cinnamon buns.  When I picked up my order the following day, the store changed the order (without informing me)  from "sticky" to "glazed" (or iced) cinnamon buns as shown in the order note. The lady at the counter couldn't explain why it was changed and who changed it from their side. She offered to order the right one and if I would come back the next day and pick up the right variety. I was already there, so I declined and picked the glazed one. It would have been less inconvenient if someone called me about it before i picked it up at the designated time. I suspect that the store may have given my order to someone else and replaced it with what was available when I came to pick it up.
Though it wasn't what I ordered, the glazed cinnamon buns were fresh, moist, and dense.  It was reasonably priced too.
The bakery looks very impressive, quite contemporary, and clean with a variety of tasty pastries and delis at fair prices. Happy to find this bakery in the Whiterock area - a real hidden gem! I would give them another chance when i order sticky cinnamon buns again next time.

UPDATE: Ordered a Pineapple Upside Down Cake (PUDC) for my wife's birthday.  She tasted this from Hillcrest Bakery last year and she couldn't stop talking about how moist, rich and delicious it was!  However, Hillcrest stopped selling it for a while. Called to order and Michelle arranged with the masterful baker. My wife was incredibly surprised when the cake was presented on her birthday. It made her birthday - and she enjoyed and savoured the cake tremendously! Hillcrest, a real precious gem in the Whiterock community. The PUDC was heavenly, a true timeless and retro treat - the best PUDC on earth! thank you Michelle and Hillcrest Bakery!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqF7iVmIj5OUPswtng_MG1G30RkBuVTKET8Byl&fid=0x0:0xa753ae9a9eaa7837"],"When":"2023-8-16"},{"Name":"Lisa G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjOge2_exdUKlST6XI83xr3DgPSCJuflRzRxaDTkzKu0tyqwWc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Hillcrest Bakery used to be the gem of White Rock and had such good pastries and breads. However, I was so disappointed when I came in today. Firstly, the bakery had a stale sour smell that was not appealing. I settled on a sandwich, soup and a donut. The girl making my sandwich was friendly and nice but she kept touch her face and wiped her nose twice with the back of her wrist while preparing my sandwich. The sandwich was okay (the bread was delicious) but for a vegetable sandwich that cost $8.50 I would expect more than just cheese, mayo, mustard and a few vegetables (lettuce, cucumber and pickles (I declined the offered banana peppers and onions)). Maybe offer tomatoes? Avocado? Sprouts? Cream cheese?
I also got the cheddar broccoli soup and ended up throwing it out as the thin soups  “cheese” wasn’t melted and had a weird texture and overall flavour. The donut was dry and obviously previous frozen and brought in.

I was very pleased to see the wall of pre-bought meals and items that could be taken. I feel this could be better set up though. It’s behind the counter so you can’t read what’s available and also there is a sign to “give the prepaid ticket to the server” - how can you if it’s behind the counter?  If I also may suggest adding a “box lunch” option folks can pre-purchase that contains a choice of sandwich, a hot or cold drink, a bag of chips and a dessert bar or cookie?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jen Young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICpnbsh8IYv5NAModSoK2ssetwisA-lJbz05jy-5pwIGGCMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Picked up two small meat pies for almost $10 realistically worth maybe three dollars each. The beef and vegetable pie had maybe a tablespoon of ground beef in a moist flower paste with absolutely no vegetables or flavour. The crust on the bottom was not cooked and chewy.
I asked the person working there, if the pies had been in contact with cilantro, as I have an allergy.  She just shrugged her shoulders, and continued to ask me for money.
I don’t know if this is under new ownership or not, but I won’t be back.
Also smelled very much like an Indian restaurant in there not a bakery.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzDgfuxCFeaM4aWqremHTJE_Tnfh7DQZewfU0S&fid=0x0:0xa753ae9a9eaa7837"],"When":"2024-2-9"},{"Name":"Victoria Camp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVP_jePY1ZFudRzJelk3DgPG4LANnhu4dNGl0EeLeIkIEaWbq7u=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered 13 dozen cookies for my wedding dessert. Hillcrest had great prices (best around as far as I saw), easy pick up and payment, good communication from the team, and a very tasty product! Great service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Gorrie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJamPcCT32pljFmqJj5lNUJl_3E8IckT8irHqNLB7dkUh3ilw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"DONUTS ARE FROZEN!  I placed a $60 order for classic and gourmet donuts (2 dozen donuts ONLY for $60). I was told the gourmet donuts needed to be ordered in advance with a specific pick up time because they are only made on the weekends but I could take the classic ones now. I had to pay for the whole order in advance. After having to wait 30 mins for the classic donuts, when there were enough already made donuts in the display cabinet, I received freezing cold one, like too cold to eat. When I went back to pick up the gourmet donuts 4 days later at the specified time, I was told I had to wait again as they weren't ready.  I ended up waiting 20 mins to receive another batch of freezing cold donuts.  Just to confirm what I believed to be true that they in fact don't made their donuts fresh, I called and was told that their donuts are FROZEN AND DEFROSTED TO ORDER.  I will not be returning which is a real shame because this place use to be amazing before the new owners took over.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR-NtWx60betHk7dk9E58udsJ87tVP5184Kcsmp3yimRSmiIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"A very strange place... First and last time I'll go there. Was sort of looked at weird the whole time (nothing on my face I swear haha) and was given it to go, but was to eat it here. No napkins or glass of water. I am eating (this is lunch time) and I am the only customer there and one of the Punjabi staff members comes near me and films me with his phone... Normally I would ask and make a fuss, but I had a cold, it was a cold winter day. I ate my lunch for 10 mins and left. Not sure why he filmed me nor why he said nothing about it to me. So just a weird group working in there, weird vibes. Bad first impression. Won't be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Terry Braumberger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuziWkPSmtFLsonsQrA8jaubopZEPk5Tb0MsabTSm9wiC9b_4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"To add to the already fantastic menu of baked goods and deli foods the holiday menu of a all the trimmings turkey dinner. Mashed potatoes and gravy, stuffing and carrots, light and dark meat and cranberry sauce! For dessert I chose the butter tart , the pumpkin 🎃 tart was the other choice. On top of being enough for two good sized meals they delivered it to my door yesterday. Worth every penny, so next holiday Christmas I’ll do it again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1JjvTeOaj2aXPg84s3uW4WmtSYUYMJmJAucDP&fid=0x0:0xa753ae9a9eaa7837"],"When":"2022-10-10"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jen S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6yRDu3X2tYRf22dSS2L1HUQ_---VPNFSZyVWrJW6KXuGpfNIHww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant is a part of the golf course, but anyone can dine in. The building looked more like a big room for events, like weddings. The ambiance was on the classier side as the tables were covered by white cloths. Service was good, but the food was a bit slow to come out.

We were pleasantly surprised by the food. I want to give their grilled bread 10 stars. All of the dishes were beautifully set and everyone enjoyed their meals. The cod could have used more flavour in the curry broth. The seafood chowder was amazing. It had a liquid creamy broth and the freshest seafood. We would come back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmNW6iyL6D-4RblggU_WQ4P_0BO4af_LVuj5Cw&fid=0x0:0x5e6b6995f625b400"],"When":"2023-3-12"},{"Name":"Blacklist Tattoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxEYbm07mGD5jjq38QdBZMtT6UgATk34IvaPxPBz4_JpnHSwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I frequent the hills for lunch when we have a break from work. Popped in yesterday and an event was going on and the dinning room was full. Thankfully the chef accommodated us in the coffee bar and we had an amazing late lunch. The smash burger here is hands down one of, if not the best burgers in town. It's truly a beautiful room for a lunch or an event. A hidden gem in summerfield. Desert was equally impressive and the service and care was top notch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNN7p5GbeLbMhmqLnCu7ZX73Uwn0cdSWT_mqKbp&fid=0x0:0x5e6b6995f625b400"],"When":"2022-12-9"},{"Name":"Faizan Mansuri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlWQ2O0Fc93P934tLSEl5EGWHalw9912eVmidi48kuUJ3K9fou=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had a party yesterday and such wonderful hospitality as well as wonderful food. The ambience is just cozy enough for a beautiful date or a full fledged musical party. Wonderful staff too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYtX4A1sVXrFW3iMiHpsOiWRFxl1zrw9lGQlO-&fid=0x0:0x5e6b6995f625b400"],"When":"2022-11-27"},{"Name":"J D'Souza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXasM3Hkct4Zm6Z42srbXDwtY8MWeM-JzJQQAr68kWr9pQSxff9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went to The Hills for the Santa Brunch this morning, and it was great. Yes, the restaurant was understandably busy with it being the holiday season and a weekend but the staff, chef, and owner were all extremely accommodating and appreciative! The food was awesome, and getting to visit Santa without having to go to a busy mall was absolutely an added bonus.

Kudos to Kira and the whole team at The Hills, thanks for being a great option for the residents of the Douglas neighbourhood!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carol Anne Cole","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqRpo-jFc2huODXEzSWZxrKWLt-Zi7AIIrkzHEF14SBozN9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a lovely late lunch here and enjoyed it immensely.  My fish and chips were great, the fish was moist and tender.  We had the best waitress (Madison) who remembered our order down to the small details, and served with a smile. I would be happy to return there and strongly recommend The Hills in White Rock, BC.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff Fimrite","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgWlJ4zhuWSN-cKZt5FTr6mszjS4Ykb54-OGQUKaJofCiXQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I just went here for a meal, and all I can say is I wish we had gone sooner. We liked the food and the atmosphere a lot. Service was prompt and staff was excellent.

We had a variety of dishes off the regular menu and the dine-out special menu (tofu, nachos, risotto , steak frites, tomato bisque to name a few), all were really nicely done. We hope some of the dine out options become regular items they were so good.

Atmosphere was awesome too, we had a family style table by the fireplace. Will definitely come back again soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tarlyn Campbell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKFfSO3L9HQBQNErq-55sU5eIW3P2sTzYrbJKpylo1y0K23_vP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Wow, I feel bad for the Staff here!

I went to the Hills Restaurant for Lunch with my husband and child, what is a beautiful golf course and should have been an amazing lunch was interrupted by the supervisor screaming at staff. [{"Name":"Shalini DC","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzwN5OQNZhe6YTFUiuOt4if-AhuvpxpthN-190_mrDp2NdunDN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a fantastic experience! The ambiance was wonderful. A special shout out to Tejal, who went above and beyond to make the evening memorable. She knew the menu inside out, answered all our questions, and gave great recommendations. She even surprised us with a cake to celebrate my husband’s birthday. Her thoughtful service truly made our night memorable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGNI3fpNW_m4zLz_AWrhCMhnYGSIbU6BAOHPMG&fid=0x0:0xa63ef39920c62ac7"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"AWAIS THE BOSS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFR2cYPf0wPxYiA1s-uSEkyon-hcTMvm8LJq6BY3cw9K_NYCzp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Showshaa - The Modern Taproom offers a unique blend of traditional and contemporary dining experiences, making it a standout destination for food enthusiasts. The vibrant ambiance, characterized by its modern decor and artistic lighting, creates a welcoming space perfect for casual gatherings or celebratory occasions.

The menu is a delightful fusion of Indian flavors and global influences, catering to a variety of tastes. Signature dishes like the Butter Chicken Tacos and Tandoori Paneer Quesadillas showcase their creative approach to traditional recipes. The beverage menu is equally impressive, featuring craft cocktails and a curated selection of beers, including locally inspired brews that pair perfectly with the food.

Service is another highlight at Showshaa. The staff is attentive, knowledgeable, and ensures a seamless dining experience. Special care is taken to accommodate dietary preferences, which adds a personalized touch.

Live music and events further elevate the atmosphere, making it more than just a dining venue—it’s a destination for entertainment. However, peak hours can be busy, so reservations are recommended.

Overall, Showshaa impresses with its innovative cuisine, lively ambiance, and exceptional service, making it a must-visit spot for food and drink lovers looking for a modern take on a taproom experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNnOwvZbK5zeJQFgS-YQ3cRpoBtPhunmEnIUrUf&fid=0x0:0xa63ef39920c62ac7"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"Jasleen Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJq_mX4JcS2qCxDJUdxLM5cEoBdw7wYfyUdfHLGfdunsmqsnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The place serves delicious food that has authentic Indian flavours. The ambience and service are amazing as well. We were a party of 8 and went to celebrate a friend’s birthday. Our server, “Tejal”made sure that all our needs were met and she helped us with a beautiful smile on her face all the time. Cheers to Tejal. We will be back for sure!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1vhV8X4F86v4kjN6L4WsRwOQozsONRjDuJK6_&fid=0x0:0xa63ef39920c62ac7"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Adi Sivaram","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpOrzD-PQC1hiQxF1opqwrMfKtsC1I92Ew4uFMWm4rId-YLzGv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great Indian fusion food, service and ambience. [{"Name":"Elena Ludovico Gillespie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2yKwIgIi7kquMER_SuGk4o46Yi6ukTVxLgMFOdq9UbLIJ_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Me and my friends came here expecting an easy and fun brunch. We had to wait 40 minutes just to be seated and 50 minutes just for the food to arrive, making the wait time over one hour. The food was greasy and heavy on the stomach, but taste-wise was good. The waiters were kind but didn’t tell us about the surplus we had to pay, so instead of spending under 20$ we ended up paying over 20$. I would not recommend this place if you’re looking for a fast, calm, light, fun brunch: there are better places to go. Overall, it wasn’t bad, but was not good at all either.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPcDLKkRd90g4w2Sc6Flj3AGjTYxUvcP8dkMlY&fid=0x0:0xc9bce9490f7dedbc"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"G Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfu-DBaOuKC7N8N7DlMSqMyljJYmJLTPnBZhRhMUkeM4mGa6do=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Came in for a daughter daddy date but turned out not to be so good. The red shirt hostess wasnt very approachable or nice. When I found a what seems to be a leg of some sort of bug I brought it to the attention of the employee and she just said "oh do you want another pancake.... Are you ready to pay ?"","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmacrp5QgsGJyP7VcZ0EaHDIll5YSBZKYPk1mh&fid=0x0:0xc9bce9490f7dedbc"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Foodieatlarge Ou812!","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUV5WjUsogcvFcdpk650G44_1nDSsUxfDfJjUXorbWVcHcaIaXI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Gr8 classic diner style fare. Comfort food as it was meant to be.Simple fresh, made to order and satisfying.
No surprises, just reliable cost effective fuel of yesteryear and it grandeur. We were warmly served by an Angel of a gal whom possessed such a genuine eagerness to get ur order, get it right and in a timely yet cordial manner. Rare these days that some truly dig their gig, I admire that passion and commitment.
Who doesn't wanna b fed,treated like a valued guest and fueled up for what's up next right?
U should go.

Appy Trails,
Brianm

foodieatlarge.yelp.ca","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJ3AzJKq4fLbcAirQTLsyMVUv1rIYw62extB8E&fid=0x0:0xc9bce9490f7dedbc"],"When":"2024-2-18"},{"Name":"jam gaña","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbUjSXgnUHHLx55MD4d7PIk1cifbmYVescZgfUL1GSm99Iq04=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best hashbrown I have ever tasted! The manager Sharon was professional in apologizing to me for this unfortunate circumstance. IHOP management, please investigate incident to find root cause and prevent similar incidents from happening again.
Thank you!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPM4Tu6gn5_dKMo0Fu2D9hF09qlcyqQyjIPzOk-&fid=0x0:0xc9bce9490f7dedbc"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"Sara Carlyle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUfagfxPSsqRzysTwGF0HJYhcU468FFL0xhcJkSC6KqdQt-JTe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brett is absolutely amazing. He’s worked here for years. I had the best service ever and he really made my day. The food was fresh and there’s endless options. They’re very flexible and easy-going when you want to make customized orders. The coffee is a lot better than places like Tim Hortons or Starbucks. Will be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"C K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0sP-spxfMR49feD7bgUCr3-pleVWPCB44P4SYKEm3Q3Urihw_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Go To place for my 88 year old mom and many local seniors and families and everyone!
It’s busy and noisy and full of good souls. The staff are wonderful and work 200% or more. They are accommodating to all. I have never seen a bad customer but they wouldn’t be there long because all who eat here understand and would protect the staff if they were rude.😉🤣
My mom would eat here daily if she could. I imagine many within walking distance do.","Images":null,"When":""}]

I came from 20 km just to this restaurant, but my experience was disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLhYwWRHZq7F0gJqJf361X-H1zEPO0V-kdWLM3&fid=0x0:0xeb7443b247cb701"],"When":"2024-1-13"},{"Name":"Melanie E","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR0bJcxqNkJt-i1wxCH3EaQXevncA86panZszfT__NAs_0KWRp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We came here for lunch. If you are on a schedule expecting to be in & out in an hour, don’t count on it. It’ll take time for them to cook your food. Their food quality hasn’t changed especially during Covid. They’re listed as a Greek restaurant but also have Indian food dishes  along with burgers & pasta dishes. Look for their  special lunch menu at reasonable prices.

Service was great! Looking forward to going back for their dinner menu. A great local restaurant to dine at. There’s free parking out front. They’re located in the plaza next to the movie theatre.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9dgF2b7eSwoGIxXwgFIRFn-UmerAeS3YaZgN1&fid=0x0:0xeb7443b247cb701"],"When":"2022-8-1"},{"Name":"Nick D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLrX_Pw4Z3I9JOHtVHvjkbzoSHOVHObb-WwEa3xQIt6_cKzwg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"EXTREMELY RUDE AND UNPROFESSIONAL TAKE OUT PERSON!  First we had to wait an additional 40 minutes to pick up food after the time was given, than once arriving home we found out that it was the incorrect order, called back in and was outright called a liar. Extremely unprofessional and have lost our business after coming to this restaurant for years, do better.  Do not recommend, will also be passing this information on to my friends on the same bases. The women that took the order ruined this restaurant for us.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Seating is quite nice and made for an enjoyable sit-down lunch","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN1HZXBxMsGnuzOVPrksEu4zJ4FtfEigDJK1GRo&fid=0x0:0xca0995b8ab1cc560"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Jennifer Dennis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLMNt6g7mU09FwrUU9sgX6l8D-NxJpiFrXIl82RywnUQRL-PTA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is an excellent sandwich shop. Only one complaint...all the portions were great, except for the French dip.  I paid extra for the Gluten free roll.  The entire sandwich was smaller than had I ordered the regular bread.
