I had the Reuben sandwich and egg drop chicken noodle soup. Both were the best I’ve ever had!! As the  very generous owner handed me my food he told me he added extra cheese because I opted out on the sauerkraut. How awesome!!! From atmosphere, counter service, and delicious food everything was perfect.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miguel J.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvFKKyw6Zz6cZM3bYhyRix8dzFrproaGAy4C3ZnwOLkIFumger=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Believe the hype.

These guys know how to make sandwiches. I ordered the club and my wife ordered the Bahn mi. Both were very well made. The bread they use is so soft and lends itself to a very delightful biting down on your sandwich experience. The sandwich is put together really well. All the ingredients stayed in tact as I chomped through. Nothing fell out. The quality of the turkey is as good as you'd expect and the sauce *chef's kiss*

Oh, I also had the cream of mushroom soup. It was excellent.

A well deserved 4.8 star average at the time of writing this review.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOa_djrLyfvriq4uMH5Yu23VQk8eYL7DYhy6NRV&fid=0x0:0xca0995b8ab1cc560"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Kiki Dhaliwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJGMFz6qTRTsakGxerQ2u7TA_FAShzQbloVJ4vk4aDe6COcA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best sandwich shop ever!!! Ps. they split everything perfectly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"E D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKd2RxMnsRltzlELiKMwjTP0IsKRsOo8h1-ITC_BgKeI74rdg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing flavors, generous portion, and great value. [{"Name":"Yuki Chin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgPmyvA2BNqgUzNUpeq8PkwjRislBWVbWQ9MeOGPDSzARy97eC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time to this location for Christmas Eve dinner.  The atmosphere was very comfortable and beautiful.  The staff also very friendly especially our server Mr. Chris P.  He gave us a very good and attentive service.  Thank you Chris.

Their food were very good, tasty and delicious.  I have ordered a full rack of Honey Garlic Pork Rib which includes of 1 side and coleslaw.  I ordered the mashed potatoes as my side and it is so yummy and smooth texture.  My two children ordered their pizza (Meateor & Carbonara). My two children loved it.  May going back again next time.  Highly recommend this place. Price is okay not too expensive, affordable price.

Plenty of parking spot at the rear.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXRg-OkMD2Odk-a8ltjKeSC1Z-Dk0JhAxOrqwM&fid=0x0:0xbc47c029d78329d8"],"When":"2024-12-25"},{"Name":"Stella Stone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWiwOLPA91h1nSRncqHRS0qib_VmmyRolNqqODNG7WYqfGpw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I might not be the best person to review a whole menu, but I can say I keep coming back for the Mac N Cheese! Delicious! Great portion size, creamy, and so cheesy.
I tried the Smoky Mountain Meatballs with Spaghetti. Enormous portion, very tasty.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Souvik Basu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxVSo2Y3x9QlduJxGzsyK7FvRv6JZsmjOlPWmAr3ju-IARvuc1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved the sporty ambience of the place. The server was very friendly and made sure we were comfortable and having a good time. I love pizza here more than most other places in Metro Vancouver. The topping was good and the pizza sauce was delicious. I took chicken pizza with honey garlic sauce and loved it. Chicken tender strips were also good, we took it with poutine fries on the side.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZ9cW7RlSQDO0crtTrrq9Mm4Xmwr8BJVK79Mkx&fid=0x0:0xbc47c029d78329d8"],"When":"2023-12-28"},{"Name":"Grady Flinn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwL3c1PbcvwMeLOJEnikld0CmPKaiF9dFqgPudVVoxm0_xtZqf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great lunch at Boston Pizza Whiterock, I might be a bit bias as I used to work here way back in 1994 until 1998, a lot of great memories. It still has the same feeling. The food was great as always and service bang on as usual. It’s a bit pricey yes, but I find it makes up in quality. You certainly can’t go wrong with a signature Boston brute! Well done five stars ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPbBznPUASpqPjG3Lc3YFBuUqTRMczUo94Fo8c&fid=0x0:0xbc47c029d78329d8"],"When":"2023-8-28"},{"Name":"wenna harper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLj7RwdeFSyawL9PyTCnjREX9u29LAKB49BQy919yTZW2wA1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Previously had 2 awful experiences at this location but MUSKAAN has totally turned that around on multiple occasions. I have been in on over 6 times and she has made me feel like royalty and never messed up any of my picky orders. I have sat at the bar and witnessed her teamwork with all her co workers and dropped  everything to help any of her coworkers .Muskaan deserves the Boston pizza 2024 award for best 1. Team player 2.best guest experience and 3. Best employee. I’m Overwhelmed by her fabulous employee performance.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve Vokey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUinb5eHsug3KbxWc8m8rntJUL-PnFNCFARDaiFhHR5guoA-Aj6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a Christmas gathering for work and we all had a great time.  The food was good and servers were very friendly. Thank you Deanna,
And the rest of the team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jack Peters","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6tuotdk1_dATGiaaY-PEJ7e94vRmmulQ4gtBej1xawfyQQRAu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Mother's Day dinner was very good. I'm told, "one of their busy days". Ordered the Thai Chicken Wrap and was very good. Normally I order a burger, but this hand held was a pleasant surprise. Good service, atmosphere was fine, fries were not good, met the franchise owner (she was nice) and was greeted with and had a farewell from one of the nice staff. The reasonably priced food would be my reason to return, but the French Fries would be a do over. Definitely open LATE.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMK1YqPIF1SlHGdguhq9egJp8BFcBcPM2tjR01b&fid=0x0:0xbc47c029d78329d8"],"When":"2024-5-30"},{"Name":"WILLIAM REN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKRmqUVmhhErGGqKi-Bzn0et1-EnBX9lgvZO2NQ0f1pzZpZEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Boston Pizza began in Edmonton, Alberta, on August 12, 1964, almost 60 years old, but it is still a popular family restaurant. Today our family enjoy the NEW TRIPLE PLAY, which is shareable portion of three guest favourites: Bandera Bread with Santa Fe Ranch dip, our Signature Chicken Thai Bites, and Cactus Cut Potatoes served
with cactus.
The restaurant is a traditional industry. It is easy to open a new  one, but it is difficult to manage an old restaurant for more than ten years. Consumption upgrade is a very common method that can attract new customers, but if you can innovate dishes without upgrading consumption, you will attract more repeat customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMepIk7OKWkkYGqsKfd7PrRQm9t9KSiuIuIF45v&fid=0x0:0xbc47c029d78329d8"],"When":"2023-4-17"}]

[{"Name":"Kevin Luo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWJMxLZr-3YvPOYEYkCwOqoRgX8yyWGLPYZ19IJEKzgIUssXc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Excellent location and service at this restaurant. The patio has amazing views and is a great place to enjoy sunset over the White Rock Pier. The modern decor is beautiful, and reminded me of much fancier restaurants. I arrived very close to closing time, and the owner still let me in and brought me hot tea while I made my orders. The food came out promptly, hot, and freshly made. The portions are big and flavours authentic. I really enjoyed the Seafood Crispy Rice, which I have not had for a long time. The Sauteed Eggplant is also fantastic, with the garnish being a nice touch. However, be warned that for a vegetarian dish it contains meat. Parking is quite a pain, since only paid parking is available and the lots are always filled up.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvnTZnSDUnS1fI4Y9FOReMV0eBrnbV5jUNqs_l&fid=0x0:0x5f007ffe4ec755d5"],"When":"2024-4-16"},{"Name":"Sel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxzAzCLWOYxeYpRHTgp946MmKZEsbMnNBaxXsImxn8VGlKuVJu8w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The dishes we tried were quite good, the portion sizes leaned on the smaller side. Unfortunately, the experience was overshadowed by an issue with the soup. We initially thought the black specks in it were black pepper, but upon closer inspection, they turned out to be fruit flies—at least three of them. This was disappointing to say the least as we had high expectations after seeing so many good reviews.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOogQ1_TLcd6S4qhM26FS8Cdzba3RUnnTeBhKWa&fid=0x0:0x5f007ffe4ec755d5"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Alen Francis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxrLyFjN5ZTdLrFMtApcbr_sxTLoknMXBkIvQ73q9JG1brMsPRmA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Posting the good stuff first cause it was an overall bad experience. We ordered 2 orders of dumplings and fried rice , and we had to wait around 30-45 min to be served. A can of pop that was ordered along with the food had to be asked for a second time to be served which would take just a couple of minutes for the can to be opened and brought to our table. There was a bigger group of customers (which I believe are either the owner/owners or a "higher priority customer") who were seated after us were served and taken care of way quicker and nicer than we were.
So my final opinion would be, if you are planning to do a takeout or delivery order, go for it. But I would not recommend it to dine in.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eddie So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISSdmRal6WEYNToT2BfCZQ0cdumKRhmtyRM82KD93UMkc0-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you like Shanghai cuisine or Chinese food, this is a good restaurant for you. When you enjoy the yummy food,  the ocean view is a bonus.
The quality of food, service, price and atmosphere all are well worth the five stars.
Since I think they have a good chef, all the food will be good.
The portion of the food are good for the price. The lady server that we met is super friendly and helpful.
When we want to order the Xiao Long Bao, it was sold out at that time 4pm.
The lady tells us after we finished our meal.  The stream buns are just freshly made. So we order one again.  It's so good with all juice inside the small bun.
It will be nicer if we can sit outside but it's too cold out there even with heater.
We sure will be back when we are visiting this area again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMA7AdUn6JcT-eFX0JWJ3HXjtm_4UpdmkxWMJUK&fid=0x0:0x5f007ffe4ec755d5"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"Sarah Kain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1fNQTLXW7baMmxna_6rnjAgvYnYPN8FT1NlVTpQgs-4Uhzebw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We came for dinner on a Friday night, it wasn't too busy, we were greeted promptly.  1st time here and my home town is Shanghai,  I was excited to try some of their dishes. We loved the fried fish, it had bones but it was very tasty.  Shanghai fried noodles was also great, it was cooked with chicken which we should've just asked for meatless. Mongolian beef was tasty, we asked for less sauce because we like the crispy taste of the dish.  Pan fried dumplings wasn't our favorite,  i think we would've been happier with XiaoLongBao instead.  We received great service and didn't wait long for our food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1KDCcHadJwZ3EeU2UMQ_P8-OOs79GIaKzU804&fid=0x0:0x5f007ffe4ec755d5"],"When":"2023-2-27"},{"Name":"Tommy “Powerbuilderwannabe” Xiao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfDi4iFU0b7G0chKTplbE5u7vf20zgZVI66nBpazopRw9TLzij=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food was delicious as the Mongolian beef and pineapple shrimp were all nicely seasoned. However, we were slightly disappointed with the portion of the food as the six of us ordered six different dishes and we weren’t even half full after our dinner. Additionally, the price of each dish was slightly overpriced in comparison to its portion size. The staffs are friendly tho.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMmjF8PcMYu0bgRpQ9mTer4JlOCfohOwgN4YNV&fid=0x0:0x5f007ffe4ec755d5"],"When":"2023-7-16"},{"Name":"Lucy Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVgWXFxWw1Rv8l5K7b7HVQzpJHlXejx7PEI6ZO88yTkTYk_OZ9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great location, excellent food but service was so so. Two servers were present. One male was good but the female server should get some training on service and priorities","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOE4Kqa6hFGdYjzYKHGimDh_ch7_P_g5H2Kyn2u&fid=0x0:0x5f007ffe4ec755d5"],"When":"2024-8-12"},{"Name":"Susie Su","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVCAuzfjFgyKqRooCVKTP8q3iWQb8FUWDyxTRXazAhINMtJDQskg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Reasonably priced Chinese food in White rock. Patio seating is available.

We liked their fried pork chop and black pepper diced beef the most. Everything else was also ok but felt like had a lot of white pepper.

Overall a great restaurant!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-6jtBjP5cdIRxilX-08Pdnf6H_zRzbdYIUIKd&fid=0x0:0x5f007ffe4ec755d5"],"When":"2023-6-21"}]

The fries and cowboy salad were yummy too. Service was average, atmosphere was good. Good AC and nice patio. Might be coming here more often…","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8fIVcWWuI7TS2PAUKBm2ehgYlukRzpkeo9_FM&fid=0x0:0x339771a4a1dfc02"],"When":"2023-8-17"},{"Name":"Gabriel Chu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZcXaZIxgZheD_Wk-zQlTEee-LgzfHHbWgBr9MkJKeKetBNHun=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I like this place and we order from here all the time. Great food and great service. Recently to our surprise however in our takeout items have been very much reduced in volume! Maybe it’s the hardships of post Covid labor and material costs? I just phoned them to let them know and they are “checking up with corporate” and hopefully they can make their proportions more similar to what they were sized in the past. Anyways, I needed to order another appy to be full when regularly this dragon ball is enough for me. Anyways the customer service was great and they responded well to feedback. Thanks so much!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8jnBjzUnyh2mfJ5r8UeV9omCFFv7p9kybh_Rm&fid=0x0:0x339771a4a1dfc02"],"When":"2023-1-17"},{"Name":"Andrea Pino-Olivares","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDHfW5CQIShXG0Q2Pw9uW-j6d53mSzuaPbenQG8OgvnErBa6_0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food is decent, but not amazing.
Tried to order take out by phone, but was unable to talk to anyone. Went in person and was ignored for around 15min until someone asked if I wanted a table. When I said that I would like to order take out, they called another girl to take my order...another 10min waiting. I know they are busy, particularly around dinner time,  but just acknowledging a person standing by the door would be very polite. The portions are smaller than a few months ago.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNO0rjgfo_7YgnzAR9UQifuIOSjNoJo4S2dGVjB&fid=0x0:0x339771a4a1dfc02"],"When":"2021-4-22"},{"Name":"Christy Boyce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMibPiiYMEgE7SJQOAv4Byr-bCjakyLRZP80ev-E1UgV5Uy_QZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great visit.  The staff did an excellent job at getting my gluten free meal to me. They have lots of great options for food. Drinks were delicious.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Judith Glenn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqO8N_UttsSJbHIgE3fgklnVfF6A4B1f9FCNxjzxoXHhTPng=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Despite the restaurant being nearly empty at 6:45pm, if you are going to the theatre at 8 o'clock you better be at this location of Brown's just a block down the street by 6:30pm, know what you want to order and place your order with your waitress immediately. If you like to have a selection of the delicious appies you better be there well before 6, the end of happy hour. After that the price goes up 3 dollars each. There is no indication of this increase on the menu. That was quite disappointing. I ordered the crispy chicken burger. After a long wait our meals arrived so we had to gobble them down in order to get across the street to the theatre.
Now about that burger; those brioche buns are ridiculous. I deconstructed mine and just ate the filling with a knife and fork. There was way too much batter on the chicken but it was very tasty. My dining partner wasn't able to eat his meal fast enough so he left quite a lot on his plate because we had to rush down to the theatre
I will never eat there in the evening again.  Leisurely lunch and happy hour dining is best.
From now on I will be going to the pub across the street before the theatre. Their food is better and cheaper and service is prompt.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth Bird","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcOt1yxUbxbyuQBKsDqOouH0_gEvQNeJK3-54fMtNoUEL4TA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"food is amazing, vibe is great, very pretty little restaurant but the part that stand out the most is the service. the staff are all very polite and kind, our server looked out for us and the manager ensured we were taken care of in an uber. 10/10 for all of the extra work they put into making us safe.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Perry Isidore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIS_JR0bXwG2vYtVFsLKG3jRQ-YLp0jm18HvP3gHez1lDznQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"A decent spot would recommend it although my fries were overcooked. Surprisingly the waitress never came back to ask me how was my meal or I would have told her about the fries. That was a bit disappointing hence why I would score them low on the customer service. Even trying to get the attention of a waitress after we got our meal prove futile. Otherwise, the fish compared to other restaurants was on par with average standard, nothing exceptional. My wife stated her shrimp dish was decent and she had no complaints. On the plus side the New York cheese cake was great.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-aSa7dBJ6VL105-De4q4_6nzUkx5clbPSdULy\u0026fid=0x0:0x2d400ef0830f58bc"],"When":"2024-11-1"},{"Name":"Anahita Abbaspour Tehrani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocINQ6HJbjlxneNevfGdjdvpIRcy8Z_1OnyIXDgl8hThjNQC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Yesterday I went to this restaurant and I asked for hot sauce. Same as all the other restaurants you expect that when you ask for ketchup or hot sauce it’ll be part of the customer service and they provide it for free. But at the end when the server brought the bill they charged me for two extra dips called “Add Dip” $1.00 each. This was the first time that i ever got charged for hot sauce!!!!!!!!! At least the server was supposed to tell me that they will charge for the hot sauce before i order not just surprising me with the bill. This wasn’t nice at all!!!! user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jamie Weins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhIg1Kb2wnv2Gwu5CpaHKGP6OAkgLsG22PmC8YHCHigI885W7L5A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We read the reviews and were a little hesitant, but I'm so glad we ignored any negative reviews. The food was excellent! The waffles are light but still have a nice crunch to them. We ordered the strawberry and banana waffle and the oreo. Delicious! The staff were friendly with all of us, and they have a nice seating area. For being down on the boardwalk, I expected the price to be higher, too. Highly recommend checking this spot out if you like waffles, crepes, or breakfast type food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8e9Hh_gbvvc3TFIAreQjB7eWVbR5KT4bzgFSJ&fid=0x0:0xdbc9b6483135a33"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Golnaz J N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwh094AvMjRiNSQoo9HjnFTPUMh8c3XSGOFZ78okUlI4KLdqnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The waffles I had were quite underwhelming, especially considering the price. I tried the Buntella and Paradise, and while they were decent, there was nothing particularly special about them. The portions were small, and the taste was simple – honestly, I could make better ones at home with just some whipped cream and Nutella. The creativity or "wow factor" you’d expect from a waffle shop just wasn’t there. To top it off, the latte I ordered didn’t taste like a real latte at all. Overall, it was an average experience that didn’t justify the high prices.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQPeItkw7hcfZGQooi5IJKFodfsh03mwP5vmiJ&fid=0x0:0xdbc9b6483135a33"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"Ashkan N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGC9QpVpAYzkuU2nETbRxXDGZW6ZxU4DFK0Bytd5fdamCstw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We stopped by for a quick bite after hearing great things about this place, but it didn’t quite meet our expectations. The service was a bit slow, the waffles were underwhelming, and the prices seemed high for what was offered. While the atmosphere is nice, I think the overall experience is somewhat overrated","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQ9Kkc9gPUtsWy2QIkWwRrK_j7VN-C8q9fsqIo&fid=0x0:0xdbc9b6483135a33"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"Monster Alive","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBCwzV2fBW-aqNyUDo9PAn82ZOw7tIyMywMxsXRX6v-VhwqPEe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Vegetarian Options, Phenomenal Taste, Mixed Feelings on Customer Service

I recently visited The Wafflers - Belgian Waffle Bar with my family, and we were delighted to find a variety of vegetarian options, especially in the White Rock area. The taste of the waffles was phenomenal, and overall, everything we tried was excellent.

However, I do have a concern about the demeanor of the staff. While the food was fantastic, I couldn't help but notice that the staff seemed unwelcoming. I'm not sure why, but it felt like they were not as friendly or welcoming towards everyone, particularly towards me. Customer service should be consistent for all patrons, regardless of skin tone or any other factor. It's disappointing to feel this way, and I hope it's something the management addresses.

Despite this issue, the food quality remains top-notch, and I would recommend The Wafflers for its delicious waffles and vegetarian options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBAX2SffMfGCzdpe17Jrd91dZSMy-Kd3JaWSeW&fid=0x0:0xdbc9b6483135a33"],"When":"2024-4-25"},{"Name":"Amy Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvtm7hBqZHDYxXgP_oxkelx2FGhwfW-EuwTv9rdyjxo-_-_8Nq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yummy waffles! Light and tasty, great for the Asian palette. It was a chill cafe and we played connect 4 while enjoying our waffle. Owners are really nice. The vibe was very pleasant and comforting. Had the pleasure of meeting one of the owners and he was super hospitable. And the beer is delicious, my fav was the Pilsner and their border porter. Will def be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Tuttle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUD17YFFa67NmhiFfAiv6ynTfiCh-Z6juLFkS5I9eGeNFrDVCDoEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a welcoming environment. Very friendly staff and a large drinks menu too. Not a huge place but there weren't waits to get in. Certainly worth  visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFFmK5cr8ZwdIHIrhtNGt_d69_L-_8Fhne51wH&fid=0x0:0x5eb2a179490adbe2"],"When":"2023-2-6"},{"Name":"Badger McTavish","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5ZnIfhhO-Tr9RBCN-nu-q0BRy9261QQDwk7XGcQf2Xw3XsjB4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great beer and friendly staff. It definitely feels like a real neighborhood pub when you walk in. I'm having their Brown Ale today on a proper (20oz) pint glass! A great traditional ale with the hops toned back to allow the toasty malt to come to the forefront. Liquid Comfort food! As always, some great old vinyl playing on the stereo. (Genesis today)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOcqQKF65iVJ_yBktN9MJKyDUrLvWe4i9L2nfA6&fid=0x0:0x5eb2a179490adbe2"],"When":"2022-1-16"},{"Name":"Kevin Field","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOnpjg4jm-3oJZtg5NH63wPgX48Z_LehNMsWxMoYEwvoP5Lguc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great atmosphere and friendly service. It's great to see so many places like this popping up. They are very Covid safe with patio seating. Good beer is a plus. Very much enjoyed my visit","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP337c3kN5bRZCsqrE69RB5JHtB6mpX6N-9WKn1&fid=0x0:0x5eb2a179490adbe2"],"When":"2021-4-18"},{"Name":"Jaeger Mah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt7hXDkFIcG6P61qcK0wBTq3t5gD1ANgzOWhiOupEWI1RBHtWj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Relaxing addition to the community. Their Pale Ale is not too hoppy, love it. ** Pet + baby friendly ** clean washrooms and friendly service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0sdRtqnT0y7nvqcgPeBbeYPSB7JO3WfjHIZDF&fid=0x0:0x5eb2a179490adbe2"],"When":"2018-6-3"},{"Name":"A Sh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRX8uNvZNK2Z4y_2bTeouDum2z0ZUXYzBQG7-gkoglqYRYRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved it.
My boyfriend and I tried all the beers they had. I am a dark beer drinker and he is a sour beer drinker at any breweries.  My favorites were winter-ale and brown ale. His favorites were sour beer and winter-ale.  And we both liked the taste of all the other beers, too. Most of them did not have very hoppy smells or much saltiness. So, if you are looking for hoppy, yeasty, saltiness, sweet flavors in your beer, maybe this is not the best place.

I am a cafe kind of person more than a pub hoppers. When I found the place when having a walk in the area by accident, I wanted to go in right away. It looked so cute and sassy for a brewery. :3 the business hour looked unusual for a brewery, but I loved it a lot. It makes the place more unique. We love places like that, so I brought him with me today.

The bartenders were friendly,  knowledgeable, attentive, and helpful.  The ambiance was so great!! Regular customers from the community hang out there appreciating the company with the bartenders and other regular customers. I was too shy to talk to them. But after some beers, I talked to the people who probably visited there for the first time like us, and we played a board game together. I did miss this kind of small town interactions with random people for a long time and I really enjoyed that.  Needless to say,  everything was so clean!!!  The bathroom was just so cute and so clean. I could even drink and eat in the bathroom if I had to. It was that great. :D","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPogkm02lu9VT3t6Jp8p6DgecKKrNuQjzXa4gyT&fid=0x0:0x5eb2a179490adbe2"],"When":"2019-4-7"},{"Name":"Katherine Crosbie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj_46fNbdhfY1fiDVDqSC0V3ehgO_hRf_cyUUX_dvudJa8IjLVdA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Neat local find. Always worthwhile dropping in to see what they have on tap. Not a big selection but quality brews. Small but friendly and always have a guest tap to try something new. Right around the corner from 3 Dogs Brewing so you can try out another great local craft brewery. Drop down on Sunday afternoons and check out the White Rock Farmer’s Market too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBJojkx3PqgzYhvRXr6vc2NsiJHQ_PwQW_UA0y&fid=0x0:0x5eb2a179490adbe2"],"When":"2020-6-21"},{"Name":"Mike Ansley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAO5eqBZOjRkAzRDMvoRPfe9zJEXP8nQNmZkzZHRYoXyJ0yjfV6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best beer in White Rock. Owners are super friendly, and winners of many community awards! Few food offerings, to keep you going, and if yiu need something more, you can bring in food for the many surrounding small businesses.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5D4mbuFcWSTSOxDku6eOUJHV0Tmw12NWR1WU0&fid=0x0:0x5eb2a179490adbe2"],"When":"2022-8-28"}]

[{"Name":"jen h","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhCIsdNpI0zn0ln1R2W8y6FEnO7Rpwo3p2N6L3S94WtNoyzHf7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great dessert place near the pier that isn’t ice cream or gelato! beaver tails are so nostalgic (and I swear they were bigger lol) but a corporate decision to cut down on dough sizing isn’t really a shop owners one so I won’t fault them for that. Nice enough owner - has his own headphones in for personal use. It can get really busy in there, but even if you have to wait a bit - you can take a seat just outside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNY0w7lf6CfmRaxCLfzh6NBdOECVg2ktLCo2fAG&fid=0x0:0xf06548285c328ad0"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"Lina Huine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTc90UClGdW5-vlLdRudv0nYQ1eUmIsZfcJ8sj-8pxZav3xZGO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This location wasn’t very busy for when I came in so I was able to order real quick, I’m only giving them four stars because I feel like my classic could’ve been cooked a little bit more so it was a little bit soggy. The location has a nice view on the waterfront and it’s across from the beach. Service was good, the staff was friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNM-q-pi4aTt0nXqKIttyi3UVg3kgVzXeSplYzZ&fid=0x0:0xf06548285c328ad0"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"Azalea Jhalli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvmM4dnJ1iQnr6boChMyCWWrMIlxOzGeRoYi4hxrcxiElIBfd1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love Beavertails and am so excited for this location to open up. It’s the perfect dessert or snack as its not too heavy or overly sweet. Each time I’ve stopped by the service is friendly and each tail is made fresh. I like that it’s on east beach so it’s not as busy. I look forward to trying the rest of the flavours! They also have poutine which looks and smells good I will have to check it out next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuOJKOM0o2ys5b-EAkeNTNxxWilAHf5C7TV2NH&fid=0x0:0xf06548285c328ad0"],"When":"2023-11-21"},{"Name":"Jason Parmar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUszIH8cvaTfy-rYQ9_tfZynvBRh5cJuF2mBEmbDCFoQ9gGHXd_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a great place for delicious desserts! There’s a variety of flavours to choose from at a respective price. I ordered the Apple Pie flavour and enjoyed every single bite of it:) Definitely will come back here for a treat, when I visit the beach next time!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIK03XAXzdebd4UcqgMzqsjVlyP4dJ4St5XyiR&fid=0x0:0xf06548285c328ad0"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"scarlett ortiz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7waCbq9y3r1eSOKt_mxY_ekBLY-go2DFIMZ9P8UkBsFAV_Xu7-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Shop owners extremely sweet and the view of the beach is gorgeous. Must stop for anyone in the states and parking was easy! Will be coming back for sure! Devoured before I remembered to take a picture that’s how delicious it was.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRQup1YG91c-QTQ3meb24ARQJ39a7GxGRLFrfd&fid=0x0:0xf06548285c328ad0"],"When":"2024-6-7"},{"Name":"Jarrett Jackson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhLFadADrWCe4la62Mdg5SQjHPrcQDmz7c11-6cbb1F0IhdA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went by for a late night snack and I live just a few steps away so figured it was a better time than any to go visit Beaver Tail! I had seen them getting ready to open in the summer but haven’t had the chance to enjoy!

It was a slow rainy evening so I understand why it was slow but I came in and they were happy to see me! Smiles, great service! They took my order and I guess one dough came out smaller than their standard so they apologized, made me a new one and then still gave me the “baby beaver tail” and gave me a different flavour to try!

Very sweet and kind hearted folk behind the counter, very delicious beaver tails that brings me back to being a kid again! Come hang out here for coffee and a treat!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfZ9tNrptXOxZZwzCsf0X7kyv-bZCpZQL0gFij&fid=0x0:0xf06548285c328ad0"],"When":"2023-11-10"},{"Name":"Felicia Pan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIy2XCL72yjdIkl-1HyNd2NXbix1mqe59RyEpUrbSZvemxxdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Owner is very nice!!

[{"Name":"Happy Sunny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhrtA612fP6soH2c7PBaInHGNvnte3YNRS_qAs35pTYrJn3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The sushi was fresh, delicious, and flavorful. The beef teriyaki was slightly salty, but still tasted great. Overall, the prices were very reasonable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODK0M4X8TOxRyGddXXjoCEpKap-vpkDuOml1jh&fid=0x0:0xb72764c3574e3c28"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Donald Yong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9n8neXRzcqctddBUWR4rip_e_oZkAlT64dYsrpmZ1Kzl3yuVf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm so glad I revisited White Rock after a long time, and I'm thrilled to have shared the experience with my family for the first time! The stunning views and charming environment made for a perfect day out.

As we strolled along the pier, the kids had one craving in mind - sushi! Luckily, we discovered the highly-recommended "Sushi Iwa" right by the pier . We ordered a variety of sushi roll combos and a bento box, and our family thoroughly enjoyed the meal. The service was top-notch, and the atmosphere was warm and inviting.

If you're ever in the area and craving sushi, I highly recommend "Sushi Iwa" for a delicious and family-friendly dining experience. We can't wait to come back! - Dine out Daily Fam -","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-oWVqZcZfLlXdAB8W3pj_n7t72Ib7NhslMTb9&fid=0x0:0xb72764c3574e3c28"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Amy Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvtm7hBqZHDYxXgP_oxkelx2FGhwfW-EuwTv9rdyjxo-_-_8Nq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time here. Fish is fresh and the sushi rolls are good and not too saucy. Presentation is very nice. The salmon belly sashimi is amazing. Sashimi slices are big and not stingy. All the dishes were good. Tuna tataki lacks a little flavour and the tamago is not made in house (I’m very picky about this). Volcano roll was packed with scallop, one of my fave. Service is great and comfortable atmosphere too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOo_QkD28-q0CY0oiCXpiK987UDBbBrjpfxunwo&fid=0x0:0xb72764c3574e3c28"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"Jason C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKpf4N3JCFNkNuH1a-iasLPioAQV9EP7a3fJkgcYHjIb_xGWA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Can't recommend this place enough. Great food and service, we stopped by White Rock on our way to visit Tsawwassen and couldn't be happier with our choice of dining at Sushi Iwa (in fact we went back after a few days).

The aburi sushi is very well priced and tastier than lots of others that I've been to. Donburi are huge with lots of thick cut sashimi in top.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGf1milJKSaRMo2nY_qcc668iQTilE006VNlj_&fid=0x0:0xb72764c3574e3c28"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"New Yorker 2019","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWo8zBH0udV5MZeFVqWqPavyYorpM251wmowK2AXSxxi4tyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food is great, the view is great but if you chose to sit on the pattio all you smell is urine smell from the corner in the picture.   It is not their fault but it needs to be hosed down vigorously and the city should monitor the streets. The chicken was exquisite and all the sauces were amazing :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWzIvJvZ81zfA9uKj2FiLIqGl8Kq32wGhammHc&fid=0x0:0xb7ae71907647f31"],"When":"2024-11-21"},{"Name":"Zainab Udaipurwala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2Qdt43KbOvcDiKYVcu_rlmAWKibytbopxYictiTIngoV3xw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a terrible experience at Kababji. The place was unhygienic, with unclean tables and a generally neglected atmosphere. The food was equally disappointing—bland, and the ingredients didn’t seem fresh. To make matters worse, I found a hair strand on the pita bread towards the end of my meal. When we complained, the staff, in charge, just smiled and didn’t even offer a replacement or a refund. This level of disregard for hygiene and customer service is unacceptable. I will definitely not be coming back and wouldn’t recommend it to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nermin Gendy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZd1bGtKD4_DkVL00SjThNy-PeCx0sChpIdoO0uThh3JceNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at Kababji! The food was absolutely delicious—fresh, flavorful, and generous portions that leave you fully satisfied. The service was outstanding; the staff is incredibly friendly and welcoming especially Zeina. The place is spacious, which makes the dining experience even more enjoyable. The taste of the dishes was exceptional, and the prices are very reasonable for the quality and quantity you get. Highly recommended for anyone looking for a great meal!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jamila R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvmMCoWayA_GJVuOPsQXDlo7T705d_DtLjRESlXk-Lzwh40A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Our recent dining experience was, unfortunately, one of the worst we've ever had. The food was overwhelmingly salty and dominated by an overpowering taste of raw garlic—so much so that it felt like we had consumed an entire pod each. Despite the higher-than-average prices, the portions were small, and the quality of the food was dreadful.

To make matters worse, we found a strand of hair in one of the dishes. When we reported it to the staff, the response was shockingly dismissive—just a brief apology and the plate taken away, with no replacement or compensation offered.

The aftermath was even more distressing. All four of us felt nauseated after the meal and ended up needing medical attention at the hospital. We even informed the staff about how poorly the food was prepared, but no steps were taken to address our concerns.

The food is served rather fast which is good, but what’s the point if it’s tastes awful.
I rarely speak poorly about food, but this experience was nothing short of a nightmare. We won’t be returning—it's simply not worth the risk to one's health.

We were very disappointed with our experience. There was no effort to offer a replacement or ask if we were satisfied with the food. In fact, there was no one available to address our concerns—the staff disappeared inside and didn’t return until most people had already left. The music was turned off while we waited and waited to give our review, despite being the only customers in the restaurant and someone with one small
Shawarma. That alone should have been a red flag, but we wanted to support a new local business and give it a try.

As for the claim that we “licked our plates clean,” this is completely false. Half the food was left untouched because it was simply inedible. We didn’t raise our concerns at the time because no one was there to talk to, and we overheard what sounded like an argument coming from the kitchen. There were only two staff members—a chef and someone taking orders—which is fine if the service is handled well, but it wasn’t.

We also have photos to support our feedback, so this isn’t just baseless criticism. Your response, however, lacks the courtesy of a sincere apology. Instead of addressing the issues, you've resorted to blaming the customer. Offering a replacement wouldn’t have helped in this case—we wouldn’t want to risk ending up in the hospital, longer.

For future reference, disappearing on customers, turning off the music, and essentially forcing them to leave hungry, upset, and feeling ignored is not acceptable. If you had apologized properly and been honest in your response, I might have considered taking down my review after some time. However, your false arguments have only made things worse. Also, regarding your portions—when the food served is a quarter of what’s shown in the advertisements, what do you expect? No one can even get a proper taste before complaining with such misleading presentation. Then u would have replied -  you’ll didn’t eat enough to know its real taste. We were polite enough not to complain about the taste or other issues up to that point, even though we were quite disappointed. However, finding a hair in the food crossed the line. When we finally pointed it out, the staff's response was a dismissive "Sorry, guys," as they took the plate away. There was no effort to address the situation properly or make amends.

Bad after taste, falling sick and now this..we don’t have any familial animosity to blame you unnecessarily…
Not going to reply any further, it’s just waste of my time and shows on your part you’ll aren’t even sorry.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sikander H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNmjTEd9_FxsAT4gVm8dv1nbtMnnm5nSfmZM0TUcGYU3YUn4kC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is some of the best middle Eastern food I've had. The grilled shish chicken tawook has an incredible smokey flaver combined with their garlic sauce. An excellent hand food after a late night out.

Also the portion size is always appreciated.

The manager takes good time to make sure the food is made to perfection and every customer is happy. Will add photos soon🙌

Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMlCkaGB54AylJgyuioKTNdrwaQZvTa-LJy2sGx&fid=0x0:0xb7ae71907647f31"],"When":"2021-6-16"},{"Name":"Perry Browne (PB)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNZHjpqjUI_Q0z3oR0l29FTmPL4dzHamyLG8fk-kxaXR8r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I admittedly was under the impression that this was just going to be a quick grab and go kebab and wasn’t going to be impressed. Glad I stopped here because the food is insanely good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOLa6rbRG4v2ksrF4GxckmD92MfXwlLfFoaOU&fid=0x0:0xb7ae71907647f31"],"When":"2024-11-3"}]

It was farmers market day so we had live entertainment out on the patio. Great bike parking, very tasty beer (like wow). Great flatbread and super friendly smiling staff. Good location on the plaza. Good place to people and dog watch.
Nice job, keep up the good work!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODP9gkSoBxaj_5WmNNE8-V8yXk_exmOMbLyCgE&fid=0x0:0x7dc4ba0a54376e6"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Alberta Dunns","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVN_86ZHKcjcuS4f3vL5nCVA5cQrtOBu9pBWylw4RuP1AtckmXZTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"West coast brewery tour continues…..today we took a trip to White Rock on a full blue bird day in the convertible. After a couple of hours on beach we decided to visit this little oasis in town. Great job 3 Dogs….you impressed us with your beer selection and oh…BTW, the Nathan hot dogs were just like we remembered from Coney Island! Well done, see you soon 🍺😉","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXY0kmdQZQp3bszwCObX8iq6-jdeDDKriIfgzP&fid=0x0:0x7dc4ba0a54376e6"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Ashley Baird","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeDChigTW6duuy3F0zigRDmRgIYsVGjXQd4C-mri6nqk2dFJjs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We always have a blast at 3 Dogs. Service is always great! Katie is absolutely the best, always smiling and working hard! One of our favourite spots to have a drink!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnjItWmnBwBoAStAEnep68q4Nlq5mmbAOzib0L&fid=0x0:0x7dc4ba0a54376e6"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Jonathan Lim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0XULAQTTICU9yubhxOf6QAazqu5J7u-JAt3dMp92YAVNOxfqk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome craft beer! Their new location is really cool with multi-level seating and a nice big patio as well.

They have great snack foods to go with your beer as well. My favorite is their array of hot dogs that always come with a bag of Hard Bite chips!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIiD0RyZ-j-q8dbc8A0xCvdV_sRHw1ArvXNtLl&fid=0x0:0x7dc4ba0a54376e6"],"When":"2022-8-7"},{"Name":"Spencer Shellborn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIgTOwrgCHU7TdTmvP3TEosFUTmsXj8V0Rcuq7OwiAkwU2OPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I are in white rock for the week. We stopped in for some craft beer. I will say this… we were not disappointed. The beer was amazing. The porter was 10/10 my favourite. I did also try a couple different things that I thought looked interesting such as the lemon ginger radler and the berry oak cider. I was amazed, so much so, I ended up getting a growler of the cider. I 100% recommend 3 dogs brewing. My wife and I will return next time we visit the city","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mitch C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUigQKnsqnd6-ECKxiWLF3yOJGPZULiTcrsHXswZ-6rjxY7_wxITQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"2022.05.04 They have moved. But their signage doesn't help. I could SEE the old place from the new one. It's in the courtyard of the new Boss place. Beautiful location. They must be doing well. But the information should be better shared / explained so people other than regulars can read it. Had a chilli dog and a flight and a double IPA... Was all delicious and a bit expensive. Downtown van prices. But the new location has a bit of that vibe. Beautiful but expensive.

Many covis safe tables around and behind the place. Pretty wide selection of beer with a couple gues taps too. These places use the giant cans for rake away (750ml). Had Rosie's (a Raspberry lemon zest wheat beer) and a plate of nachos. They have buzzers so you know when your food is ready but mine didn't buzz, so they came and found me. Thank you! Getting seated without moving the chair was a little tricky (kidding! See the sign on the table). A popular place, it was pretty busy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORQwf7XoBcBhCawDUNhaTHDGl258-z1D46wCrA&fid=0x0:0x7dc4ba0a54376e6"],"When":"2021-5-14"},{"Name":"Patti Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUI_Jud3rc0hbZoDXNHPJCo2_gArLQJcL2r-p_wOdQWSanokMA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friends and I came to do a painting class at this business . We were so excited to see a foot long hot dog on the menu ! The wiener was SO full of flavour! The bun was the exact right size and so so deliciously soft ! It had amazing toppings that were perfect choices . The service was fun and very polite !!! The area feels like you’re downtown but without the noise and chaos ! Absolutely wonderful atmosphere fair pricing and a great  experience! We will be back soon .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnf4y4cUnr0SGejC3TzcFAF7jbXxnM2TMBGcOr&fid=0x0:0x7dc4ba0a54376e6"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"T T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJs0oODkAvERBrISWp0p0g8VwGTl5VkzY9pryevrrHLRPDFdg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped in for a quick pint and a bite to eat. The staff serving the beers were very helpful and let me try a few samples before settling on a Kolsch. They had a nice selection on games while waiting for your food. I appreciated the veggie option (beyond meat) although it could have used a few extra minutes on the grill as it was still kind of cold. Great spot for stopping in with friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOL96k2b85RjVy9wCZcde9pkX2Z8CtoqhlPLFss&fid=0x0:0x7dc4ba0a54376e6"],"When":"2023-12-8"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alan McInnes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCm8qVRpvDNKuamdrhQWTEoat8FiAxK_Mn66iKM4HGcv6_Llvzaw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The regulars may not appreciate my comments as the Five Corners Café is already a pretty busy place, but I think it is one of the best breakfast places I’ve ever been to.  I love the fact that it is a classic family run cafe that means they care about the food and their customers.  The breakfast we had; a Spanish omelette and Huevos Rancheros, were some of the best versions I have ever seen, and the flavours were authentic.  The coffee seems bottomless as my son and I sat there for over an hour and the waitress just kept topping us up.  I understand it has a cadre of loyal regulars and I understand why.  It is what we all want in a local café: great food, good coffee, and a cozy place to hang out with family and friends.  You know a place has a loyal following when there is a wall of longtime customers’ photos on the wall.  I will be back soon, and hope to become a loyal fan.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1kxWojhygJ2jqo4TWlVZFVnjy_Pt1pPFlfx7T&fid=0x0:0x7a550edff6cfb2ec"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"D. Wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCpc5zZbVP2o8XnBOq3v4V9YScG2N-Mg6rPL2UekOE1JOnk_UZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been meaning to check this place out for a while and I’m so glad I did!
Excellent Food and Service. Wonderful 1950’s atmosphere and decor that’s like a window into the past.
I can’t wait to dine here again! Five Stars","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-O-2X7jBBbyjrVNOKMRmgZL9X3GSj_Jio9hpv&fid=0x0:0x7a550edff6cfb2ec"],"When":"2024-7-15"},{"Name":"Patrick Conlan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhh-tSXadAO3qH6JVXDH-I8GzdsB9Yqw6a4lrz3tp9VeYPCm0TWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cash only breakfast spot, good selection of diner breakfast and lunch favorites

My Mushroom and Swiss Omelette was nicely cooked with fresh ingredients.

Staff are lovely.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6sADVTyCLIxhTxpbYhZdQfKQNb1uAhNU4jNDH&fid=0x0:0x7a550edff6cfb2ec"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Ryan Kelly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRC_Uab4RSpvE1EVVfFvDRTt4t4nmnwTDewRzwEP9cbWSv0A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Without a doubt my favourite breakfast spot. The family that runs the place are absolute dynamite. A mother and two daughters that have kind hearts and fantastic energy. I’ve run the menu at this point and they are all bangers. The flannel hash though is stellar. Special shout out to Shannon who rocks the front of house… I don’t know how she does it but she remembers each and everyone one of their regulars. A proper old school diner that a pal and I are happy to call home.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jen S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6yRDu3X2tYRf22dSS2L1HUQ_---VPNFSZyVWrJW6KXuGpfNIHww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sure there are fancier/healthier places all around the city. But this place provides the true Canadian diner experience. I love to support places like this, in hopes that they don’t completely disappear and the memories remain. My daughter and I thoroughly enjoyed our visit. Vintage decor, good portions, tasty food and good service. We will be back :)

P.S. Cash only.
Plenty of free parking in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVnXhfx_UiBRbrBsQDLKH8FPyvazCS8PhikVT5&fid=0x0:0x7a550edff6cfb2ec"],"When":"2022-2-1"},{"Name":"Ally Lowry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAcOCBddw2ROr7ek8hFPPX_HGTMZa-LtxWU6NWx1DGnXfnOdU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved it here! My boyfriend and I went to get pancakes and wanted a diner kind of feel for breakfast. Five corners did not let us down! The food was great, the decor was super cute and cool, and the owners were so sweet and friendly. Definitely going back :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rick Pappin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6m2v9un-K5EFFDGVAKhdVofvtLFal44K8NjQm1-hej06K9jVs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Best "hidden away Greasy Spoon"...! We always look for these Gems from the past... N O T E :  Cash Only . . . !  That's OK, experienced travelers know to be prepared!
Well worth the drive 🚗 and search to find it","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaAqQsKaxEePTtGguNeCtr9llUDWhK1ncNDzsF&fid=0x0:0x7a550edff6cfb2ec"],"When":"2023-6-25"},{"Name":"Andrea Pino-Olivares","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDHfW5CQIShXG0Q2Pw9uW-j6d53mSzuaPbenQG8OgvnErBa6_0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here and had a unique experience. Nice atmosphere despite the little space. Friendly service. Seems to be faster if you are a regular. Will come back and bring friends for brunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0khFGimtvZmJdblF8BKMuhLB1H2wzHJLIx11q&fid=0x0:0x7a550edff6cfb2ec"],"When":"2022-3-9"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Alina Rogers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0d-m_KkCmIwKhbw39E6r-FXjcoAi618TrjJXFKEZHSeW2aNU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good little spot in White Rock. First time we tried Tacofino. We ordered the Happy Hour Chips & Dips ($10), the Crispy Chicken($18) Burrito and the Fish Burrito ($18). Everything tasted great. Service was good. Portion sized was good IMO, I’d say similar burrito size to Chipotle probably a little smaller as it’s less loaded.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrXiEoqfMY5ONvvFYE0Xaf6dJVNVl93EZbwOHK&fid=0x0:0x6d82a0d6fcdcb46"],"When":"2024-6-22"},{"Name":"Jack Peters","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6tuotdk1_dATGiaaY-PEJ7e94vRmmulQ4gtBej1xawfyQQRAu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely one of the best meals in the neighbourhood. Great happy hour prices, beer on tap. Would pick this business as a go to place. Casual atmosphere with an outdoor patio for the warmer days.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOoyinnlg2vcDHcTspkeEbqXZaeLw2iu1ovH37&fid=0x0:0x6d82a0d6fcdcb46"],"When":"2024-11-27"},{"Name":"RTL","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrBA0X4_3k1lfZjU3nbB1JjLtAoENl2g6UnPFtRkoVABMgGg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I always try to give restaurants a second try before I write a review. This was our second attempt at trying the new recently opened location. Ordered 2 burritos one combo to go! The person taking the order couldn’t get the order right - one barbacoa and one super veg, pretty simple! Really disappointing- I received 11 over cooked tater tots , and two of the most crappist burritos ever! Ingredients were lacking - inconsistency compared to the Vancouver location. My super veg was all rice and beans no tempura yam. Won’t be wasting another dime here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmV50nKOSpjj1-OV8oYuKU1BeCF22O1BfT68sg&fid=0x0:0x6d82a0d6fcdcb46"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Harrison Peers, Realtor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLj2rlpKO7KJT6UpX1QjjJ2eHUX0QnhMR1u4oJxXhKAEkrBbvS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is great, vibes are funky, and service was excellent. I rate the crunchy chicken burrito an easy 9.5/10 - This is the place to be!! Probably the new best “fast” dining option in White Rock.

Their happy hour & daily deals also look to be great value! Can’t wait to try everything out.

The burrito was better than the photo shows - I dove right in - it’s absolutely worth it, and a great size.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtwHARM1fQXIHWMAiLZ8W3tr8nkj2CwEWxnKDN&fid=0x0:0x6d82a0d6fcdcb46"],"When":"2024-5-16"},{"Name":"Afsana Tabibi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzp6b-InW6PAK15vNh9v8ga8zbWmNjzR0Dlq305Lj5B3Ej-HpL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"My husband and I went to the Tacofino in Tofino two years ago and we aren't sure why the tacos there tasted way better than the tacos at every other Tacofino we have since tried.

Nevertheless, this is a new location so they are still working out the kinks, for example, they brought out my husband's barbacoa gringa first, then about 4-5min later brought out the three other tacos (i.e., yam, crispy chicken, and chorizo), and then 1min later the nachos we ordered. The tables are small and when they bring all the food out at once, it makes for an awkward dinner. Additionally, we waited for about 10min after ordering to ask our waitress if we were to fetch our own water or if they were going to bring it to our table. The service is really slow, but like I said they are still working out the kinks of a newly established location.

In terms of the actual food flavors, the nachos and the barbacoa gringas are absolutely delicious 🤤 but the tacos are try-hards and you end up with a heavily greasy mess. I might try their bean gringa since I heard that it isn't too greasy, but I'm not rushing to go back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFGfxbQphovRqR3VcOP6Q8bcTSkXwTnMI5ckdN&fid=0x0:0x6d82a0d6fcdcb46"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"Alexander Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrEd-3C35RnZfOBALnIaHIXpbR4PG2JnDJvXbczsh8rAohi5OH4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Tacos are great, wings are good too. I love tacofino, but this one left me feeling more than a bit frustrated when the staff did not tell me I was 2 minutes off from happy hour, and let me order wings for $20 instead of $10… I asked the staff and they did that knowingly.

Edit: Management replied so I will cut you guys some slack and raise the rating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCKERBOKjxNhCscoW5HtxvKUa_SSCwlUY7I36g&fid=0x0:0x6d82a0d6fcdcb46"],"When":"2024-7-10"},{"Name":"Dan Lorenz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa_eC-U0kV3zmKzI4E1osV8_z7ABPGLuq9fXQNAmdOuVhfXvuZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place serves amazing Tacos and Nachos. I personally get 2 fish tacos and the Macho platter every time I’m in there. Almost met with a great attitude and great meals. A big shout out to this location! Keep up the great work. ❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ivette Jacobson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKj4P9dqkjeIRN6e0B0zwNsCh9snjUU2P6ppuHRZKqKRCZ-Yg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"First time I was welcoming for a nice cashier and waitress who actually asked me about how like the food, very nice, friendly kid!
The chicken was awesome fresh and quite tasty!
Now they serve chicken breaded tacos 😞
They don’t like if you don’t tip.
The main girl unfriendly.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Sara Roberts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs6HumbJHwsBlt_8qVpXfL6FPGZetj8rJTvFAm7_XTufdEPiHfhg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Lebanese food!
We always stop by here when we go to White Rock. The price is fair and the quality + portion is always great! We often order take out but ordering in restaurant is good too! Staff are friendly and the store is clean with nice ambience. I love the chicken shush tawook platter with Tabbouleh salad and my boyfriend loves the chicken shawarma platter with Tabbouleh salad too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmLgttRI1j_1qRku1KbFSU5EKuL2S6C8Wi-zT_&fid=0x0:0xc3d1b3914f494ea"],"When":"2024-11-14"},{"Name":"Foodieatlarge Ou812!","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUV5WjUsogcvFcdpk650G44_1nDSsUxfDfJjUXorbWVcHcaIaXI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Aka: Crispy Falafel.
Decent food, fresh ingredients, lotsa variety. Choices & options r plentiful and flavours r classic for this cuisine.
One of the cleanest kitchens I have seen. Bathroom could be checked on , aside from that, a gr8 place for a quik nosh.
Very comfortable dining area.
Bright street views with large windows. $$+","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_69sfqpBA_PRTFV0zopHUqdzIwYqvmR4RlML7&fid=0x0:0xc3d1b3914f494ea"],"When":"2024-4-11"},{"Name":"aotm vhiam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlFvmPRiJUmkpz02ZHTW2VHjIc34VNQpDvWQ4wekuZ97OL0iRNqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"That was scrumptiously delicious.  Falafels are light and crispy.  Love the Tabouleh.
Back again for shawarma wrap and plate, both as good as ever. Great to be able to depend on consistency.
Birthday family dinner, ordered Shwarma Platter, so good, so complete, drinks, salads, sauces, so easy. No preparation, minimum cleanup.  Thanks again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvS9EX5xEJnOmmv_ZY4i1gbfZBaYO2ZEuxhYBV&fid=0x0:0xc3d1b3914f494ea"],"When":"2021-12-13"},{"Name":"Hassan Makhlouf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYREoqUkazVJoJhrGCrjS5g1lIMahzFkhsZA1Ir7O3A-YofJyb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice place to get shawrma, donair and other delicious Lebanese food. Service were great and staff so friendly. Seating is inside and out side. Location is very nice while heading to beach road.i like it","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNS8W94lD_FRLFqz4iOl7aUA-jSy2y2RdWALvb5&fid=0x0:0xc3d1b3914f494ea"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Yen Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyAvN2C5T1q2J6fu0sEvKIZg90A5kizb5W6RpIOGWgUYujcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"As a regular customer, I came there on November 20, 2024, to dine in and ordered a rice plate.  When the cashier rung in the order I became suspicious of the high tax.  She said that a Greek salad was extra.  I was confused because the menu stated that a salad is included in the price of the rice plate.  After a brief exchange, the other food attendant, the one with the cloth around her head, yelled at me saying that a tabouleh and Greek salad was extra.  I was still confused because the menu stated otherwise.  I decided to order a wrap because it was straightforward.  They could had made more money with a rice plate if they knew how to talk to me appropriately.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zahra Mousavi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwyNJqbUb8Y9TN7_vnMJQY_c2FxHkyxUrsTeHlxXhOGdx7vw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The environment was very clean and the food was great. Customer service was good. The portions could have been bigger but overall recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNg4BOtnnQoZ5CZiZlvd0AwZhv0Iy58cVB0MNV2&fid=0x0:0xc3d1b3914f494ea"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"Susannah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqbq5yVN7tyGe8Qtjl7pKFEWguL9k4jiBww765LZapdPgH_x8P=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Chicken kabob came wrapped in burnt plastic on the plate and had been barbecued in the plastic as it was cooked into the chicken. The cook clearly forgot to take the kebab out of the plastic. This gave me flashbacks to eating meat cooked in plastic when camping with girl guides. This ruined what would have been a good meal. Very disappointing and disgusting. Will not be back or recommend to anyone. The food took 20 minutes longer but this is not a big deal compared to the plastic kebabs we got served.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO169WtQOIoT6jGAB0vAs47ihbSv7xDqMScr0uJ&fid=0x0:0xc3d1b3914f494ea"],"When":"2021-6-27"},{"Name":"Rabiya N. Rana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXA_d6sgJ707qTpjrKjThybnnWjlvtRpnn-xtlZQoYX0XGBKMFmw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just loved it. It was simply delicious. The chicken in Shwarma and Shish Tawouk was just sooooo soft and juicy!! Perfectly made. Salad was fresh and crunchy. The ambiance was lovely too. Neat and clean area to dine in and washroom with a nappy changing area for babies for a life-saver for me, as many shawarma places do not usually have it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJUTgcmrk1ya0Y6ysTu2f0vO-DG8NVJQ8_P6cO&fid=0x0:0xc3d1b3914f494ea"],"When":"2022-3-20"}]

[{"Name":"Sejal Prasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5IrvUjGJFOK1JCNkVPHfFsBJKF7NFIUYQQ337eAtOEqvYHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I enjoyed this resturant overall! The taste of the fish was tasty however,  I wish they were larger for the price and less battered. The chips were good as well but a little bit too greasy. The service was great and the views are very peaceful!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCr1ge667VOiqmHBRlUflIUQzJ-8_tAtj_9ON2&fid=0x0:0xa3948341a2f3f746"],"When":"2024-9-5"},{"Name":"Lanie Zulueta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIjacOZZNFIlv1T1yr25Te9nNNi1G78MhV6gOT7cCRO1Lr8sw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was awesome! The Fish N Chips and Calamari were fried just right. Crisp and moist. The chowder was really tasty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHa5GCPBNy4BX44jO8rW9UuaPfe4pzBBgashrs&fid=0x0:0xa3948341a2f3f746"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"JF Hedge Trimming Ltd.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7L8RXQwc9sRg6r76xgHxm91YafwmxDn7959dr4kvlVTc60Gw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Very friendly staff, nice atmosphere overlooking the water. Halibut and fries had great flavour. Where they can improve on is follow up quality service while eating and checking in more often to see if needing more drinks. Fish and fries were really really greasy. Took forever to receive check and with paid parking about to expire went inside to ask to pay. Quality of food over price wasn't really worth it but the restaurant was pleasant to visit nonetheless. May go back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOY1K7cQf3rfYdAZoJGxuuRZ3etjw7ubEyJqB5t&fid=0x0:0xa3948341a2f3f746"],"When":"2023-8-9"},{"Name":"MG_FXV","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiigFyUNoiwP5bHSXlNRrOpnatj6VSziAvS6zd1X48n-qBzP4n=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Not the best or worst fish and chips we've had. We love the fries... not salty, nice and crisp. Plus the tartar sauce. Delicious. During our visit it wasn't that busy so it was great we had our orders right away... it will take longer when there's more costumers because it is run by two people. Waitress/cashier and the cook. Waitress was not too bad. She got us what we needed. The inside is a little bit outdated and disorganized.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuSiDOiwmqQ3hBwGjqbCUzYYiOAKGY8qNpjrlM&fid=0x0:0xa3948341a2f3f746"],"When":"2021-8-25"},{"Name":"Kalvin B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpsxIHtx566TqZDCrOwTsGe-Qx8XrNmTCi9ANsvGYucbEFtt4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good tartar sauce, the cod was flaky and battered nicely. The fries where nice
The bacon cheese burger had a frozen patty, but its a fish and chip place so forgivable.
The view was gorgeous you could see the pier and water.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Eggers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIDquKA7aCOhLK2YF_IjsrtgsgukjFSjIDkyDDyeAaX6gu_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"HUGE pieces of fish that were nicely battered with out excess grease. The fries were the kind that are dipped in a batter before being fried. Oh so crispy!!!! I live 80 miles away down in Wa state by Marysville and will for sure go back with my wife. A 3 piece fed us both to a happy full tummy. We dined in and the host was very nice and attentive. Other shops looked ok, but this was the best. The cash option below says per person but the meal was 33.99. So for two ppl, cheap date!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kg grewal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdDVeJr2DFqvYet3dfK8Tk141zTUMX-sqFC-TKloPTI_VJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff is really nice and attentive. The wait on the food is not that long either. Docks fish and chips has great prices and honestly, I think it’s fair for the food. The tartar sauce is a must!
10/10 definitely coming back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Calvo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPT3u9F4tno_QsaZnTJpTTUYEZMap2izOcH46FvI0ZiRtiHulf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m from Brazil and I’ve never eaten a fish and chips so good in my entire life. We have good fish in my country but here… It is perfectly crispy and the fish almost melts in your mouth. The prawns are very good as well and it comes with a salad so you can have a balanced meal with healthy and unhealthy food lol","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAwTk56VP_MddpXd9scpT8FKrtwF3t5afS1zTq&fid=0x0:0xa3948341a2f3f746"],"When":"2023-7-4"}]
