user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ben Klein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9R820F28I0t3X369CmfDuA-HVVZc86vM9sktLJOY_Gt7-9IRU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a delightful extension of the Bahn mi Tres Bon in Richmond. Same owner, slightly different menu but overall just a wonder. The restaurant has a nice overall theme and decor. Gentle blues, nice whites, it leans into its french accents a lot. Just like Richmond they have a number of character pieces scattered around the restaurant (an old white wood tea cart, local art, and more) all designed to make you feel comfortable. It has a larger view of the kitchen and you can see them prep from the booths and front area.

Food is delicious. The pho is always rich with the 24 hour broths. The bahn mi is great and filling. They also have a number of spring and salad rolls that are great to try. My kids have the mini flight that is a small spicy beef bahn mi with a small chicken pho. They still have the macarons up front and my kids love picking them out as a desert.

Its great to sit here. Sometimes it can be a bit chilly on a rainy day but pleasant to just while away your time in. Bathrooms are clean and the overall establishment feels friendly and well maintained. The sounds of the restaurant and nearby diners never really seems to intrude on my thoughts.

Parking is available from the mall the restaurant it is in, or from the street nearby (usually full but you can get lucky). There are bike racks and it is on a bus line route. A fairly easy walk if you are anywhere in white rock.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiwZC9-1-Y6-2Te0V3ameur9M1CvNoS04Oh3ms&fid=0x0:0x2a8cf15f9e78e86e"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Keresna Bradley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFL4Gy14bplhQhEXbmVpDttucEOZGeSD1VNXBGULacoWk5Vv4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From start to finish this is the best dining experience I have had in ages! My daughter and I ordered a few smaller dishes to share and still brought home leftovers.

The salad rolls were delicious and peanut sauce was the perfect accompaniment. We had the trio of mini Banh Mi sandwiches and these fabulous! They baked their own bread daily and it shows. The star was the Duck confit Bao buns. These are hands down the best bao buns I have ever had anywhere.

We wanted the full experience and ordered the tea service and dessert. It was all amazing especially the Passionata. It was full of fresh passion fruit flavour, and my daughter loved the rich chocolate opera cake. The tea was so good I didn’t add any milk or sugar, it didn’t need it at all.

The ambience and service were extraordinary , we couldn’t stop saying what a wonderful evening we had. We WILL be going again! This place is a gem ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcT1FKX5ViVuLLM2eyi6CEmh9wm4jeRMmay5HR&fid=0x0:0x2a8cf15f9e78e86e"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"John Dang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwUBimuyg2RIoNxj2yjF92YNHG4hHZxyoeLPt_4WtTH62MRw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was an absolute delight to discover this incredible Vietnamese cuisine, made with high-quality, authentic ingredients. Their banh mi was perfectly crispy and bursting with flavor. Having lived in California, this place truly raises the bar. I had a fantastic time with my family, enjoying dishes like beef stew, pho, banh khot, spring rolls, and bun bo hue. I can’t wait to come back on my next visit to Vancouver!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNW8Zc4pcyBiiQ12tqT-zm7ijQwd0FWAlOVfeRx&fid=0x0:0x2a8cf15f9e78e86e"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"万竹","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnsirj2w9NgKxB4GQZVGrpbGaK60xEpSi0cVmeVC0yEcSSkqbG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of my favorite places uptown white rock.  The food is amazing, service is hilarious sometimes, and the atmosphere a bit funky and very clean and organized.  I must have come here 6 times by now an old keep coming back.  We asked the waitress who we can talk to about not paying the bill and she casually said "the cops".  Then i died.  The soft shell crab ban mi is a must try imo.
Bon Appétit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLlyu6QiXlvz6RRUvZbAnbLvLz9EaUepAavdIr&fid=0x0:0x2a8cf15f9e78e86e"],"When":"2024-5-23"},{"Name":"Yuki Chin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgPmyvA2BNqgUzNUpeq8PkwjRislBWVbWQ9MeOGPDSzARy97eC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service is good and fast but the foods are decent.  To me the beef and broth flavour isn't there.  Just bland and salty.

Restaurant is super clean and comfortable.  Feel like high class restaurant.  Price also affordable and not too expensive.  Food portion is not big though.  I ordered their Vietnamese coffee, and I don't like it.  Taste too bitter because the condensed milk they gave isn't enough.

Overall foods are fine but just lack of beef flavour in their meat and broth.  If they can make changes on this, I'm sure this place is a good place to go for Vietnamese cuisine.  I like PHO but at this moment this place isn't my favourite place to go due to the above-mentioned reason.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcCT9WW01SSPwjQE34r8Rf9nF2bILzUoQdCDYo&fid=0x0:0x2a8cf15f9e78e86e"],"When":"2024-4-21"},{"Name":"Catarina Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKax4d4e7hhy5Iw3AGIqhlLoUri__zGdpp_VINEdvai2u7E2c3AA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful decor and cozy atmosphere. Friendly staff greet you at the door as soon as you enter. Small patio that is nice for these beautiful Summer evenings. Peace Arch Pilsner is a must try. Will be back soon and recommend to friends. This is my first time reviewing a restaurant but I felt compelled to given my great experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdGzLhW-E6axOvzCXcBV5Saz1bOQfK-4ilKCKH&fid=0x0:0x2a8cf15f9e78e86e"],"When":"2023-7-3"},{"Name":"Michelle Harrison PREC*","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeBKgoJCUMylGWh_ZJgovCxhQ4PLjEs9gsYU7V6w_lfhxkLmLX=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lemomgrass chicken bowl was bursting with flavour.
Food came out fast. Sauces added extra pop.
Restaurant is extremely clean, service was friendly, speedy, and helpful in deciding what to order (as it all sounded so good).
Highly recommend.
Beautiful atmosphere, decor was really on point with the French influence.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXjjuAxFE67LwcBMkY4HoppL_Ck_X6x5HtVp3B&fid=0x0:0x2a8cf15f9e78e86e"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"TAYLOR RUBY","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgNKXOHgh8k-DtDwLOUPn9m1-vO2HovUK2e3JE3t06VfSlXZ18=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a bit of a phõ critic— I will say after eating at various Vietnamese restaurants through New York, Montreal, Toronto, Vancouver, Seattle, and beyond; Bánh Mì Très Bon is the best I’ve ever had! NO expense has been spared when it comes to atmosphere plateware ingredients, and quality of dish!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4YVUYk3UovtyyROX2l9XoDCsqBitvCQPSeqgX&fid=0x0:0x2a8cf15f9e78e86e"],"When":"2024-7-5"}]

[{"Name":"Perry Isidore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIS_JR0bXwG2vYtVFsLKG3jRQ-YLp0jm18HvP3gHez1lDznQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A bit late with my review, nevertheless I took notes at the time. I ordered a smoothie variation to what was on the menu and someone came out the kitchen to insure they got my order right. The picture I added is before I ate them btw.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmRtVC2IExqAAelUJ4-5FP9YvmnT8rj1niuEr3&fid=0x0:0x9ffac3bfc27ad9c4"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Rhea Chand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2ZXUFu3n61mHvuybWDvqea_UJcuwhKZm-h6X4Qmicup6v0ujz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food here is soooo good!!  I came here one time one a whim since we were in the area and was craving Chinese food. Ever since I’ve been wanting to come back, specifically for the stir fried fish with green onion. I came back again on Labour Day weekend with my family and ordered the: Hot & Sour soup, lamb stir fry with green onion, chicken fried rice with egg and the stir fried fish with green onion. We all finished everything within minutes because it was SOO GOOD!! You may look at the prices and may be a little taken aback, but the prices are %100000 justified because the portion sizes and amount of meat you get is WORTH IT. [{"Name":"Sarah Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5Iz1KR8kmG8qjkIsSukhtm-U1cED21Gn5azpb95699-x6i8VC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update:
Has AC, coleslaw was good! Everything as my previous review, we tried haddock vs halibut to l tonight, definitely sticking with halibut in the future!!!

Our go to fish n chips!

-----

Halibut and chips was great, the cabbage in the coleslaw was very bitter though 😂. Tar tar sauce didn't have any pickles but taste was there.

The bisque was a bit watery but the taste was good, not alot of stuff in it though but I would order again!

A bit hot today and it was pretty hot and bright in the restaurant, probably going there again on a less sunny day as they keep the doors open.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMh1GxMfIVsm49jBdMbAx0qaqkIzzclYA5_Ct9&fid=0x0:0xa782385e4c92b6f0"],"When":"2023-4-29"},{"Name":"Tayyaba Omar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOnbL5d4TacOaGi2tmt32gV3GfwXDcSagH_8GTDAwwGM4ti1e1Kw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"So I’ve ordered first time from this restaurant 2 piece fish and chips the fish was really tasty but not crisp at all as I was expecting 😔 and there’s no tarter sauce too I don’t know I I’ve to order it separately or what so but the fish 🐟 was tasty 😋 it was a takeout order","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSyMCZ-kSYW7hrL2pey0RYec5DC8mx81p4D_4r&fid=0x0:0xa782385e4c92b6f0"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Aaron T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6yeVYoOYlrWiU4-xdpCz0WgE82XOpObn1iG8FrHVsKVO78q4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here to do some repair work and the owner kindly treated us to lunch. The food almost made me wish I paid for it! Far better quality than cockney kings or white spot. Delicious crispy fish, satisfying fries, and a decent slaw. The fish was really the star though, every bite was tender flaky and savoury with that fantastic batter. Would gladly stop by when I'm in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwiHV7ekkLKYCRiJKcBirbcIrJhtbvg-GtdoK3&fid=0x0:0xa782385e4c92b6f0"],"When":"2021-3-10"},{"Name":"Alexi Machado","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpsDcC61xPzNiSXtvbvJkdZ8qbcWpIrDk7i52TJ_Ly4DSa2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I went last Sunday to this place thinking about one of the many great fish and chips establishments in White Rock
At 4.30 pm the place was empty, not even one customer
I should have left right away but I gave them the benefit of the doubt, terrible mistake!!!!
I wanted to order 2 pieces of Haddock and chips to go, unfortunately the Haddock was not available, only cod or Halibut
I should have walked away but I ordered the Halibut
$ 30 and 20 minutes later I went home and found out 2 pieces of fish with not batter only panko pan fried and a bunch of fries unevenly cooked, some burned and others raw
Needles to say that it was the worst fish and chips that I ever had and I will not patronize this place anymore
The smile and manners of the lady taking the order was the only positive thing about the place","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCKXpiCbZIR47KVNFRd-j2NtIyOsX2pvk_KAfiRozRkejYhZUopw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"tasty and warm authentic butter chicken and crispy fish and chips. And everything for a  beautiful price too! On top of that, the nan bread is obviously homemade. Delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOe5R3w0eIEI08GD0FMVvcLE-pYJX3O0NXBOhaQ&fid=0x0:0xa782385e4c92b6f0"],"When":"2024-2-10"},{"Name":"Julie B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4pd43YT5KSqkORSPaVbra7_KcodZ1kkwID5yaolZD_WuCOEiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had to make a run to Whiterock and took a chance that they were open today for take away! I am happy to say YES!
I had the Halibut special with a side of their house made tarter sauce. I missed the Cod special they ran but so wanted to try this place out.
The piece of halibut was a nice size and super flaky. The batter was nice and light, not over battered and the chips, I've never met a chip I don't like, LOL. I literally ate them in the truck.
Now I want to go back for the cod but I have to bring the family.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMcCBmLPGuTF_SPgCI6IQUfArS-OHBnv1t1AGlD&fid=0x0:0xa782385e4c92b6f0"],"When":"2020-6-1"},{"Name":"Briana Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1-KgT4Jf4crVSUTRDqIvcpfJZr-3I87dfs1U2YAhmIngTwipV5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the cod and chips and it was really really delicious!!! [{"Name":"Bharat J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUD9dbY4qAQ2dPsCPfXMrxD0qc5XH1sAucyAeLDGfoZYUZ50a0L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best pizza in white rock! The dough is so soft and the toppings are always fresh and flavorful. I especially love the bhangra bliss. The staff is also very friendly and accommodating. Cheers!! 🍕🍕🍕","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvjsVNR1_-da_PZk7J8KttEWE-J4GSF4ATMLW4&fid=0x0:0xcb58bd7e7da41999"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Justine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJM8iN-NzRSxuCg9Ni8IcmqyJ8-52Np1VjihB9fffmJOWkFgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is a gem hidden in plain sight.  It's essentially the same as Ojas Blend. Everything I've tried is delicious and the pizza is ready in just 15 minutes.

The care put into the preparation is evident. I was told later that they let the dough rest for 72 hours which explains why it's soft and airy and doesn't leave that heavy feeling in my stomach afterwards. They said the resting process aids digestion.

There is a wide variety of toppings which taste very fresh and are prepared with care. I'm happy to order straight off their menu because the flavours are unique yet perfectly balanced. I'll keep coming back. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWFHOAKPCntJwy48ABbzv29zoCHvxmS7Q7VwEe&fid=0x0:0xcb58bd7e7da41999"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"Thomas Canale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXI86Srvqkt9rsTZVzzifeScuS77fy_Mt5gtnpRNPlkxb3BeeCh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered their pizza for the first time today and it exceeded all expectations. Our entire family really enjoyed how light and fluffy the crust is. And they have a great variety of flavours. This will definitely be our regular pizza joint in White Rock.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOx2G8V_1Soj2-CbiHfYPaCDBkWnhuANDBfFpDV&fid=0x0:0xcb58bd7e7da41999"],"When":"2024-5-11"},{"Name":"Arsh Ganda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS1zbxhJkQXGEvE_g0GKRAkfFnPiXs924BOqMffkO9PKSB_mlmzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Rebel pizza is absolutely fantastic. The tomato sauce is so fresh, the dough is light and fluffy. Can't go wrong here.

You can tell the owner really cares about his product. He wanted to know if it was our first time, if we enjoyed it, and even offered some samples. They're doing all the right things here. Can't wait to come back with more friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Twitt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXT_3gq4N9txIEAhqc4DUH0F7pBK3pfMV23ecJc5ZhYkav9g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What is a pizza? It's not that complicated. Crust, sauce, cheese. And yet, this place elevates all three to something approaching the sublime.

Ordered a pepperoni, the one with the beets and the goat cheese, and the underground Roots a white pizza with potato etc.

Every element was as good as you could ever dream. The gentleman in the back who made the pies Is a humble artist. This guy knows his stuff.

The reviews convinced us to check it out. The pizza convinced us to write a review. Keep up the good work! This is hands down the top pie in the lower mainland.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_t0DUUjbKsqRMRiatnNJocspMAoDyhX6axqo4&fid=0x0:0xcb58bd7e7da41999"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"P S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIE-ZeKWjdGUOdFFYG9bCcoFfhA4XKC5-KKed7AqYcsKpN_-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best pizza place in White rock/South Surrey. The crust was perfectly crispy yet chewy, and the toppings were fresh and flavourful. I especially enjoyed the creative combination of ingredients in the specialty pizza I ordered. The service was friendly and efficient. I was also impressed with the restaurant's commitment to using organic and fresh, sustainable ingredients. It's great to see a business that cares about both flavor and ethics. Highly recommend!!!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAG6kvZw207AbN_70O0Zw5wWGWC4KeNc2i4yv3&fid=0x0:0xcb58bd7e7da41999"],"When":"2024-1-18"},{"Name":"Annie P.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhpP-7O0cZuyOA3naj1Fvo_Osh3xlXLw3XoqnG-4eNrM_m0JC8Zw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I recently tried out this place for the first time. We just got a medium pizza to-go and absolutely loved it. Generous amount of toppings which were tasty and fresh, and the pizza dough was soft and chewy! The owner seemed like a very nice guy, too. He definitely went above and beyond in every aspect while I was there waiting, and I really appreciated it. Definitely coming back for sure!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOPmFiV6TtkfM7r8Ou6-OPMnp80m7Hu3JMKXb3w&fid=0x0:0xcb58bd7e7da41999"],"When":"2024-3-10"},{"Name":"Sam Parker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdb49TVZo5VxB4TOrVOWIrBCCGD7v4mDpBAhmIOWg8vreeSoAk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just love this place! I’ve tired from almost every location around but this place definitely has the best pizzas. Generous toppings, lip smacking delicious, fresh ingredients, great customer service, very reasonable prices. I mean it’s just 5 stars all the way. It’s a hidden gem. Tired almost every pizza they have over the months and not one of them has disappointed me. So flavourful! Give it a try, you won’t regret it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIw6uco6EsLsniJ83ndghIsI0yq5LJizl0x6la&fid=0x0:0xcb58bd7e7da41999"],"When":"2024-4-17"}]

The lady there is extremely sweet and smiley as well. Really happy to support this business.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV57Kgxo8ZzwDEfp3wNHVpKBdvw4gwQDsQ81msO8zNVNGklGydl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Absolutely piss-poor, I asked for a Donair platter which in Ontario and everywhere else in Canada means you get a Donair wrap with fries and a salad, out here they gave me a phone full of meat and rice and three quarters of a flatbread. When I told her this is not what I ordered I wanted a Donair and not some mix plate she argued with me even though I'm the customer and told me that this is better yet this is not a wrapped Donaire like I want it I do not see the Donair in this plate. Also instead of offering to give me what I actually wanted they just handed me this crap and told me to have a nice day so this is the last time I will ever go there, it's unfortunate that there is absolutely no place in BC that offers a good traditional Donair that actually run by people who's country it comes from","Images":null,"When":""}]

Thank you so much Penang!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2bk4dtzecANXbvp1mnhFZDCpZdg77Y56eI8Pv\u0026fid=0x0:0x4cf87250e05e2a14"],"When":"2023-11-19"},{"Name":"Darlene Salceda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVc-YJi_5Pk-m6viD1FUcqIuqew1cWXWE19Ixo0SfaVRuZAVtB1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"came here for the first time to get a quick meal after the gym and ordered off their lunch combo/specials. my partner got the sesame chicken and I got the beef and broccoli. the food was absolutely delicious and quite a generous portion for the price, they even came with soup! our server was very kind and attentive and I found the atmosphere quirky and homey. definitely a hidden gem that I’ll come back to whenever I’m in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3EYAoMbl3Ecdr-fnv99cR02rFB2wOSXxUCI7F\u0026fid=0x0:0x4cf87250e05e2a14"],"When":"2024-5-2"},{"Name":"Justine H (Sunny)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmvMXm-P_-zaDju2DtLb4mJNuo8OiXNtbw6zPhVOcICWtiAOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was tasty and prices were reasonable! A cute, small casual restaurant with a hardworking waitress. If we lived closer to White Rock, we would probably eat here or takeout more often.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnTkfCu42zdrlOKhJiGuWBQ0SDcDisBxp5hygy\u0026fid=0x0:0x4cf87250e05e2a14"],"When":"2024-1-31"},{"Name":"Dave Conrod","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqCvoz82ecpQy9AFGkYRXRsCcEMKJAODvLIK0XPbSLZ6EQXJOk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went to Penang tonight for dinner. We were seated quickly and did not have long to wait for our food, which was garlic chicken, prawns with snowpeas and vegetable fried rice. Everything was delicious. The hostess advised that they were trying to use less oil and salt. This was apparent as we could taste the flavors of all the ingredients. All the vegetables were fresh and crisp. Speaking of our hostess, she was gracious, polite and pleasant. This was our second trip to Penang we plan on returning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Huimin Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLipitoxW8jjR7OVf09Zf-Z2BVg9ud5hdsBQkGbF1iNs7IRYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time we went to white rock, it is really beautiful city and the people here are very friendly. The pancake dip with the special sauce also very impressed, their dessert is very amazing, not very sweet and so yummy. For sure I will go with my friend again. Highly recommend!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGPUrSHNhXeEf_wLO4DIbpM4jTz4OPBSvbSgHb\u0026fid=0x0:0x4cf87250e05e2a14"],"When":"2022-5-1"},{"Name":"Greg Newman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4wy0IFIOFBoK8D8OddsLS_8pyWCN0lN2RRPLB5-ts35zKEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered Beef with Broccoli, House Special Chow Mein, and Sweet and Sour Chicken. Highly recommended for old customers and new customers alike.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMYA1nIubEw4RiukoPLsbLhe0g2DeXC1MPZHjN\u0026fid=0x0:0x4cf87250e05e2a14"],"When":"2022-5-7"},{"Name":"KRISSY LAYUG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXxUTFrSoTTPtL9DELuLfTUB7URZIHiOmB49GlfJNT2ebo23eY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For me, it is the best noodle in town. [{"Name":"Gazal G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNfRt6AYTRne5R5YyIlS82FlCPvw6yjMF8Wl3AyoUgCtB2w_8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"First review:Very tasty Indian cuisine.ordered 4kind of foods chicken tandoori,chicken beryani,chicken vindalo,beef beryani ,all of them were good 👍🏻
🆘🆘🆘🆘🆘🆘🆘🆘
Second review: l want to add another review, which is more of a warning for others. A few days ago, I went to this restaurant again and ordered food. A lady at the counter told me to come back in 15 minutes to pick it up. I ordered biryani and requested it to be mild, but when I got home and started eating, it was extremely spicy. I could only eat a few bites before I had to stop. She clearly misunderstood my request and made the dish way too spicy for me. Now, a week later, I’m still dealing with a skin allergy reaction caused by the chili. In my opinion, she should work more attentively, with a better and happier attitude, as she has a responsibility in her job. I’d prefer to take back the stars I gave them, and I won’t be returning, nor will I recommend this place to anyone ever again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVJlmRvj88hy_PL2Krg0lZ0kugKnEeqRBA2SbE&fid=0x0:0x1563393f3bb708ff"],"When":"2024-5-23"},{"Name":"DR. I would eat here agsin because her overall service was exceptional!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMJothvjO_S00KW2DjNZE9p171S7tva2hVyAGv&fid=0x0:0x1563393f3bb708ff"],"When":"2024-2-28"},{"Name":"Monster Alive","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBCwzV2fBW-aqNyUDo9PAn82ZOw7tIyMywMxsXRX6v-VhwqPEe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Culinary Delight at Tandoori Flare!

Rating: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

My experience at Tandoori Flare was nothing short of wonderful! The tandoori dishes left me speechless with their impeccable quality and the service was exceptional.

The Amritsari Kulcha was a true delight, each bite filled with deliciousness and a homely touch that made it stand out. The Chicken Masala was equally impressive, bursting with flavors. The naan and rice showcased excellent quality, enhancing the overall dining experience.

It felt like indulging in a feast of homemade delights cooked with love. I am eager to revisit and wholeheartedly recommend Tandoori Flare for a culinary experience that goes beyond expectations.

#Foodie #TandooriFlare #CulinaryDelight","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgeSgNgcHao52ENzDj2iEv2-BoqEO_9qnBONRT&fid=0x0:0x1563393f3bb708ff"],"When":"2024-1-10"},{"Name":"Dan M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUupO-3oR9ShJXvON9gy3p2B_E0v1Clu1L7a1EOYmD9dNrG-hkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ate there for the first time yesterday and all I have to say is amazing! The food was fresh, cooked perfectly, seasoning was done just right and the service was very friendly. Will definitely eat there again and again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vipin Arora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUT50cgktpApBPjWAYGyhFVZCVNAsaS2Walp_G2PL-dgGyln8ah=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I love to share my experience with this restaurant.I to ordered chicken Biryani, butter chicken and naan. Butter chicken gravy is so yum. But they still need to learn how to make chicken pieces. When someone ordered naan from the restaurant. They expect freshly made naan but instead, they sent readymade naan. Chicken Biryani was delicious. Moreover , I made special request in the uber app as well as specially call the restaurant to provide some  Onion and mint sauce along with the food, but they were not courtesy enough to pay attention to my request . I would never order from here again. So disappointed. Restaurant need to work  in kitchen as well as on customer service .

REPLY....

For your kind information i called uber eats to add notes to provide onion and mint sauce . Because there is no option on uber eats to buy it . Then i called two times at your restaurant. The first time they put me on long hold after saying transferring your call to the kitchen. I wait for 5 minutes then i call again. You are providing discount for your own benefits. I am paying for my uber one subscription.
So don't sound like that you are doing some charity or favour on me.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4Z8j3U7f52seFxs5EhM0bCp0wR9VQTmX9L5hC&fid=0x0:0x1563393f3bb708ff"],"When":"2024-4-8"},{"Name":"Amandeep Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXHvQk_t34tvPVZSzEO3pG4_IA84jwl7Cbh3K3aQbBsinlfw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great buffet!! Unfortunately that was all put on a halt, as the rough looking caucasian woman with black hair and Australian-like accent who was minding the front of the house would not allow my fiance and respite client into the establishment unless they showed her 3 pieces of ID and was extremely short and rude to them about it. It was witnessed that she allowed everyone else into the establishment without checking any forms of ID. This is a first for any bar/brewery to screen their guesses prior to entering , as the screening/checking for ID is done prior to a client wanting to order an alcoholic beverage and not at the door. A place to avoid  as this establishment discriminates against people of disabilities. Cannot comment on the beer or food, as my finance and respite client were not allowed in.

I spoke to owner,  Doug, about this incident and he spoke to the black haired girl named "Paige" and Doug stated that "she is actually very nice".   Apparently "Paige", told Doug that my respite client did not have proper forms of ID. My respite client had his govt issued ID, bank card, and student card on him that night.  Unless "Paige" cannot read or see,  these are all considered forms of ID. Delusional owner, gets defensive and argumenative about client complaints and sides with his staff, even though his staff, "Paige", was in the wrong. So much for supporting small businesses.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D Maynard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkR-p8JcTPgrZiGZSR1fRdxLY0t_CUYH_tC306L48RnX_gRO3QPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped by for a quick beverage prior to a show at the Blue Frog. [{"Name":"Jason Chi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPKMARPtkW-qvBT6AAYyJlEjrXtkzgH4VYcK-ppxLf_WcPXzSE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"As mentioned in other reviews, the quality of the food has declined significantly. It was once of exceptional quality, even when it was quite expensive. These photographs were taken ten years ago, when we celebrated my sister’s birthday. Everyone present joined it. However, the taste has completely vanished, even though the appearance of the food has remained unchanged over the past decade. It is a sad state of affairs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORshYn0zmqdvtaCPfpv9yG8o9xndwSIs53fEsx&fid=0x0:0x5f714bea561324be"],"When":"2024-10-31"},{"Name":"Rose Bombshell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDPJkSp3dwoDaWbjLrEu1BlMhSXcKTSKbjTLQs1L-Aza8_2Ro=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Order early!  My favorite roll is the Angels Wasabi.  It is wasabi marinated flying fish roe with cream cheese centre… I grew up in white rock and moved 6 years ago, and came back to take my kids to this epic experience… we were THRILLED with the sushi!  It was exactly like it was 6 years ago.  They are BUSY please order with time, they are perfect tasty beautiful rolls!

We can’t wait to move back!  And be a regular customer again.  Thanks so much for many years of delicious food and memories","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUrlWaf7GjLh7F735OATCqDf2rPUJUqSbE7Is7&fid=0x0:0x5f714bea561324be"],"When":"2024-9-18"},{"Name":"YK Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULDvodznT0NF-su1P11rq3dENQgESqikteySug3kvwX5P9sUb4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Overpriced + Underwhelming.

“Thick-cut” sockeye salmon sashimi were the smallest pieces of sashimi I’ve ever had. It was criminally not worth.

Canadian Sunset and Spicy Scallop rolls were bland, and the spicy sauce was not spicy. It’s bad when you’re not sure what you’re eating even when you know exactly what’s in it. We also ordered only 1 Spicy Scallop but they gave us 2. They didn’t read back the order. Server probably fat fingered on the tablet and didn’t double check.

Only thing that was better was the Handsome Roll. There’s no reason to recommend going to this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNYtE79rL_b1omLpO5bqRBaA6hQp9sVh1JNDmQl&fid=0x0:0x5f714bea561324be"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Tony Lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaC7FCkayh5lB_j-APPM2EYFevXz_LIxUmBrxZsqH7Ac0zfLo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Simply divine. Limited seating, so book beforehand. Server is very knowledgeable and supportive. The fish itself is extremely fresh and has no fishy taste at all. Each dish is crafted with care and excellence. They even had a fish that was almost extinct! A restaurant to experience, comes with a steep price tag, that's for sure! Feel free to ask for the servers recommendations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5gLVHoo3dB20pWsWMzQTgIyaoCLB3YzXWmyE8&fid=0x0:0x5f714bea561324be"],"When":"2024-1-7"},{"Name":"Foodie Vancouver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6n06QAfqStqer1ZgBILsv-fiSHmrGRZuznSS1ny9iQFfb_Ognuw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Until recently, Taka was undoubtedly one of our favorite Japanese restaurants, a cherished place we frequented often. The fresh and delightful selection of sushi and sashimi was simply unparalleled, leaving us with a memorable culinary experience each time.

However, as of late, we have noticed a slight shift in the dynamics of the restaurant. The prices of some of their signature fish dishes seem to have soared, making the overall dining experience somewhat costlier than before. With this, we find ourselves contemplating our orders more carefully, opting for more budget-friendly options and occasionally compromising on our usual indulgences.

Moreover, the growing popularity of aburi-style sushi in many other establishments has taken a toll on Taka's clientele. While the allure of perfectly seared fish and the play of flavors has captivated many, it has also led us and others to explore these alternative sushi spots, drawing us away from our once-beloved haunt.

Another factor that has subtly impacted our preference for Taka is the noticeable decrease in available seating. Previously, securing a table was relatively hassle-free, but now it seems like a challenge. Perhaps the combination of loyal patrons and the restaurant's modest space has led to this spatial constraint, affecting the overall comfort and convenience of dining there.

Nonetheless, despite these recent changes, Taka remains a place with fond memories, and we might still return for special occasions or when we crave the unique flavors that only they can offer. Yet, for now, we find ourselves exploring other Japanese eateries in search of new culinary delights and dining experiences.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMScyHJi_-50cymwxxi8fkW3Ff-CncaXAand8UW&fid=0x0:0x5f714bea561324be"],"When":"2023-7-18"},{"Name":"J D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6nRf7-C791e6o74FBgXg6jbRwc2Hxzd8_Qc8MsQZfN7gcSFxvgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very fresh sushi with a team of professionals creating the experience! We had fresh pieces and a number of roles.

Docked a point because it has very limited seating and although warm welcoming and prompt, I would have liked to see a bit more follow through with diner experience.

Thanks for the lovely meal, Taka’s!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkbMc3kVMPAgBya8pGfxSbijvwpiHNXmGrwM34&fid=0x0:0x5f714bea561324be"],"When":"2023-4-30"},{"Name":"Yulei W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIXJKO6CznL36JhigtJmxd4mTgRGfUdF8E7Ai4qu5wEJy5rvha=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Aburi and rolls were very very good, but appetizers missed the mark","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNAbwQ0p_k4XSj2u9eDBGeN_v3AARgX1ruMf3N&fid=0x0:0x5f714bea561324be"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Antonio Marvuglia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI3NxULlfekZjXz22noxgaqhWytZshZPTZBJ75hEdTHF4vjHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing fish. Pure expression of quality. Very well curated seasonal specials and amazing sake selection. One of the absolute best restaurants in the area. ❤️❤️❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfKhuvOwTFQouvxl6EA_GYLT9878_vUGRAJBjq&fid=0x0:0x5f714bea561324be"],"When":"2024-5-25"}]

The food is disgusting. War Wonton is flavourless, I asked for SOFT veggies they are rock hard. And the pink juice like S&S tastes off, like gone bad but they added more and stirred. Spoke to a lady who claims she is owner.. she brushed me off saying “oh best in town”. I think she meant oldest oil in town, never cleaned!!

You’re better off going to Semiahmoo Mall and grabbing GOOD Chinese food","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBmSF3qgF1S5rfYnM9A9PsTbglAUy6wetV-FNR&fid=0x0:0xf6dc49d0802c00ad"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Farida I","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNMTkKwdOMr4ub_wKd9GYVELWT4EByE1UnnnWA19O9vpX_Flsy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Went for their Sunday Smorgasbord. There was wonton soup sitting on warm in a crock pot, with roughly 12 items in the barely there steam cart. Not sure if every Sunday the menu is different but there was fried rice, chow mein noodles, chicken wings, sweet and sour pork (was not red but light brown in colour), blackbean beef, Ginger beef, Chili shrimp, fried shrimp, sauteed veggies, can't seem to remember the last few items. The dessert consisted of jello (nice to see pineapple flavour), strawberry and cantaloupe, and of course fortune cookies. I wouldn't call it authentic Chinese food, more westernized. Run by a family, with the wife being the main cook in the back, as she was coming in and out to check on the buffet food. Food was mediocre, only giving it 3 stars as we enjoyed the old 90s feel of having a Smorgasbord dinner with the family.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPu5u0hpe_7N395UVNNygYF5Pf4zve7lfLl7-0z&fid=0x0:0xf6dc49d0802c00ad"],"When":"2024-5-30"},{"Name":"diane jaehrlich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKza6mqlAHxKjDCRQHxn9mApe7KkQ7AVpT-NV5JEvnX6bR9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"So disappointed today...we ordered meal for 5..lots of food was nice...price was good ...my egg rolls has a weird stretchy paste in it..no food in in.and so greasy.. don't know what was in it..the fried shrimp was greasy batter..so thick .too much creamy stuff in veggies.?has no flavor...I'm sorry for this poor review. haven't been here since spring... December 11.2024
Sad birthday dinner","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Pineo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIocM6GCiKv07oxRQRA6Go_9p2-lWBnAqBfIjT_Xk-sUR8kkM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For the cheapest Chinese takeout in White Rock/South Surrey it is hands down Silver Dragon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_Aqf3jsyc_lR78_df7fyrpRqJp2t4qe-58TGc&fid=0x0:0xf6dc49d0802c00ad"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Simson Simson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTEGQP7uk5hBSMMfThs8wIBvkkqI2n0IfUI8GPvNPC78PQLneJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Was not impressed. Food wasn't that good. Was dry, only wonton soup was ok. Pricey for what you get! Not clean, especially bathrooms, sticky floors. Would not go again. I don't recommend this restaurant to anyone. You can hear them arguing in the back. Was way better 3 -4 years ago.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zane Chia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbUHixp2t-8Ie1iwnGI1oVgHA-jjBiopeqb4oFGkar05ONPnY3kQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I order an Egg Roll, an Skewer, Onion Cakes and Pan Fried Dumplings for dinner....................The food was sooo gross, they all had a weird smell to it. I almost threw up.

The Egg Rolls looks like a deep fried donut...??? And it had a Sour taste to it, I'm sure it had gone bad.

Onion Cakes tasted like Korean Pancake without any seafood. It was okayish.

Pan Fried Dumplings smelled like the dish pit, they Reeks. They were drenched in milky yellowish oil. I took a bite and threw them out...

Skewer Meh...

The food is not authentic Chinese food and definitely aren't freshly made.

Never ordering from here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsKxLnck96Ptd4Ed6pxamO3EKZzTMto_WGqXgY&fid=0x0:0xf6dc49d0802c00ad"],"When":"2020-8-7"},{"Name":"Jonn Clint","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKeMOexUjWQJfMmeLj1pKkCPe4LDqC81r3yCR1T228INS2kgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We went there thinking it was going to be a decent place as we have done take out from here but when we got there we got our food had little to choose form it was far from fresh and we had to get drinks from a 2L and small plastic kids cups","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCCADOHcfr83Tv_2UwCbOFEoSZLnhOkovAZx3g&fid=0x0:0xf6dc49d0802c00ad"],"When":"2023-10-30"}]

Highly recommend their wings","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLp9IpACWIm4hWalx97iAHvhDbaN5hxdCV4uLz&fid=0x0:0x5b181081ecd11c2f"],"When":"2024-10-17"},{"Name":"Tommy “Powerbuilderwannabe” Xiao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfDi4iFU0b7G0chKTplbE5u7vf20zgZVI66nBpazopRw9TLzij=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is by far my favourite Shanghai restaurant in Vancouver! The food was authentic and delicious. I highly recommend their bifengtang chicken wings, eggplants with tofu and veggies pot, lamb meats on iron skillet, and seitan veggie pot. Especially the chicken wing was a die for dish as the chicken was cooked crispy and coated with bread crumbles on the outside which gives it an extra kick when you bite on it. The owner was also nice and consistent with their food quality. 10/10 restaurant in my opinion :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNG8e_K_abqcmvNQ4UMD8iw8svmXhXwGhgwE-ui&fid=0x0:0x5b181081ecd11c2f"],"When":"2023-1-12"},{"Name":"Garrett McMartin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBZ6D0-4lNeY8j4gnRM1g_3u1vMShl9pdnVvMh8rAk4vQ683io=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Great food but tiny portions.

Our dinner for two consist of 11 pieces of pork in the SS pork, a barely over half full fried rice and roughly 9 pcs of broccoli","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKnctUCo9hsV4Zp7VSLzDr7aoF-ToCimBteeTD&fid=0x0:0x5b181081ecd11c2f"],"When":"2024-2-19"},{"Name":"Edgar Ignacio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7oexz4qXoBKr6ujKuYxwMvlf16ckv-ovFMKFmC4nzUqeMSoelFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"One of the best place to dine if you like authentic chinese foods. They serve delicious and super tasty lunch combo meals. The price is just right but serving is smaller and you need a second course of order in my opinion. They have a large selection of dishes to choose from. Service was great and their washroom is well maintained. The dimly lit ambience is very good for a romantic setting. I love it here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMq-chNlN1x1arw_E7svLWWu2TkPm2s3FxCPUJY&fid=0x0:0x5b181081ecd11c2f"],"When":"2021-12-13"},{"Name":"py0413","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhqvwQrQBP1Ho2kEoDqZgSrifkk5JwGR5lNkcGFu5IU-p8UTjq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small little shop that has some of the most authentic Chinese food especially the spicy choices. They are family owned/operated small restaurant, sometimes it takes a bit of wait but the friendly owner or server will always notify customers about that. Delicious food that are made fresh takes time and the wait is definitely worthy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNW6fMa6u6GbBiZlv6oeXUZFt90BkguNLYO4DcA&fid=0x0:0x5b181081ecd11c2f"],"When":"2018-12-21"},{"Name":"Junjun Baby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBeGgMpnNz0T2uxE4lSjGJexej7jdbyGP_E6pKzewuJ_8mbVrG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had dinner at this restaurant last night. Chatting with the waitress/ owner, we learned that this is a family restaurant, run by the couple who originally was from Shanghai. It has been around for 17 years. The dishes we ordered most in the category of Shanghai cuisines. They were authentic.
The restaurant has quite a menu. I notice it also has Sichun cuisine dishes, which have stronger flavors and spicy taste.
I like the atmosphere there, small, quiet, and cozy with contemporary oriental decorations. If there's a background music, it would make the setting more lively.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexandra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWod6EbW5D4lQiIr-KZpM7_XafS1GjbPyWk8hXBh63OaLnzfHCWEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My favourite place for comforting Asian dishes! This family owned restaurant is one of my personal favourites here in White Rock. I have been coming here for years now with my family and they never disappoint. The owner is super friendly and adorable, it's always nice to see her 😊 I especially love coming here with my family when I'm back from university during the summer or winter. She remembers us too and always thoughtful to ask how we've been and how the school year was. The feeling of having a meal here is the feeling you get when you're having a meal at your grandma's or a big family gathering. It's cozy and comfortable and the food reminds you of home. Pre-covid it was fabulous, and now during covid, my family has been getting takeout from this place and it's not any less delicious. The service is excellent! Would definitely recommend ❤️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOp_5uyeymTz66_boSDb9FES8xHTMIjRDnYi2DU&fid=0x0:0x5b181081ecd11c2f"],"When":"2021-6-5"}]

[{"Name":"somayeh aghajani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbDfzwKcGqhnu0XGjTJwPUyjO8954pgnor6WCon4LeVRfE61h6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"White Rock is easily one of the most beautiful destinations in BC! The beach is stunning, and the city has a charming vibe with its cozy cafes and restaurants offering breathtaking ocean views. A must-visit for anyone in the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNzSZUCXaeM2mKXx_oN4h6UADRqvYhozrkgPiGJ&fid=0x0:0xfc52ee8d824e628f"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Rolando_ Rose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQBfjayv2V3eqQ6nmwU1uOEqgsWCG5VdwRxO3uXCF1EsXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely recommended!!! A charming coastal town with Canada’s longest pier! We had an amazing visit here with the family. It was captivating and picturesque with a piece of history, lots of eateries, quaint shops, cafes, ice cream parlour to name a few! The scenery is absolutely beautiful, relaxing and inviting, making it a perfect place to unwind and create memorable experiences. It gets very busy during summer and parking can be quite challenging. But it’s worth the visit! Loved it! It’s beautiful indeed!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdV8R5Vsxrd_NR2uFVgaUN-3AYppPk258poUc&fid=0x0:0xfc52ee8d824e628f"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Clare B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1m3J4FuXLDpx5mMEPObnV54seybAV1WGt451VGbe8svBkwYnJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful area, well worth the visit.
There are plenty of information plaques as you walk up the pier and around the surrounding area, offering a wealth of fascinating information.
The views from the pier both out to sea and inland are incredible.
Probably a one time visit kind of place, but absolutely worth it. Be sure to walk along the front and see the sculptures and the actual White Rock if you can.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0M8PlS7Rz0t6MyoVXHva-dlWTdYBq71CkEYkm&fid=0x0:0xfc52ee8d824e628f"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"Ravi Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLHaeqE4UWd4AZkkKtoinTfp3mQzHqs3nbe041zXMQXXcCIv0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The White Rock Pier is a beautiful spot with breathtaking ocean views and a peaceful atmosphere. It's the perfect place for a relaxing stroll, watching the sunset, or taking stunning photos. The surrounding area offers great restaurants and cafes, making it a wonderful day trip destination. The pier itself is well-maintained, but it can get a bit crowded during peak times, which slightly takes away from the serene experience.

Parking can also be a challenge on busy days.

Overall, a lovely spot that’s definitely worth visiting!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaGaU5wVo4fLszCeJlm3vo849CgIhZCNVLEgx2&fid=0x0:0xfc52ee8d824e628f"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Maryam Zaribafan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6qFyfnU-AIpbv8PcqtBeVh0gxPG9nML2mZVcql24rVnAD7QWB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited White Rock, and I must say, it was an enchanting and unique experience that left a lasting impression. This charming coastal town offers a captivating and picturesque environment that is perfect for a relaxing getaway.

The moment you arrive in White Rock, you are greeted by stunning ocean views and the iconic white rock that gives the town its name. The long, sandy beach is perfect for a leisurely stroll, and the beautiful promenade lined with quaint shops, cafes, and restaurants adds to the town's appeal. The atmosphere is relaxed and inviting, making it a great place to unwind and enjoy the scenery.

One of the highlights of White Rock is its vibrant and diverse community. The locals are incredibly friendly and welcoming, and there's always something happening, from local markets to outdoor concerts. The town has a unique charm that blends a laid-back beach vibe with a touch of sophistication.

The sunsets in White Rock are absolutely breathtaking. Watching the sun dip below the horizon while reflecting off the water is a magical experience that you won't want to miss. Whether you're enjoying a meal at one of the waterfront restaurants or simply sitting on a bench by the pier, the views are truly spectacular.

White Rock also offers plenty of activities for nature lovers. From kayaking and paddleboarding to exploring nearby parks and trails, there’s something for everyone. The town’s commitment to preserving its natural beauty is evident in the well-maintained green spaces and clean beaches.

If you’re looking for a place that combines natural beauty, a vibrant community, and a peaceful atmosphere, White Rock is the perfect destination. It’s a wonderful spot to relax, explore, and create unforgettable memories. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5uRzwyzZA9hL7eYWmOWTk3DPsd3DSYhNnMXEl&fid=0x0:0xfc52ee8d824e628f"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Sangeeth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOxDTI55299-17xHczbV49Haf4_WAoEcbKkLa_T9lAaE1M6YHr6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This pier in White Rock, British Columbia, is 470 meters long, making it the longest in Canada. It's a popular spot specially with tourists, and offers stunning views and a well-kept surrounding area. You can also easily access the beach and enjoy various activities nearby. The experience is thrilling, and the best time to visit is during the second half .so many places nearby to enjoy seafood and other treats. washrooms available near the main entrance by a statue. Paid car park is available where you can pay by the kiosk or using the “PaybyPhone” app. Overall highly recommended and definitely a must-visit spot!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-Z4Y3R-TQzu7diSTJILOwi-1gQkuUEtnHqmMS&fid=0x0:0xfc52ee8d824e628f"],"When":"2024-8-8"},{"Name":"M. A.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLB10KqeIl0fqiL0pGNdfKbos8ZnoBDkwk_kgO3yJezaC8LhTs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You should take the whole family to this lovely place. The pier and beach make for pleasant walks. In the vicinity are numerous eateries and pubs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2Y4Wx7rRBrPIvfyezSs3xTjXlHHr5-YxM_sPT&fid=0x0:0xfc52ee8d824e628f"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"Keith Ver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVdqxLCf1LEt0AU82myo-eUqDcb2LcbdnfhupJTEW0sPAQ-qQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Gorgeous place! It's definitely a must visit when you're in BC! I initially wanted to go here because it was one of the shooting locations of Twice's 2017 hit song, Likey, but I had a fantastic experience going here altogether!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNg8VzaSsU3U7LQFPUU5an-z4AhcCmlbow7-af9&fid=0x0:0xfc52ee8d824e628f"],"When":"2024-8-29"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Thomas R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUR-NtWx60betHk7dk9E58udsJ87tVP5184Kcsmp3yimRSmiIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"It's okay. Some of the customers are wonderful! The best part (as I write this in 2024 at least). Many are still local actual Canadians so it has that environment with the customers. The people working there are a little spaced though. Probably not people people, not the most open sociable types. I ordered a baked good the last time I was in and the young guy working there after I purchased it, expecting me to have already done it, says I can just grab one myself. It's just there on the counter wrapped in plastic. So I do that and I sit and grab my own napkin at a different station and eat it over plastic and napkin over the table, surely crumbs getting spread out. I said it was for here. What am I paying for exactly? Is this a little newsstand at a bus station where I get a snack for 50 cents? Is this not a place to spend a bit of time since there are seats inside? Just weird. And how the staff communicates is off.  Not how I grew up to socialize but then I grew up in White Rock before it became this strange tower filled foreign population place. So the café is okay. The people working there aren't the worst with customer service. But something is off.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Justine Roo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAQoC1sFgPJ6yj73Syg75podVcnn8oGnLLnNvApy7zcibZmOV4vA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Might be the worst latte I've ever had. Ordered an oat milk latte and was disappointed it tasted soapy and watered down. Then when I went to add some sugar I found there was no milk and sugar station or anything out to dress your coffee. You have to ask the barista for everything. Key to use the washroom. It's like they are expecting someone to come in and rob and abuse the entire store. Just overall a very poor experience. This used to be a very nice place and every other bean around the world establishment I've had a pleasant experience but this was really bad","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paula Hlavacek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUEHsTUDREBV0VNUK6UGtTRNbBuCTOdBVYyLeZYC7hO1QTx25MLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This cafe is so cute! The coffee was quite strong but was surprised they can make a flat white! (It’s not in the menu) They don’t offer barista special almond milk unfortunately, they just have just the usual Silk almond milk... the customer service was really good. Lots of working space and free wifi!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXxbPhOXzEGt4t8TKV-AVvWpXIjP3xJHVLzRnX\u0026fid=0x0:0xd13c5b0bd650b00f"],"When":"2020-3-22"},{"Name":"J.J. LaRocque","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs1wnHH1wE-6ehYO1ShgkgKN3A6ZFemN0kZy8RwdiX8HwJ30lb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this spot. Great little coffee shop to stop in and go for a walk downtown. Coffee is really nice and a great selection of food and specials as well. The staff are extremely kind and friendly. They have almond milk and honey behind the counter, so you need to ask for it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP25XNxaWyK2OufNy0gFuJA5FKCByMS-iyJqyad\u0026fid=0x0:0xd13c5b0bd650b00f"],"When":"2020-3-22"},{"Name":"James w","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWux6QogVBrguYBWvtrWqHXIiLNsuqV-Pma5cB7eUP8KMT-hvE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Paid $6.25 for a 20oz iced mocha. Recieved a medium (maybe 12oz) after an extreme wait time. After taking one sip it was horrible. Im not sure who taught the people there how to make coffee but they should also take a training course. In their defence I should have gone back to get it fixed but I didnt realize until i was down the block. Yikes.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Naomi Fazan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8X_K9zqJBscJ5-zT635d-5KkttndwKSf6nQ7WUK14aNp8eQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I spent 8.20 dollars on my large iced latte , tipped 1.80 for an even $10 spend. I dropped my coffee outside as I walked away. I brought the empty cup back inside and they charged me for a replacement. This to me is bizzare, greedy and not custom service. I understand the spill was my doing but this happens all the time in the service industry and we don’t penalize the customer for dropping something. It’s a cost the business takes on (spillage, waste, damage) etc. Mike the owner I presume said they would only charge me for a small instead... I don’t know with so many other options for coffee around here, you’re much better off going down a block to island cafe or just across the street to grounds and greens, or up to pelican rouge or even Starbucks. Very unfortunate.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9tmTgzn8-W6je7LGwMIQzW_mJuoyhl1GFvK3y\u0026fid=0x0:0xd13c5b0bd650b00f"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Tannis Zboroluk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9FnlGDpKGSy_fc09OaANTBleqoD1NZSVbHGCdZN42Oaf5NA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful coffee, lots of regulars and a great space to visit with lots of natural light. Their lattes are delicious as are their cinnamon buns and scones.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jen S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6yRDu3X2tYRf22dSS2L1HUQ_---VPNFSZyVWrJW6KXuGpfNIHww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I like their Americanos. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jamie Weins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhIg1Kb2wnv2Gwu5CpaHKGP6OAkgLsG22PmC8YHCHigI885W7L5A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a fantastic bakehouse!!! Specialty Sandwiches, coffee, specialty drinks and as the name says, baking! We stopped in for Sunday brunch. Got parking, right across the street and had a wonderful view of the pier.
But what really wowed me was the food. You can tell they put love into their baking. We had 3 different sandwiches, and all 3 of us were blown away. The sourdough bread on my sandwich made me so happy. I typically find sourdough to be mediocre, but it was deliciously sour. They make a lovely mocha and latte. And finally, the baking. Oh my word... I wish I had taken more home with me.  The cruffin, I'll be dreaming about it. It was so light inside and crispy on the outside. ❤️ I look forward to coming back to White Rock to visit this bakehouse in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYV6KVmG5DgId3NusrMKO7DFWW58NEbmIWXX6j&fid=0x0:0x7ae81666d0d94eb3"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"David","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXE3mSDKhEMEGOkPAtyVQwrJnUlnySlva1iLxmCdzIsIe7GC30=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow sooo good, read on!

Located in the old ZERO pizza burger food court that unfortunately failed. Google says opens at 8 but really opens at 9. No website just on FB and the gram. Closed some days so check first.

Well where to start!!!

Large clean establishment with large elevated deck with a perfect view over looking the pier. Some long Baquette style seating along walls. Loved the music which added to the modern European vibe. Edibles, Chez Christophe’s take note you have some welcomed competition! The pastries I sampled were to my high quality, labour of love, many crusty layers and of course made with butter code. All made onsite fresh in the early morning. French croissant’s are a fine art to make and these for me fall within that baking realm. These was golden brown, great dry crust that snapped open to reveal the moist butter inside with too many layers to count. The Aman was much the same except with a caramelized, not gooey topping= excellent. Had my routine skinny cappuccino  which was smooth not bitter, served at the right temp with lots of foam. They serve a breakfast sandwich but save that for next visit. Just arrived and a young family were ordering double shots and the kids were going crazy for the potential treats.
This will be my new  coffee and desert haunt. Welcome to White Rock Monkey Puzzlers, good luck to the new owner, chef and staff. Cheers","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVtfTL1AyfKPTXBUwMgxEErU7Rqgn20e17SIRS&fid=0x0:0x7ae81666d0d94eb3"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Thomas Canale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXI86Srvqkt9rsTZVzzifeScuS77fy_Mt5gtnpRNPlkxb3BeeCh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have tried pastries here on a few occasions now and have never been disappointed. By far the best place for baked goods in the White Rock area! The quality is right up there with the best Vancouver bakeries. They only recently opened, and I can tell they have made some positive changes (e.g. they now have mini trays for in house orders instead of paper plates). It would be nice to see them using mugs instead of paper cups for in house orders in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0v3A9tn1l6u3IMHI2udHiju1YZOFEIbjfT-Lz&fid=0x0:0x7ae81666d0d94eb3"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Talia Phillips","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQm47Dd4BKDlBxQMlpEUIOQ2g_kKXyQpwXAzouqPIy1PR_xw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm obsessed now and I'm bound to go broke. This bakery is phenomenal.

Everything was delicious but the raspberry marscapone cruffin was to die for. Just the right amount of creamy and sweet for the fillings, just the right amount of each and the texture of the cruffin itself was soft, crispy and chewy all at once. Man, I want another one.

The woman at the register was like a ray of sunshine, so nice and happy. I love this place! I can't recommend it enough. YUM","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAk4ZYUNft8QncUacRQ2sgsEfAEja8u35ggtCA&fid=0x0:0x7ae81666d0d94eb3"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"David Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4RSnQP2rP5f6kTABnanZHzdOgI8Fs6ee6D4bwA1UiT-d0KIRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Newly opened bakery in the center of white rock. All made in house and delicious. Had their pastrami sandwich and croque monsieur! Patio with a view even made the food even better!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXmECRA6-TbV_GwT3s53d7KAiIwbkAKjHGcGrN&fid=0x0:0x7ae81666d0d94eb3"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Mackenzie Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJujiBlZ_CiJ46cWWsi3JseE920_T1OHx6AC-iX7ow5w762ew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So good! Finally a good coffee shop and bakery at the beach. The breakfast sandwich is delicious and great value. Iced latte was fantastic! 5 stars!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9ty5HVhCc0PbfrYMpmz-vsdiCaGDjS86vOj9W&fid=0x0:0x7ae81666d0d94eb3"],"When":"2024-7-26"},{"Name":"Megan Maxwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSDAQIUS-D_byeRhMGS8X9EuBbngKGuVpO75nfRne4D98XcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service, delicious food, drinks and pastries and right on the beach. My new fave cafe on marine drive. Can’t recommend enough.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOackB7FfzRojIFG_6ttp346Bcj9RrYGvYob_Y&fid=0x0:0x7ae81666d0d94eb3"],"When":"2024-7-18"},{"Name":"Alex Lapitski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtqtC0jezV6pqNiexK1twIDiM0tCwe--IZGUAsTMXPCtXYrP9W=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came to visit my brother who lives in White Rock, and we were trying to find a spot for a quick coffee and a muffin. We stumbled upon Monkey Puzzle Bakehouse and noticed they were putting up decor. Curious, we asked if they were new, and it turned out they had just opened. The treats looked delicious and were very reasonably priced, so we decided to give them a shot. Let me tell you, it was the best decision we made that day.

We both ordered a little breakfast pastry with egg, bacon, and tomatoes, and shared a sweet berry tart. Both were on par with some of my favorite bakeries in Vancouver. We spent the next half hour sitting on their patio, trying to make eye contact with random passersby to encourage them to come in and support this newly opened gem.

Great vibe, super kind staff, reasonably priced, and most importantly – delicious food and coffee. I hope that this bakehouse sticks around for the long haul, and that we can turn visiting them into a weekly tradition.","Images":null,"When":""}]

title: Pizza Hut

[{"Name":"Delightful Blossom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9OUjZ985M55r_x1AEjyhn7fBe4ZZWH_m_6K3G74jFnLSqgGcE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This Pizza Hut has disappointed me so much that I'm writing my first review. I’ve been a regular customer here, often ordering once or twice a month because my family and I have loved Pizza Hut for over four years. I usually spend about $50 per order. But in the last few months, my orders have consistently been ruined, leading me to finally decide that I won’t order from this Pizza Hut again.

When they offered fries (they don’t anymore), they were often soggy, too few, or even the wrong type — once I got waffle fries instead of regular ones that was not even in the sides option until now, and there were only nine pieces. I tried to be patient and gave them several chances before writing this review, but things haven’t improved.

The pizza crust hasn’t been crispy in months, and today’s pizza was a disaster. Crispy crest is what they are advertised and known for but now...I just can't. It was undercooked, and the cheese wasn’t properly melted (although that may not show in the photo). The bread that we used to love is now stale and gooey. I’m genuinely sorry to say all this, but they’ve lost a customer. I used to recommend Pizza Hut to friends, but sadly, I can’t do that anymore.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVI4iaZs5QxQDdaYVZVn930mKOuJ08sCivY6j_&fid=0x0:0x81d1c2da027eb64c"],"When":"2024-11-8"},{"Name":"melissa de venecia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRu1ZbFWLEPi5FEp4g-AzPf7-cjNVew1QdD9vmp7rF8j0Z2yi6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first time visiting this local Pizza Hut, and I was thoroughly impressed! The staff were incredibly friendly and went out of their way to make sure my order was exactly how I wanted it. They were patient as I askes few questions and they even offered some great suggestions.

When i picked up my pizza, it was hot, fresh, and absolutely delicious. The crust was perfect, and the toppings were generous. I’ll definitely be coming back for more!”The crust was crispy on the outside but soft and chewy on the inside, and the flavor was spot on. I could tell that the ingredients were fresh, and the cheese was perfectly melted.

Overall, it was a great experience from start to finish. If you’re looking for a place with delicious pizza and a staff that truly cares about customer service, I highly recommend this Pizza Hut location!”","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Doug Reiffer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIeo2NahwN3VffqSUI-SklIakNEjjoszpLhrL5BHUN47poNhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great pizza.  First time user. 2 Large for pick-up. Didn't know how 'small' the '4' garlic bread 'pieces' were 'til I got home.  Would have ordered more.  Or not at all.  Should have checked before I left.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kay Gee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlV36m9t14GR_ZizneDOW1eIG2Xs2zYUXXNc1N4BxPQ7iwNg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I visited this place as a delivery driver to pickup an order. Front counter staff was very rude and didn’t hesitate to disrespect finding I am doing this to make the ends meet.

Have some respect for delivery drivers, they are human being too and working similar to you.

As a customer I would never buy from this store due to this bad behaviour from front staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVW4N84i-RYr3ItwapVkD8Vamx2qrjkYqOh1o7HxhpOovIVL35_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We normally order there but this time was so annoying! I ordered online and pick up was supposed to be at 7:05 p.m. We arrived on time and my son went in to pick up pizza. They told him it's not ready yet and told him to come back in a half an hour. I then send him in with my phone and the confirmation number and the indicator that it is done and they sent him out telling him "I already told you, it will be a half an hour." Well, this prompts Papa Bear who is wearing pajamas and a hoodie (I never go in public dressed like this) to head outside and into the store. I promptly identify the person who is being an effective expeditor and inquire about my pizza. And immediately, said pizza was located. Not only was our pizza ready but they made us wait an extra 20 minutes because the person behind the counter couldn't be bothered to check. It was a very frustrating experience. The pizza was usual Pizza Hut pizza. The service was definitely lacking.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dianne Serrano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKXZwCEzdTDH4hKKYj49XzPuzzN7-7uAlYSCL5-ZjtZjH5OMg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I went there last August 25th and bought some pizza. The girl that served me, I believe, is the Supervisor named Michelle. It was a hectic day, and she helped her staff and jumped in to take my order. The pizza I requested and cooked the way I wanted was served. And, as I looked at the store, I noticed that the supervisor was really diligent and welcoming to both customers and staff. She ensures that time flows smoothly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nadeem Chohan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_J-vhO_FMshQBl6YHwQxtS2r-V_JbTxh9vtfWwx5KZlMo2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Whenever I go to this store, Warren always helps me get the right deal. He is very friendly and helpful. Unfortunately, he was not in store today, so his assistant manager took my order. I ordered a Chicken Arrabbiata and a ranch sauce. The assistant manager was very polite and helpful. I think his name was Shamin or something. The staff prepared my order quickly as usual, and the pizza tasted good.

Highly recommend this location!!!
Great customer service!!
Helpful staff","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mahesh S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJQiq5PKKTWj9z9z4XcwZk0Q6sYFBNtZ6z7u-a5X2y5qFW93LQsg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"This place used to be good and in fact I gave a five star about a year ago. But recently the quality has gone down and I got some absolutely  horrible pizza today. I would let it slide if it were cheap but nothing is cheap anymore. It was a waste of 50$. Crust too thick, borderline uncooked, too less cheese, too much veggies, contends for the worst p9zza I've ever had.","Images":null,"When":""}]
