[{"Name":"Harrison Peers, Realtor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLj2rlpKO7KJT6UpX1QjjJ2eHUX0QnhMR1u4oJxXhKAEkrBbvS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great! Highly recommend the shaved ice with Mango, it was so delicious! It wasn’t too sweet and the mango tasted fresh. Super refreshing, perfect summer treat! The portion sizes are also great for the price - pictured is the “Regular” sized portion and it was enough for two of us. Service was great!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOsIsUk7afE5rfuLo1Y7UdunNdJYEIp1044qXqf&fid=0x0:0xdcee8755129c727b"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"M H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXEwCuKMIMDolDIGtOiTVSXMdmaiK64aKmAzQkA_o1J5bv6Vpu0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Run, don't walk! This shaved ice spot is new to the White Rock Pier area, but will definitely become a quick favourite.

Plenty of indoor seating, and enough room around tables to be stroller friendly. Super clean despite how busy it got. And has a cute neon sign/floral wall for all your Instagram photos. Staff were super friendly, efficient and hardworking despite the consistent flow of customers.

Food 👌🏼👌🏼👌🏼 Had the large mango shaved ice which was more than enough for 3 adults, and it was delicious. Shaved ice was soft, and flavourful, there were layers of mango and whip throughout so you didn't end with a pile of ice, and they were so generous with the fresh, delicious mango chunks. We also tried the mochi bubble waffle which came out fresh so it was warm, and each bubble had a mochi in it. It'll be my mission to try each flavour at this spot because I have a feeling it'll never disappoint.

They also have fresh fruit cups and banana bread for sale!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPywPBVgzWS7MGf9zj91FARv2QfYHLklV5Ua1ou&fid=0x0:0xdcee8755129c727b"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Jessica Greville","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVi1HmvfZo6ZEH-pJLpLVVhH1StEVSZjyscQoBq0jggNNlGwyJW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A small but mighty dessert shop in White Rock! We went in the evening mid week and there was no wait, plenty of seating and a cute, clean space. I shared a regular mango shaved ice with hubby & it was more than satisfying! So neatly prepared and a good portion to value. We are so happy to see Bingsu in White Rock! Keep up the great work!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-1D_fNzG8hS-VK7aw8od048xVs7kD_iqQigxF&fid=0x0:0xdcee8755129c727b"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Justin Eagles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOIWdyWSvG6-il9m8rOMc3PWfYigKnuOwSQGUVUEfzDsc6J2iMpw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is incredible! The owners are super nice and make beautiful desserts. The shaved ice was the best we’ve ever had - so much fruit!

Our party had multiple items from their menu and were blown away by everything. Try the watermelon juice - you won’t be disappointed!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZsuO0gIb5ppdSiVKRntrNIPC0ww78G6-_FfN-&fid=0x0:0xdcee8755129c727b"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Hedarson Erardo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpXA2V1UWXJx-If05cfHyi_cqZN0bK_4dBwYO1Sf6SV_ZTXT9J=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Top shaved Ice in Whiterock. I ordered the Matcha. Its so good and the mochi is so generous. My kid said that its the best bubble waffle he ever had. Staff is so friendly. Very clean place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeHMYtE1LgNrSyQTXMscIUpuey6jbbWMF2e62w&fid=0x0:0xdcee8755129c727b"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Helen Do","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_SCl1fSgrjvuViAh5dfzhRTmNN7V0YHTedXmjU--39ap3IWRX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sway Sweets is an absolute gem. The atmosphere is a perfect blend of chic and cozy, making you feel welcome the moment you step inside. The staff? Not only incredibly friendly and attentive but also very attractive 😍😍😍😍, adding a delightful touch to the experience.

The desserts are nothing short of stunning, each one a visual and flavorful masterpiece. Every bite is a burst of pure bliss, clearly made with love and high-quality ingredients. Despite the upscale feel, the prices are very reasonable, making it easy to indulge without breaking the bank.

In short, Sway Sweets offers an unforgettable dessert experience that you'll want to revisit again and again.

Overall? 🧑‍🍳 💋 10/10, love it, will definitely be back again. We got the Mango Shaved Ice, Vietnamese Iced Coffee Shaved Ice, and Matcha Bubble Waffle. Hope this helps!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyt0xHlekyjHNjIZd8yanpFqss0PFLoC-oV_f5&fid=0x0:0xdcee8755129c727b"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"Thomas Canale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXI86Srvqkt9rsTZVzzifeScuS77fy_Mt5gtnpRNPlkxb3BeeCh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A great addition to the White Rock area! The mango shave ice is huge and full of fresh mango! The bubble waffles are fresh, warm and perfectly sweet. We also enjoyed the fresh watermelon juice - the perfect summer drink. To top it off, the owners are both so kind.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlfK_voZFNMq1095c1mPZmkJWKpWYjE8eAgXLm&fid=0x0:0xdcee8755129c727b"],"When":"2024-6-8"},{"Name":"Gabrielle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPZLarUKpKgUXVfA9tOjdGjVW91k303l5VxK6A47szHf5BAzECDw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love that it is not another ice cream shop that opened on the strip. Their shaved ice was delicious. Lots of fruit and the presentation very on point. It is located on the west side of the beach and seems more quiet than other ice cream shops. Hope more people will come and visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPoClCaXh5o-izQBNYQ1zXM5nBQyUFguc6vsqj&fid=0x0:0xdcee8755129c727b"],"When":"2024-8-3"}]

We shared the pork and shrimp wonton soup, red bean mooncake, chiffon cakes, with cold flower tea and watermelon juice for drinks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMh1we9X4KMTAgHV2SwBnXCoLUZYF2dWtNOr0Xb&fid=0x0:0x5feb2a95a35bffa2"],"When":"2022-5-23"},{"Name":"Eran Xu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKC5k58tc2I-5ZmKGNXg9puHPBCVnyi2YzCnE0v-JyXnc22Pg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'd have to say this is my favourite Chinese tea house in the Vancouver area! My dad is a zisha pot collector. I believe the owner of this store is also a collector and I saw many valuable zisha pots in the cabinet. Even the tea set for customer drinking is from a famous contemporary zisha pot artisan.
Enjoy a chilling afternoon and learn the traditional Chinese tea ceremony techniques:D","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1vmiTePjRqB0DZYQTXbof09bLYW54d4hHEkWR&fid=0x0:0x5feb2a95a35bffa2"],"When":"2022-10-16"},{"Name":"Kevin Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXw3DzbJjzagFGCffaUf_bEzzROuckrEmR2MKidBKSJv211VH8c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place orders authentic Shanghainese buns and the tea, while not cheap, is also of high quality.

You can taste the ingredients being fresh which means that you will also need to be patient as you wait for each dish to be made as you order.

Great seating area for everyone to enjoy!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQYbHlT-trdRYCnVK_NJdxl2Xt4jiT0OM1YjDy&fid=0x0:0x5feb2a95a35bffa2"],"When":"2022-11-2"},{"Name":"Jenn Ifer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwYOiT4s09kBUcn2YXnUp-q88RMTw22n4Q6hc7XzqeMm83rA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bubble tea is so good. [{"Name":"Erika Rabura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNQja6bLOMl-_XIYyKGiG2lsiQwkMJ5YSZDByWJfCGC0XOQuM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I loved this place! The owner was very friendly. And it had by far the best tomato soup I have ever had. My husband especially loved the nachos and the special sauces that were put on top. I wish we lived closer as we would come here more often. I 100% recommend this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tanis Gaitens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBkWuNJjySwVop8zo82b2i8oQlDUUX0bvv2r7YlkDL2i6-7vVk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful fish & chips at the best price on White Rock  beach! Really diverse menu, Bombay indian faves, Mexican and more.  Sat outside, great atmosphere and  beach view. Shout out to Nency the chef and Jeel our server was wonderful 💛 Definiteky will come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOknZGQnI_VsledHpqasZKi9jWAiQhLbgbeoXq5&fid=0x0:0x217505478212a499"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Dan Watt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHDWJmFQujsvitgVogjnVUUl0OIJ-UvB6DHRZ7ZXtbBO7TY-rkVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We stumbled upon this place by chance, and it turned out to be their opening night! The kitchen was definitely working out some kinks (didn't have all the menu items yet and was a little slow -- about 30 mins),  but the food was worth waiting for! It was my first time trying Elco Pani Puri and I was grateful to the server for some instruction. They were FUN! The chicken Tikka was also delicious and the momos were mouthwatering, each with tasty dipping sauces. I had a lime soda -- not too sweet. My one suggestion would be to turn the music down a little.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODNKT-ZQUP1KElE-jHo1dv9BbmmOZYi8B91MEN&fid=0x0:0x217505478212a499"],"When":"2024-6-8"},{"Name":"Felicia Pan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIy2XCL72yjdIkl-1HyNd2NXbix1mqe59RyEpUrbSZvemxxdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is So DELICIOUS, Excellent Service too!! Highly recommend to all the local residents!! A must try restaurant!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0sHIX17v6OXn8NmY9wkVtFBqCVsDA_xocwJ4z&fid=0x0:0x217505478212a499"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"Dharam Badech","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUibn58NPlvJLC_ZG_CO4BUEws1fzH8KqLcWEIC5f3cJpVN98i2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bombay chutney Sandwich is as authentic as it gets. If you want to try real Mumbai food this is the place to eat. The sandwich is exactly the ones you’d find from a street side vendor in Bandra, Mumbai.

Bang bang cauliflower is the perfect vegetarian starter but best to eat at restaurant the take away won’t taste the same.

Wash it down with a Fresh Lime Soda (Sweet). Tastes just like a restaurant in Mumbai.

Vada pav again is as authentic as it gets.
It is the staple food for many labourers in Mumbai who were either born in Mumbai or came to the Bollywood city from other rural towns or villages. The reddish powder thing is a spicy dry garlic chutney.

Finish it with a Tres Leche cake made Indian with the Thandai flavouring","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPR8oJeD9Q_bfyFmTTL3C9Dnu_xOIvjOiC3Nwb&fid=0x0:0x217505478212a499"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Toan Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpG9Pu6tm08jVTwx0CscWpizMzakUqn-NOd_89h4x16dlKCDg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is just the spice White Rock needs. This fish pakora is the perfect alternative if you crave fish and chips but want something with more ethnic flavor. Quickly try them before they get popular and realize they can raise their prices!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJpXgOlmPt4p8fGn4DqLaod93pbcewpskTpNrC&fid=0x0:0x217505478212a499"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"sonu sahota","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWv1qgHPDhvfld9Cp5gSeO-y6ugI7mZBq6jNVb5dqzilTUyBT65=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had a cutting chai ( I liked that they gave 2 "parle G" biscuits with it.... I know its a small effort.. But its a good one..it just give a little kick to ur childhood memories  ) 4/5
Then we had "Vada Pav" i will give it 4.5/5
It was great
Then we had "Fried Chicken Momos" those were good in taste too.. Not good as Vada Pav but.. Still good enough i will give those 3/5","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoOcU6KPlc-iZ4Dwdz4mT8R_tmxvThf3syPEM8&fid=0x0:0x217505478212a499"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Sid Marcinew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtQqhtXLYIeCfqaI18tiLSvGqhvdiZQ_lpfgmS0jm6pcUQ9778=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quaint little sidewalk cafe.  Fish and chips were crispy outside, tender inside and tasty.  Ample serving of chicken nachos were flavorful even without the guacamole and salsa.  Butter chicken was masala style; spicy and smooth to the palate, but not hot.  Had enough food left over to take home for another enjoyable meal.  The staff were welcoming and friendly.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"David & Patti Ens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCrwxnBL2_VqJnEgLg0JtK_fNSDOCo9bnsDqabFska_Kpl4DON=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted Mexican and we were on the way in to Vancouver. Ay Chihuahua looked like a nice place. The four of us came in and were welcomed by a lovely young lady. It is like fast food where you order and they begin to prepare right beside you. It advertises authenticity and I must admit it was like a taste of Mexico. They even have several flavors of Mexican soda. My burrito was humongous and delicious. We also got a taco salad that was too much to eat, Chimichanga,and Chiles Rellenos. We got hot sauce on the side (thank goodness) as that tiny little container has some serious heat. There are several places to eat within fifty meters, but Ay Chihuahua is well worth it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrr1Jv5FuanslFVC3OI6UfR4laDohDis8VW-GF&fid=0x0:0x9ecfbdd85efc6a3f"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Steven Olmstead","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtGPLsUg7ybhRCsA9-VeVYuyaFqArSeyzqddnDm9gdPpsZ3M0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ay Chihuahua is a great little hole in the wall for lunch.  Advertised as authentic Mexican, it is surely reminiscent of small family run Mexican seen all along the west coast of the states.  We ordered posole and chicken quesadilla.  The posole was filled with chucks of fork tender pork, hominy and a delicious, moderately spicy broth.  Fried tortilla chips and greens were on the side, to add to the soup as you liked.  The quesadilla was also very good, but I would definitely return for another bowl of their posole. 5 stars for that, worth the trip!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXfWBl1zO2JxizB9bbK-xcLA36-n4sI68FJrOm&fid=0x0:0x9ecfbdd85efc6a3f"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Camille Viray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkdkT4X5qC5aAz9jOrqshB2cM3PY7bHR0O0CInQ6UAnZ__twbI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious authentic Mexican. Good portions and options. Fast service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBp5D9cYIar4K75jbHGfFtly8vpbx1SlZqY_Pr&fid=0x0:0x9ecfbdd85efc6a3f"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Anna Glibka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQ3s4p5BFTfbqIn6a72xnBdpIRj85XI0YEVnjOGbaNHetssEPCFg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I enjoyed a delightful meal of quesadillas and a burrito at Ay Chihuahua in Surrey. The food was delicious, showcasing authentic flavors. The service was excellent, and the woman who served us added a warm and welcoming touch to our experience, reflecting the restaurant's genuine atmosphere. I would recommend Ay Chihuahua for a culturally immersive dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8ti0kNYWJ5s-BRraVsbMUtnU4-cepqElfB9ij&fid=0x0:0x9ecfbdd85efc6a3f"],"When":"2023-11-30"},{"Name":"Sukhraj Hothi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxQjM5nJbgElJc2hyhhoXQyiMBiFOcfOQTg0d9N8DVTMBMUnkcEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I really did have to think about this review being someone who LOVES a good burrito, but I don’t think I could give this place a 5/5

That being said, the food was decent but felt bland (discussed with my group visiting)

Maybe this doesn’t align with the other reviews, but it wasn’t up to my burrito standard; please reference my other taqueria reviews

However! The service is f-ing impeccable; they really know how to operate a well-decorated taqueria and provide excellent hospitality :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaDGhezotS-tgB3XBCM93OwaUOStJp6TOXfiOF&fid=0x0:0x9ecfbdd85efc6a3f"],"When":"2022-5-22"},{"Name":"Vochito Warrior","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlYTtetIkYwlXvPOnKu0Z2qEq_vrGgv9KocLeNEC704VRxQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pozole I have ever tried in 16 years in Canada!!!

As a mexican, I often get disappointed when it comes to authenticity. Although I understand I'm not in Mexico but this restaurant has a 5-star authentic flavor! 😋","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOVytLULp3nfpahqyawldOa37kxXzHGuvv2fiUa&fid=0x0:0x9ecfbdd85efc6a3f"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"gowan321","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyfnjcdfT1IAoKmtyLuq18HCFoiSALiqDPnIwgyAPGsT7hR_U4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, awesome staff, friendly atmosphere and cozy. I only tried one thing it was so good that I could not stop eating it. Would highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDfjWBwTiYh78m6GeDuxiLPIO4Y4he4h9KHM-W&fid=0x0:0x9ecfbdd85efc6a3f"],"When":"2024-1-30"},{"Name":"Sabinus Brutus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4cHKhg-OjL9cJuToW7e7meJSPUWNoMSyvI-jf9A0YSKtHYno=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent Mexican food! It's been a while since our last Mexican meal. The beef Chimichanga was melting in my mouth. The used pastry was so delicious. It came with mashed beans like a puree, rice and a tasty salad. The 3 tacos we had came with pulled pork/ chicken, onion, guacamole and cilantro. Even they were delicious, but not the best tacos we had (the best one had 17 ingredients).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnMayf7Ox0PbyB2BLhbJ5oWeC2s6jqe-hgAkoy&fid=0x0:0x9ecfbdd85efc6a3f"],"When":"2022-7-10"}]

[{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dairy-free Ice Cream available! Excellent and friendly customer service and delicious ice cream! Just what you need on a hot day","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6Hb7MbCtguVQrTYev2CA_sAAHRkyveUE8H0WV&fid=0x0:0x918e8cdeb18af665"],"When":"2024-8-1"},{"Name":"Cristian Riquelme Personal Real Estate Corporation","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWk_Wir3Ks8_DhnVqmljD19XH-Wsww4isABB3OOKAO1tudSeoPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious Ice cream 🍨 with lots of flavours to choose. The services was great and the location is great. Price, well you can’t ask too much because they are all overpriced and this one is not the exception. You can sit down to eat the Ice cream 🍦 or take it to go like we all do.
Anyways, totally recommended!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkS8W7_S5zsE9IbxmfRhyeTCK8861KbYU2fqOu&fid=0x0:0x918e8cdeb18af665"],"When":"2023-6-3"},{"Name":"K Turtlepie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlmg1KKp4tcxA7_sujmWBsO-ycHaCIwYSvczYT4dH-RA1Scg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little Cafe with authentic and delicious choices. Many options available,  probably can find something for anyone. Very fresh and clean place. Ladies working there are lovely. Great experience. Helpful and kind staff. Flavors were amazing. Nice treat on a hot day. We had Gelato and sorbet. They also have many delicious reg. ice cream available. They also have non dairy, vegan, nut free options available. Love there fresh waffle cone. Delicious! Perfect treat for National Ice Cream Day. Thanks. We will come back soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-uZY8OwpTX9CtaoJKJzHPTeBFlPK74y6T1DQe&fid=0x0:0x918e8cdeb18af665"],"When":"2021-7-19"},{"Name":"Gord Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzqg26JTAvjLSvQR6iHAQ0vAHCgUM-McCo69jnkyAJxgQEMg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An absolute gem !
This sweet lil place has some of the most amazing tasting ice cream and home made Gelato in White Rock !
Dee , great customer service, definitely the best lil hidden gem on the strip !
Out of all the I’ve visited on the strip , this one is definitely the best !
Will definitely be coming back to this quaint lil place !
Thanks Dee","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGTJVjEdKmGsjhWY5wDvP_A64EE3lMXGZkTlq3&fid=0x0:0x918e8cdeb18af665"],"When":"2023-7-23"},{"Name":"Chris L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlo27yi0c3tMg1MEFW8gltVROJwlBrQGtk927fnMS7KkAAA0UJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The gelato here is AMAZING! So good on this hot evening. We enjoyed our gelato on the patio and did some car/people watching. They even have dairy free options. Great service, neat place! We will be back! The only downside....deciding which flavour to get! Lol","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPV2eTmHyMKLhPpC8fTTEfDu8syNmGTPCidGEOy&fid=0x0:0x918e8cdeb18af665"],"When":"2023-6-7"},{"Name":"Robert Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlAkMc5h58DpsuTOrDV5dMZ_QamLBJDA5p60lG4V6c6STBi6Hg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice, quaint, little cafe we came to for some gelato. Had the mango on top of salted Caramel. Was good. Preferred the mango. The blue one was cotton candy (I think). It can be quite sweet however it is still tasty. The cotton candy was also on top of mango. Forget what the last one was. Would recommend getting some gelato and then going for a walk. Even at night is good.  Check this place out.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuS_ymilXovIZBZWMzUbbzCm9bQtqvR524Ra35&fid=0x0:0x918e8cdeb18af665"],"When":"2022-8-31"},{"Name":"Rae Lynch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFX7GUEELpGdVFACOmGkb0-hx3bP--hJAsumB3An4G2wumdzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Small little cafe which sells excellent tasting gelato and ice cream🍦 Burgers if your real hungry.
Staff is friendly as it’s family ran.
It’s really cute how enthusiastic their daughter is. Makes you feel how the local community treats the many tourists that stop by! 🙃
Also learned by a friend of mine that a popular K Pop music video was shot here.
Called: “Twice “Likely” M/V” with 270 million views!
Really friendly and tasty desserts. It’s getting real hot out there! 🌡","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0MbXXcoGB5SHhUIFTPp0kfvvO-AztbAiX4w3p&fid=0x0:0x918e8cdeb18af665"],"When":"2018-7-15"},{"Name":"Debbie Lawrance","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9Nh8i9RqfAqGxwFwQ0bNSbafZIO90yEjS2z08lNrtw7vyqvR3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Once again, another AMAZING Home Made GELATO experience at White Rock's OCEAN ROCK CAFE!    We had a lovely time together eating Gelato (& Ice cream), laughing and watching a beautiful sunset.  This family fun business is a lovely little gem. Try it you will LOVE IT!!     #quality #care #fullyloaded or: #sugarfree #dairyfree","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwdBCFBkLNMv8S0HB-4qDTMKRGASwe2csmQbCB&fid=0x0:0x918e8cdeb18af665"],"When":"2024-8-24"}]

Do not order take out from this location! I ordered a cajun chicken, and swaped my coleslaw for a green salad and I received this garbage though Uber eats. This is not their regular salad. I literally could've purchased this at Costco and threw it in a bowl. Spent well over $100 for this delivery and beyond disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGjhC96tYP4frWYiB9MxWaxj2X0jtFSZlWBqfw&fid=0x0:0xa8f831f4f7372e8"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Kaye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiM0TF3EEpBss1JD84r5xUYABu3XFmLG_g4JjKU53bu_SoZREK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I took my mom and me to this location today at around 3pm.. I’ve never had an issue with customer service at Earls in the past but visiting shortly today left me feeling strange.

We were greeted and asked for a phone number to register for a reservation despite the entire restaurant being empty besides maybe 4-5 tables occupied by guests. I understand this must be protocol and wasn’t out of the ordinary. However, after I gave them my phone number the guy attempted to pronounce my name then asked why there were two names on my number. I told him it was a friends name as many people can’t spell or pronounce my name. He then quickly passed us off to a younger host who placed us right beside a full table. Like literally 6 inches in between us.. when the entire place was practically empty lol.

I felt so unwelcomed I just decided to get up and leave before ordering anything. I’ve had better customer service interactions at fast food establishments. It could possibly be untrained staff or new staff but to seat us right beside a full table like that just didn’t feel right.","Images":null,"When":""}]

title: Ocean Promenade Hotel
address: 15611 Marine Dr, White Rock, BC V4B 1E1
descriptions: Modern rooms & suites, some with balconies, in an oceanfront hotel, plus a coffee shop & a gym.
about: null
user_reviews: [{"Name":"james white","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEPHX1_c4RE3qACVThCXEAZCr6Nxp8x4qLLj8n9eEAgiBGaCk_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Lights flickered in the room, sink wouldn't drain in the bathroom, but most importantly room smelt of mold and when I woke up in the morning I had a sore throat and cough. Food was really good. However, the shared appy portions were quite small for the overall price. The roast lamb was absolutely delicious, and the calamari was perfectly done. We will definitely go back. Service was quite good considering there were a few large groups at that time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAOCAuOudlOf_pN6hwjvuf2pbLLUUqDJ9dmk_O&fid=0x0:0xb776f83a8657f36a"],"When":"2023-3-6"},{"Name":"Robin Daniel Petipas Roscoe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUU6Y9SYvixfkCGnYdN8HB3R62wbw8H_5bJgm6EJrCqdOWT0qqJzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It's sad to say that this place was painfully mediocre for the price.

The food was quite bland and there wasn't much garlic or lemon in anything. The tzatziki didn't have much flavor at all and you are only given maybe 3 tablespoons for the large beef souvlaki plate.

The Ceasar salad was good. The calamari was lightly breaded and cooked well though it wasn't very crispy and did need salt.

The desserts were not worth it for the price.

The Ek mek was boring but it tasted alright, it was described as having a crust that turned out to be kind of a soggy cake that was indiscernible from the custard, the 'roasted almonds' were not roasted and the cinnamon topping overpowered it.

The creme caramel was fine, it tasted good and had a coin sized amount of whipped cream on-top. It was a little smaller than a pudding cup but they charged $6.75 for it which seemed steep.

The servers were great! Friendly and attentive

Overall we won't be back, we were disappointed but understand that they're just catering to the demographic of the area (elderly white people.)

I hope this restaurant brings more flavour to their menu in the future as it's unfortunate that such a prominent restaurant in South Surrey is as boring as it is. No shade to those working there, I genuinely hope that this place can improve in the future","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Haley Camplin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdASxrjoNKHr0lyIbNiWvufLYTtaQOQjthkmNsXM5IqcqV4e0L=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kiki’s is one of my absolute favorite restaurants in my area. Do yourself a favor and get Kiki’s the next time you’re feeling like Greek food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Oceane A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0ZkQ6osemLbFSBeJ8rZC3vNfpBJ6DL53fr2CmvE2QUSo2AjqX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Please tell me how 6 small prawns are 15.95 … I’m very upset over this. Edit: I’m updating this after we finished what was edible. One skewer was raw, both Greek salads had raw mushy cucumbers. For over $100 we are very unsatisfied. The only enjoyable food I ordered was the hummus and the Greek salad. For sure I regrets the $90 spent on this horrible meal.
